UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It\'s fascinating... I have heard orcs proclaim the odor of humans to be sickening and I have heard humans proclaim the odor of orcs to be wretched; yet, to me, all of the races of these lands give off the same odor: The foul, dizzying scent of greed.$B$BDo you doubt the validity of my claim? Do you not see these things that run your life as merely runoff from the greed which dictates your every decision?$B$BSo be it. As it was greed that displaced me from my home, it shall be greed that takes me back.' WHERE entry=1302; /* Text0_0: It\'s fascinating... I have heard orcs proclaim the odor of humans to be sickening and I have heard humans proclaim the odor of orcs to be wretched; yet, to me, all of the races of these lands give off the same odor: The foul, dizzying scent of greed.$B$BDo you doubt the validity of my claim? Do you not see these things that run your life as merely runoff from the greed which dictates your every decision?$B$BSo be it. As it was greed that displaced me from my home, it shall be greed that takes me back. */
