UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hello, $N! If you don\'t see it in my shop, chances are good I can get it!' WHERE entry=1571; /* Text0_0: Hello, $N! If you don\'t see it in my shop, chances are good I can get it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t see many Blacksmiths this far from Ironforge. What can I do for ye?' WHERE entry=1597; /* Text0_0: Don\'t see many Blacksmiths this far from Ironforge. What can I do for ye? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I just can\'t seem to get comfortable without a sturdy ceiling of granite over my head. All these stars up there, enough to give ye the shivers.' WHERE entry=1598; /* Text0_0: I just can\'t seem to get comfortable without a sturdy ceiling of granite over my head. All these stars up there, enough to give ye the shivers. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Now that\'s a piece of steel worth wearing. Form and function lad/lass, I am impressed. Only ever seen it\'s match once, a Master in the Great Forge named Grumnus Steelshaper. I bet he has learned a few things since then, could probably teach some to ye.' WHERE entry=1599; /* Text0_0: Now that\'s a piece of steel worth wearing. Form and function lad/lass, I am impressed. Only ever seen it\'s match once, a Master in the Great Forge named Grumnus Steelshaper. I bet he has learned a few things since then, could probably teach some to ye. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Go to the Great Forge at the very center of Ironforge. He works there, alongside the other Masters of our kind.' WHERE entry=1600; /* Text0_0: Go to the Great Forge at the very center of Ironforge. He works there, alongside the other Masters of our kind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to my forge, Blacksmith. Let me share with you a little secret. No one, no one in the world can you trust. Not men, not women, not beasts ... this you can trust, Steel.' WHERE entry=1605; /* Text0_0: Welcome to my forge, Blacksmith. Let me share with you a little secret. No one, no one in the world can you trust. Not men, not women, not beasts ... this you can trust, Steel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What is it you seek at my forge? Is it training? Do you perhaps seek the secrets of steel? The mysteries of the forge? Speak up Grunt!' WHERE entry=1606; /* Text0_0: What is it you seek at my forge? Is it training? Do you perhaps seek the secrets of steel? The mysteries of the forge? Speak up Grunt! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Travel to Orgrimmar, to the Valley of Honor. There she lives with her husband and two daughters. All of them are smiths of great skill, but the spirits tell me that she will best guide your learning.' WHERE entry=1609; /* Text0_0: Travel to Orgrimmar, to the Valley of Honor. There she lives with her husband and two daughters. All of them are smiths of great skill, but the spirits tell me that she will best guide your learning. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You guide the spirits in the steel to protect and defend with far more skill than I ever could. The student has surpassed the teacher and now I must send you to where your education may continue. $N, you must seek out Shayis Steelfury in Orgrimmar. She is the finest Armorsmith I have ever known, and she can teach you much.' WHERE entry=1610; /* Text0_0: You guide the spirits in the steel to protect and defend with far more skill than I ever could. The student has surpassed the teacher and now I must send you to where your education may continue. $N, you must seek out Shayis Steelfury in Orgrimmar. She is the finest Armorsmith I have ever known, and she can teach you much. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Everything has a spirit, if you learn to listen to it you can get it to take any shape you want. Blacksmithing isn\'t about beating metal, forcing it to do your will. It\'s about listening to the spirit within the steel and guiding it to the shape you know it wants to take.' WHERE entry=1611; /* Text0_0: Everything has a spirit, if you learn to listen to it you can get it to take any shape you want. Blacksmithing isn\'t about beating metal, forcing it to do your will. It\'s about listening to the spirit within the steel and guiding it to the shape you know it wants to take. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have the look of a $g man : woman; who seeks knowledge. Perhaps you seek the teachings of the forge, and the hammer. Perhaps I can guide you down that path. But only once you have accepted the spirits, and listened to their calling.' WHERE entry=1615; /* Text0_0: You have the look of a $g man : woman; who seeks knowledge. Perhaps you seek the teachings of the forge, and the hammer. Perhaps I can guide you down that path. But only once you have accepted the spirits, and listened to their calling. */
