UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Armor like the kind you make could stop even the sharpest axe. I\'m impressed $N, that doesn\'t happen often. Seek out an Orc named Shayis Steelfury, she makes the best armor outside of that cursed Dwarven stronghold.' WHERE entry=1617; /* Text0_0: Armor like the kind you make could stop even the sharpest axe. I\'m impressed $N, that doesn\'t happen often. Seek out an Orc named Shayis Steelfury, she makes the best armor outside of that cursed Dwarven stronghold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='How is the edge of your steel? Good enough to cut through the belly of your enemy? Let me show you some things to make it even sharper.' WHERE entry=1618; /* Text0_0: How is the edge of your steel? Good enough to cut through the belly of your enemy? Let me show you some things to make it even sharper. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Want to be a smith? Want to forge blades to gut your foe? Hammers to crush his skull? Aye I can help, and gladly too if there is blood to be shed from it.' WHERE entry=1619; /* Text0_0: Want to be a smith? Want to forge blades to gut your foe? Hammers to crush his skull? Aye I can help, and gladly too if there is blood to be shed from it. */
