UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Salutations.  I am a guardian of entry.  Unless you have the Plates of Uldum already integrated with your disc set, I will not allow for entry into the Uldum compound.' WHERE entry=1674; /* Text0_0: Salutations.  I am a guardian of entry.  Unless you have the Plates of Uldum already integrated with your disc set, I will not allow for entry into the Uldum compound. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Plates of Uldum are discs synthesized by the Creators that allow access into the Uldum compound.  These discs house and store specific data related to the Creators\' activities here.$B$BPhysically, they are nearly identical in circumference to the disc set you currently possess.  Their markings, however, are directly related to information on Uldum as opposed to the Uldaman complex.' WHERE entry=1675; /* Text0_0: The Plates of Uldum are discs synthesized by the Creators that allow access into the Uldum compound.  These discs house and store specific data related to the Creators\' activities here.$B$BPhysically, they are nearly identical in circumference to the disc set you currently possess.  Their markings, however, are directly related to information on Uldum as opposed to the Uldaman complex. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My purpose is to regulate access to the Uldum complex for the Creators.  I allow entry into the compound only when the solicitor exhibits for access the proper sequencing discs.$B$BYour disc set currently does not contain the Plates of Uldum, the primary prerequisite for entry.  Access is not granted unless the Plates of Uldum are present.' WHERE entry=1676; /* Text0_0: My purpose is to regulate access to the Uldum complex for the Creators.  I allow entry into the compound only when the solicitor exhibits for access the proper sequencing discs.$B$BYour disc set currently does not contain the Plates of Uldum, the primary prerequisite for entry.  Access is not granted unless the Plates of Uldum are present. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Several sets of the Plates of Uldum have been synthesized by the Creators for their expressed use.  The Creators control the distribution of said discs for all complexes on this world.  As such, Azeroth has been rescheduled for visitation, and therefore future discs may enter circulation at that time.$B$BExisting discs have been fully distributed to those parties with appropriate security clearance.' WHERE entry=1677; /* Text0_0: Several sets of the Plates of Uldum have been synthesized by the Creators for their expressed use.  The Creators control the distribution of said discs for all complexes on this world.  As such, Azeroth has been rescheduled for visitation, and therefore future discs may enter circulation at that time.$B$BExisting discs have been fully distributed to those parties with appropriate security clearance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Creators use visitation as a means to reestablish control over seeded worlds when forces, both external and internal, upset the matrix dynamics associated with it.  Such tactics are not to be taken lightly when executed by the Creators.$B$BFor additional information on this world\'s scheduled visitation, please consult the appropriate data repository that fields all Creator-related scheduling considerations.' WHERE entry=1678; /* Text0_0: The Creators use visitation as a means to reestablish control over seeded worlds when forces, both external and internal, upset the matrix dynamics associated with it.  Such tactics are not to be taken lightly when executed by the Creators.$B$BFor additional information on this world\'s scheduled visitation, please consult the appropriate data repository that fields all Creator-related scheduling considerations. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Uldum is a research facility for the Creators in their continuing efforts to enhance the biosphere of Azeroth.  Specific information regarding their work as it relates to Uldum is restricted to those individuals who possess the Plates of Uldum in their disc sets.$B$BData repositories inside the Uldum complex have been programmed to address specific experiments and data compilations; please refer to them for detailed information.' WHERE entry=1679; /* Text0_0: Uldum is a research facility for the Creators in their continuing efforts to enhance the biosphere of Azeroth.  Specific information regarding their work as it relates to Uldum is restricted to those individuals who possess the Plates of Uldum in their disc sets.$B$BData repositories inside the Uldum complex have been programmed to address specific experiments and data compilations; please refer to them for detailed information. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Thank the light you are here! I\'d accept help from a two-headed ogre at this point.$B$BThe city has been overrun by troggs! The attempts to wipe them out resulted in mass contamination. But there is still hope.$B$BOur scientists who evacuated to Ironforge are working on a cure for the fallout sickness. Meanwhile, if you can help me stop the trogg invasion, perhaps the city can be retaken. ' WHERE entry=1693; /* Text0_1: Thank the light you are here! I\'d accept help from a two-headed ogre at this point.$B$BThe city has been overrun by troggs! The attempts to wipe them out resulted in mass contamination. But there is still hope.$B$BOur scientists who evacuated to Ironforge are working on a cure for the fallout sickness. Meanwhile, if you can help me stop the trogg invasion, perhaps the city can be retaken. */
