UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Greetings, $N. Have you come to learn of the history of Ironforge?' WHERE entry=2234; /* Text0_1: Greetings, $N. Have you come to learn of the history of Ironforge? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Notify me when you are ready to listen to the story.' WHERE entry=2235; /* Text0_1: Notify me when you are ready to listen to the story. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Hundreds of years ago, the great city of Thaurissan stood proudly in a lush expanse of land that is now the dilapidated Burning Steppes.$B$BThaurissan was home to the nation of Dark Iron dwarves and at the time, in the midst of a civil war among the dwarven nation at large.$B$BYou see, that area of the world was at one point in time part of the Redridge Mountains - until the day that Thaurissan was consumed by a gigantic explosion. The city lay in ruin, the surrounding areas reduced to an ashy wasteland.$b' WHERE entry=2236; /* Text0_1: Hundreds of years ago, the great city of Thaurissan stood proudly in a lush expanse of land that is now the dilapidated Burning Steppes.$B$BThaurissan was home to the nation of Dark Iron dwarves and at the time, in the midst of a civil war among the dwarven nation at large.$B$BYou see, that area of the world was at one point in time part of the Redridge Mountains - until the day that Thaurissan was consumed by a gigantic explosion. The city lay in ruin, the surrounding areas reduced to an ashy wasteland.$b */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We do not know.$B$BThe Dark Irons that did survive made their way into the mountain and began rebuilding their city.$B$BFrom the ashes of Thaurissan then rose Blackrock Spire and the new Dark Iron nation. Additional fortifications were made within the Searing Gorge, in the area known as the Cauldron.$B$BStories of an ancient evil that controlled the kingdom of Dark Irons began to circulate.' WHERE entry=2237; /* Text0_1: We do not know.$B$BThe Dark Irons that did survive made their way into the mountain and began rebuilding their city.$B$BFrom the ashes of Thaurissan then rose Blackrock Spire and the new Dark Iron nation. Additional fortifications were made within the Searing Gorge, in the area known as the Cauldron.$B$BStories of an ancient evil that controlled the kingdom of Dark Irons began to circulate. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Recently, the Dark Irons have been seen on the surface world with greater regularity. Fortresses have been built in the Badlands. Massive exploratory forces have been sent into the depths of Uldaman in search of ancient lore. They have even invaded our own homeland, striking at our dam near the loch.' WHERE entry=2238; /* Text0_1: Recently, the Dark Irons have been seen on the surface world with greater regularity. Fortresses have been built in the Badlands. Massive exploratory forces have been sent into the depths of Uldaman in search of ancient lore. They have even invaded our own homeland, striking at our dam near the loch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We need adventurers to assist us, $N. Will you help?' WHERE entry=2239; /* Text0_1: We need adventurers to assist us, $N. Will you help? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Um, hello!  If you are here about fee collection and/or a summons, then you must have me mistaken for someone else.  Terribly sorry!' WHERE entry=2253; /* Text0_0: Um, hello!  If you are here about fee collection and/or a summons, then you must have me mistaken for someone else.  Terribly sorry! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I think my necklace fell in the lake.  My daddy got it for me, and he\'s gonna be mad now.' WHERE entry=2273; /* Text0_1: I think my necklace fell in the lake.  My daddy got it for me, and he\'s gonna be mad now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Thank you $g mister : miss; for finding my necklace!  You\'re the best!' WHERE entry=2274; /* Text0_1: Thank you $g mister : miss; for finding my necklace!  You\'re the best! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Besides the Grunts outside, my brothers and I fought at the battle of Hyjal. Any who seek to steal from the bank must face us first.',Text0_1_loc9='Besides the Grunts outside, my brothers and I fought at the battle of Hyjal. Any who seek to steal from the bank must face us first.',Text1_0_loc9='I guarantee this bank\'s security with my own blood, is that good enough for you?',Text1_1_loc9='I guarantee this bank\'s security with my own blood, is that good enough for you?' WHERE entry=2275; /* Text0_0: Besides the Grunts outside, my brothers and I fought at the battle of Hyjal. Any who seek to steal from the bank must face us first. */ /* Text0_1: Besides the Grunts outside, my brothers and I fought at the battle of Hyjal. Any who seek to steal from the bank must face us first. */ /* Text1_0: I guarantee this bank\'s security with my own blood, is that good enough for you? */ /* Text1_1: I guarantee this bank\'s security with my own blood, is that good enough for you? */
