UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'ll have to be patient with me, $N. I\'ve got my Spybot inside working on a very delicate matter. I\'ll be with ya in a second.$B$BOh, and do me a favor, try not to let Lescovar see you... we\'re about to ambush him.' WHERE entry=2394; /* Text0_0: You\'ll have to be patient with me, $N. I\'ve got my Spybot inside working on a very delicate matter. I\'ll be with ya in a second.$B$BOh, and do me a favor, try not to let Lescovar see you... we\'re about to ambush him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Rough times, huh, $N? No matter where you turn someone needs help, and my wife and I are no exception.' WHERE entry=2414; /* Text0_0: Rough times, huh, $N? No matter where you turn someone needs help, and my wife and I are no exception. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hi there! The name\'s Gregan. What can I do for ya?' WHERE entry=2433; /* Text0_0: Hi there! The name\'s Gregan. What can I do for ya? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Sure thing, $N. You look like you can be trusted... Trustworthy! I can spot that a mile away...$B$BAnyway, back to what I was sayin\'. Takes one Evoroot plant to make the Videre Elixir. The rest \'a the ingredients are trivial really, but the Evoroot, well, that can be a bit tricky to get.' WHERE entry=2434; /* Text0_0: Sure thing, $N. You look like you can be trusted... Trustworthy! I can spot that a mile away...$B$BAnyway, back to what I was sayin\'. Takes one Evoroot plant to make the Videre Elixir. The rest \'a the ingredients are trivial really, but the Evoroot, well, that can be a bit tricky to get. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Get it over with you filthy $r.$B$B<Kharan lowers his head, exposing his stubby neck.>' WHERE entry=2473; /* Text0_0: Get it over with you filthy $r.$B$B<Kharan lowers his head, exposing his stubby neck.> */
