UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ye\'ve come to the right place $glad : lass;!  People come here from all o\'er the world to train to be a blacksmith.  Ye\'ll find Bengus Deepforge hammering away at an anvil in the middle of our fine city by The Great Forge itself.',Text0_1_loc9='Ye\'ve come to the right place $glad : lass;!  People come here from all o\'er the world to train to be a blacksmith.  Ye\'ll find Bengus Deepforge hammering away at an anvil in the middle of our fine city by The Great Forge itself.',Text1_0_loc9='Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  $B$BIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge.  ',Text1_1_loc9='Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  $B$BIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge.  ' WHERE entry=2795; /* Text0_0: Ye\'ve come to the right place $glad : lass;!  People come here from all o\'er the world to train to be a blacksmith.  Ye\'ll find Bengus Deepforge hammering away at an anvil in the middle of our fine city by The Great Forge itself. */ /* Text0_1: Ye\'ve come to the right place $glad : lass;!  People come here from all o\'er the world to train to be a blacksmith.  Ye\'ll find Bengus Deepforge hammering away at an anvil in the middle of our fine city by The Great Forge itself. */ /* Text1_0: Are ye really askin\' me where the Blacksmith is?  Have ye not heard of The Great Forge!?  All our best blacksmiths gather there to craft their weapons and armor!  $B$BIt\'s dead smack in the middle of Ironforge, and that\'s where you\'ll find one of our most brilliant blacksmiths, Bengus Deepforge. */ /* Text1_1