UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A Cooking trainer is it?  Well then, get yerself over to the Bronze Kettle on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.  Daryl Riknussun will teach ye to make a mighty fine dish that\'s sure to put the life back in ye!',Text0_1_loc9='A Cooking trainer is it?  Well then, get yerself over to the Bronze Kettle on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.  Daryl Riknussun will teach ye to make a mighty fine dish that\'s sure to put the life back in ye!',Text1_0_loc9='Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.',Text1_1_loc9='Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=2796; /* Text0_0: A Cooking trainer is it?  Well then, get yerself over to the Bronze Kettle on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.  Daryl Riknussun will teach ye to make a mighty fine dish that\'s sure to put the life back in ye! */ /* Text0_1: A Cooking trainer is it?  Well then, get yerself over to the Bronze Kettle on the northeastern side of The Great Forge.  Daryl Riknussun will teach ye to make a mighty fine dish that\'s sure to put the life back in ye! */ /* Text1_0: Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge. */ /* Text1_1: Och!  That Daryl Riknussun is a brilliant cook!  He makes a chilli so hot ye could temper steel with it!  I don\'t think he\'ll teach ye the recipe, but he\'ll certainly help ye to become a good cook.  Ye\'ll find him at the Bronze Kettle o\'er on the northeastern side of The Great Forge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, I believe Gimble Thistlefuzz is who ye\'ll be needing if yer looking to learn the Enchanter\'s profession.  Ye\'ll find Gimble in his shop, Thistlefuzz Arcanery, right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.',Text0_1_loc9='Ah, I believe Gimble Thistlefuzz is who ye\'ll be needing if yer looking to learn the Enchanter\'s profession.  Ye\'ll find Gimble in his shop, Thistlefuzz Arcanery, right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.',Text1_0_loc9='Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'t spill a drop, but now I can\'t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  $B$BYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He\'ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.',Text1_1_loc9='Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'t spill a drop, but now I can\'t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  $B$BYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He\'ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=2797; /* Text0_0: Ah, I believe Gimble Thistlefuzz is who ye\'ll be needing if yer looking to learn the Enchanter\'s profession.  Ye\'ll find Gimble in his shop, Thistlefuzz Arcanery, right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge. */ /* Text0_1: Ah, I believe Gimble Thistlefuzz is who ye\'ll be needing if yer looking to learn the Enchanter\'s profession.  Ye\'ll find Gimble in his shop, Thistlefuzz Arcanery, right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge. */ /* Text1_0: Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'t spill a drop, but now I can\'t drink from it!  Such a tragedy.  $B$BYou be sure to heed me advice when ye see Gimble.  He\'ll be in his shop right by the Gryphon Master at The Great Forge. */ /* Text1_1: Och!  Ye should be careful what ye get enchanted $glad : lass;.  I had me mug enchanted so it wouldn\'