UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The skill with which Telonis crafts armor is beyond compare.  You should be grateful that he does not charge more for the knowledge he passes to others.  Go now and seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in the northeast section of Darnassus.',Text0_1_loc9='The skill with which Telonis crafts armor is beyond compare.  You should be grateful that he does not charge more for the knowledge he passes to others.  Go now and seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in the northeast section of Darnassus.',Text1_0_loc9='We plant the vegetables.  Our vegetables are eaten by the rabbit.  The rabbit is devoured by the wolf.  The wolf is slain by us.  We take the meat and hide from the wolf\'s corpse.  It\'s that Magic Circle of life, or whatever you call it.  $B$BNow go see Telonis in the Cenarion Enclave to get started and let me return to my duties.',Text1_1_loc9='We plant the vegetables.  Our vegetables are eaten by the rabbit.  The rabbit is devoured by the wolf.  The wolf is slain by us.  We take the meat and hide from the wolf\'s corpse.  It\'s that Magic Circle of life, or whatever you call it.  $B$BNow go see Telonis in the Cenarion Enclave to get started and let me return to my duties.' WHERE entry=3040; /* Text0_0: The skill with which Telonis crafts armor is beyond compare.  You should be grateful that he does not charge more for the knowledge he passes to others.  Go now and seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in the northeast section of Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: The skill with which Telonis crafts armor is beyond compare.  You should be grateful that he does not charge more for the knowledge he passes to others.  Go now and seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in the northeast section of Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: We plant the vegetables.  Our vegetables are eaten by the rabbit.  The rabbit is devoured by the wolf.  The wolf is slain by us.  We take the meat and hide from the wolf\'s corpse.  It\'s that Magic Circle of life, or whatever you call it.  $B$BNow go see Telonis in the Cenarion Enclave to get started and let me return to my duties. */ /* Text1_1: We plant the vegetables.  Our vegetables are eaten by the rabbit.  The rabbit is devoured by the wolf.  The wolf is slain by us.  We take the meat and hide from the wolf\'s corpse.  It\'s that Magic Circle of life, or whatever you call it.  $B$BNow go see Telonis in the Cenarion Enclave to get started and let me return to my duties. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='In death, the animals of the world bestow both life and protection unto us.  If you feel that you can offer the appropriate respect for their sacrifice, then the skinner\'s profession may suit you.  Speak with Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northern Darnassus to learn more.',Text0_1_loc9='In death, the animals of the world bestow both life and protection unto us.  If you feel that you can offer the appropriate respect for their sacrifice, then the skinner\'s profession may suit you.  Speak with Eladriel in the Craftsman\'s Terrace in northern Darnassus to learn more.',Text1_0_loc9='As a culture we believe in letting nothing go to waste.  When we are forced to slay a creature we take what we can to make sure its sacrifice was not in vain.  $B$BIf you wish to learn the proper way to take the skin of a slain beast, then seek out Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace.',Text1_1_loc9='As a culture we believe in letting nothing go to waste.  When we are forced to slay a creature we take what we can to make sure its sacrifice was not in vain.  $B$BIf you wish to learn the proper way to take the skin of a slain beast, then seek out Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace.' WHERE entry=3042; /* Text0_0: In death, the animals of the world bestow both life and protection unto us.  If you feel that you can offer the appropriate respect for their sacrifice, then the skinner\'s profession may suit you.  Speak with Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northern Darnassus to learn more. */ /* Text0_1: In death, the animals of the world bestow both life and protection unto us.  If you feel that you can offer the appropriate respect for their sacrifice, then the skinner\'s profession may suit you.  Speak with Eladriel in the Craftsman\'s Terrace in northern Darnassus to learn more. */ /* Text1_0: As a culture we believe in letting nothing go to waste.  When we are forced to slay a creature we take what we can to make sure its sacrifice was not in vain.  $B$BIf you wish to learn the proper way to take the skin of a slain beast, then seek out Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace. */ /* Text1_1: As a culture we believe in letting nothing go to waste.  When we are forced to slay a creature we take what we can to make sure its sacrifice was not in vain.  $B$BIf you wish to learn the proper way to take the skin of a slain beast, then seek out Eladriel in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You would certainly be looking for Me\'Lynn if you have any hope of learning to be a tailor.  She resides at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus.',Text0_1_loc9='You would certainly be looking for Me\'Lynn if you have any hope of learning to be a tailor.  She resides at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus.',Text1_0_loc9='With the garments that Me\'Lynn tailors, one might think that her needle was blessed by Elune herself.  Unless your needle is so blessed, you best pay her a visit and listen to her teachings.  You can find her in The Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus.',Text1_1_loc9='With the garments that Me\'Lynn tailors, one might think that her needle was blessed by Elune herself.  Unless your needle is so blessed, you best pay her a visit and listen to her teachings.  You can find her in The Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus.' WHERE entry=3044; /* Text0_0: You would certainly be looking for Me\'Lynn if you have any hope of learning to be a tailor.  She resides at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus. */ /* Text0_1: You would certainly be looking for Me\'Lynn if you have any hope of learning to be a tailor.  She resides at the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus. */ /* Text1_0: With the garments that Me\'Lynn tailors, one might think that her needle was blessed by Elune herself.  Unless your needle is so blessed, you best pay her a visit and listen to her teachings.  You can find her in The Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus. */ /* Text1_1: With the garments that Me\'Lynn tailors, one might think that her needle was blessed by Elune herself.  Unless your needle is so blessed, you best pay her a visit and listen to her teachings.  You can find her in The Craftsmen\'s Terrace in northeastern Darnassus. */
