UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Kar Aman, $N. You look to be a strong $c--you would do well to mind yourself in this area. Touching things you know nothing about, or showing disrespect to your elders is just cause for punishment.$B$BYou may not respect me or my companions, but you will learn to respect our power if you prove foolish enough.$B$BNow, enough with the pleasantries, was there something I can do for you?' WHERE entry=3298; /* Text0_1: Kar Aman, $N. You look to be a strong $c--you would do well to mind yourself in this area. Touching things you know nothing about, or showing disrespect to your elders is just cause for punishment.$B$BYou may not respect me or my companions, but you will learn to respect our power if you prove foolish enough.$B$BNow, enough with the pleasantries, was there something I can do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ah, a fellow warlock who has proven $ghis:her; worth to some degree.$B$BI am pleased to meet your acquaintance. My name is Menara Voidrender... and not without just cause.$B$BYou seem powerful and well-learned enough that other tools... more powerful tools... would be welcome and not foolishly imparted. If this is true, then speak to me further. If not, well then, you know your way  back to the docks and off into the ocean.' WHERE entry=3299; /* Text0_1: Ah, a fellow warlock who has proven $ghis:her; worth to some degree.$B$BI am pleased to meet your acquaintance. My name is Menara Voidrender... and not without just cause.$B$BYou seem powerful and well-learned enough that other tools... more powerful tools... would be welcome and not foolishly imparted. If this is true, then speak to me further. If not, well then, you know your way  back to the docks and off into the ocean. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='In decades past - of now ancient wars and conflicts - our kind was driven to the brink of extinction. Much we have endured, $r.$B$BThe onslaught of the Burning Legion. The Demon Soul. The Aspects divided. The ascension of Deathwing. The enslavement of our Queen, Alexstrasza, by the Dragonmaw.$B$BThrough it all, we have been the unshakable will of the dragons - the undaunted force that has fought to represent our waning existence in this world.' WHERE entry=3301; /* Text0_0: In decades past - of now ancient wars and conflicts - our kind was driven to the brink of extinction. Much we have endured, $r.$B$BThe onslaught of the Burning Legion. The Demon Soul. The Aspects divided. The ascension of Deathwing. The enslavement of our Queen, Alexstrasza, by the Dragonmaw.$B$BThrough it all, we have been the unshakable will of the dragons - the undaunted force that has fought to represent our waning existence in this world. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Indeed. I stand before you in a form that you can comprehend, mortal. Surely, you could not bear to stand in the presence of the dragon known as Vaelastrasz.$B$B<Vaelan laughs.>$B$BShall I continue?' WHERE entry=3302; /* Text0_0: Indeed. I stand before you in a form that you can comprehend, mortal. Surely, you could not bear to stand in the presence of the dragon known as Vaelastrasz.$B$B<Vaelan laughs.>$B$BShall I continue? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Perhaps I should tell you why I am here.$B$BDo you know of the Aspect, Deathwing? Or of his progeny, Nefarian and Onyxia?' WHERE entry=3303; /* Text0_0: Perhaps I should tell you why I am here.$B$BDo you know of the Aspect, Deathwing? Or of his progeny, Nefarian and Onyxia? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Deathwing, or Neltharion as he was once known, was the Aspect that embodied the strength of the world - granted almost limitless power over this mortal realm by the Titan shaper known as Khaz\'goroth: Forger of the world.$B$BThrough treachery and deceit, the foul one convinced the four other Aspects to imbue an item, known as the Demon Soul, with their powers - greatly weakening them, forcing a division among the once great Aspects. $b' WHERE entry=3304; /* Text0_0: Deathwing, or Neltharion as he was once known, was the Aspect that embodied the strength of the world - granted almost limitless power over this mortal realm by the Titan shaper known as Khaz\'goroth: Forger of the world.$B$BThrough treachery and deceit, the foul one convinced the four other Aspects to imbue an item, known as the Demon Soul, with their powers - greatly weakening them, forcing a division among the once great Aspects. $b */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Indeed. The item was ultimately destroyed and Deathwing nearly slain by the combined and renewed power of the four remaining Aspects. Where Deathwing is now is unknown. What we do know, however, is that one of his progeny, Nefarian, rules this citadel and wishes to continue where his father left off.' WHERE entry=3305; /* Text0_0: Indeed. The item was ultimately destroyed and Deathwing nearly slain by the combined and renewed power of the four remaining Aspects. Where Deathwing is now is unknown. What we do know, however, is that one of his progeny, Nefarian, rules this citadel and wishes to continue where his father left off. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Before his banishment, Deathwing was attempting to create impure offspring. Half breeds that would not only be immune to the innate natural powers and abilities of their Aspects but also under the complete control of Deathwing.$B$BIt seems that where his father failed, Nefarian may have succeeded - at least partially.$B$BIt was Ysera, Aspect of Dreams, who saw the abominations and forced us to act. If these \'Chromatic\' dragonkin exist, they must be destroyed.' WHERE entry=3306; /* Text0_0: Before his banishment, Deathwing was attempting to create impure offspring. Half breeds that would not only be immune to the innate natural powers and abilities of their Aspects but also under the complete control of Deathwing.$B$BIt seems that where his father failed, Nefarian may have succeeded - at least partially.$B$BIt was Ysera, Aspect of Dreams, who saw the abominations and forced us to act. If these \'Chromatic\' dragonkin exist, they must be destroyed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is not our way, nor would it be possible. Nefarian is guarded by ancient wards, as old as the Aspects themselves. It is what prevents me from entering the inner sanctum of this citadel. The dark magic prevents any of the other flight to enter without being ordained... unless.' WHERE entry=3307; /* Text0_0: It is not our way, nor would it be possible. Nefarian is guarded by ancient wards, as old as the Aspects themselves. It is what prevents me from entering the inner sanctum of this citadel. The dark magic prevents any of the other flight to enter without being ordained... unless. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is possible for one, not of dragon kind, to obtain the Adorned Seal of Ascension and pass through the protected barrier. While possession of such an item would surely destroy me, perhaps you could utilize it and lower the barrier.' WHERE entry=3308; /* Text0_0: It is possible for one, not of dragon kind, to obtain the Adorned Seal of Ascension and pass through the protected barrier. While possession of such an item would surely destroy me, perhaps you could utilize it and lower the barrier. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You must find one amongst the wretch in the lower portion of this citadel that has attained an Unadorned Seal of Ascension. It is a great honor for one of the lesser beings to obtain this item, as it is the first step in gaining access to the upper citadel and becoming one of Nefarian\'s elite guardsmen - the Blackhand legion. Find such an item and return it to me so that I may examine its properties. I will know how to proceed once my inspection of the seal is complete.' WHERE entry=3309; /* Text0_0: You must find one amongst the wretch in the lower portion of this citadel that has attained an Unadorned Seal of Ascension. It is a great honor for one of the lesser beings to obtain this item, as it is the first step in gaining access to the upper citadel and becoming one of Nefarian\'s elite guardsmen - the Blackhand legion. Find such an item and return it to me so that I may examine its properties. I will know how to proceed once my inspection of the seal is complete. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Be warned, mortal, it is exceptionally rare that one of the lesser clans in this citadel would hold such an item. Your search could take decades. I recommend you destroy these beasts without impunity.' WHERE entry=3310; /* Text0_0: Be warned, mortal, it is exceptionally rare that one of the lesser clans in this citadel would hold such an item. Your search could take decades. I recommend you destroy these beasts without impunity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do not bring it any closer, mortal. I can sense the evil coursing through the seal from where I stand.$B$BGive me a moment to inspect the item - hold it firmly.' WHERE entry=3311; /* Text0_0: Do not bring it any closer, mortal. I can sense the evil coursing through the seal from where I stand.$B$BGive me a moment to inspect the item - hold it firmly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Dis ain\'t no game mon. Joo want to use da axe, joo got to say da line. Say it wif me???Say hello, to ma little friend.' WHERE entry=3321; /* Text0_0: Dis ain\'t no game mon. Joo want to use da axe, joo got to say da line. Say it wif me???Say hello, to ma little friend. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='$N, I\'ve come to find out how rampant the effects of Fel Moss are throughout Darkshore. The corruption of Teldrassil and our surrounding lands really concerns the druids of the Cenarian Circle, and all Night elves.$B$BIt is my goal to find out why this has happened and to put an end to it.' WHERE entry=3334; /* Text0_0: $N, I\'ve come to find out how rampant the effects of Fel Moss are throughout Darkshore. The corruption of Teldrassil and our surrounding lands really concerns the druids of the Cenarian Circle, and all Night elves.$B$BIt is my goal to find out why this has happened and to put an end to it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Because the blade can never be too sharp nor the armor too tough a talented enchanter will always be needed.  Such an enchanter is Taladan, who can show you how to properly weave enchantments to improve your weapons and armor.  Seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace.',Text0_1_loc9='Because the blade can never be too sharp nor the armor too tough a talented enchanter will always be needed.  Such an enchanter is Taladan, who can show you how to properly weave enchantments to improve your weapons and armor.  Seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace.',Text1_0_loc9='I\'m flattered, but really I\'m not interested... What?  You want to know where to learn enchanting?  Oh, how embarrassing!  Well, you should...  I\'m sure you could... go see, um...  Taladan!  Yes, see Taladan over in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace!',Text1_1_loc9='I\'m flattered, but really I\'m not interested... What?  You want to know where to learn enchanting?  Oh, how embarrassing!  Well, you should...  I\'m sure you could... go see, um...  Taladan!  Yes, see Taladan over in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace!' WHERE entry=3337; /* Text0_0: Because the blade can never be too sharp nor the armor too tough a talented enchanter will always be needed.  Such an enchanter is Taladan, who can show you how to properly weave enchantments to improve your weapons and armor.  Seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace. */ /* Text0_1: Because the blade can never be too sharp nor the armor too tough a talented enchanter will always be needed.  Such an enchanter is Taladan, who can show you how to properly weave enchantments to improve your weapons and armor.  Seek him out in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace. */ /* Text1_0: I\'m flattered, but really I\'m not interested... What?  You want to know where to learn enchanting?  Oh, how embarrassing!  Well, you should...  I\'m sure you could... go see, um...  Taladan!  Yes, see Taladan over in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace! */ /* Text1_1: I\'m flattered, but really I\'m not interested... What?  You want to know where to learn enchanting?  Oh, how embarrassing!  Well, you should...  I\'m sure you could... go see, um...  Taladan!  Yes, see Taladan over in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to my shop, $c. What is it the Goodstitch brothers can do for you?' WHERE entry=3357; /* Text0_0: Welcome to my shop, $c. What is it the Goodstitch brothers can do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, one of my favorite customers. You look to be of a warlock of some power, $N. I am pleased to meet you. If there is anything I can do for you, please, just ask.$B$BMy brother and I feel that it will be your kind who lead us into the next great era. One with such power... such control... it\'s only a matter of time before the Legion itself bends to your will.$B$BI am but a little envious.' WHERE entry=3358; /* Text0_0: Ah, one of my favorite customers. You look to be of a warlock of some power, $N. I am pleased to meet you. If there is anything I can do for you, please, just ask.$B$BMy brother and I feel that it will be your kind who lead us into the next great era. One with such power... such control... it\'s only a matter of time before the Legion itself bends to your will.$B$BI am but a little envious. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ah, $r... I possess great knowledge a\' da world and how ta create charms a\' great power.' WHERE entry=3375; /* Text0_1: Ah, $r... I possess great knowledge a\' da world and how ta create charms a\' great power. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Mau\'ari know why you seek her out...$B$BBring me da E\'ko you find in the world, an\' I can transform it for you.' WHERE entry=3377; /* Text0_1: Mau\'ari know why you seek her out...$B$BBring me da E\'ko you find in the world, an\' I can transform it for you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yeah yeah, I know Dadanga dislikes smoke.  From the smell of it though, seems like Dadanga also dislikes bathing.' WHERE entry=3380; /* Text0_0: Yeah yeah, I know Dadanga dislikes smoke.  From the smell of it though, seems like Dadanga also dislikes bathing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Da Cache of Mau\'ari holds great secrets... The shards used ta make it are reflective, and you can use its shiny surface ta siphon power from other tings and den reflect it onto yourself.$B$BKeeping da charm in your inventory lets you collect e\'ko, da spiritual power from the beasts you fight. Once you find e\'ko, you bring it ta Mau\'ari.' WHERE entry=3382; /* Text0_1: Da Cache of Mau\'ari holds great secrets... The shards used ta make it are reflective, and you can use its shiny surface ta siphon power from other tings and den reflect it onto yourself.$B$BKeeping da charm in your inventory lets you collect e\'ko, da spiritual power from the beasts you fight. Once you find e\'ko, you bring it ta Mau\'ari. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='E\'ko is da power dat each creatures possesses. Da charm I made for ya allows you ta capture it in a physical manifestation.$B$BI know an incantation dat can transform da e\'ko you find, and turn it into juju.$B$BYou can den take the Cache of Mau\'ari, an\' use it ta reflect da power of da juju onto yourself.$B$BC\'mon, give it a try. Bring da e\'ko ta Mau\'ari an\' we have some fun.' WHERE entry=3383; /* Text0_1: E\'ko is da power dat each creatures possesses. Da charm I made for ya allows you ta capture it in a physical manifestation.$B$BI know an incantation dat can transform da e\'ko you find, and turn it into juju.$B$BYou can den take the Cache of Mau\'ari, an\' use it ta reflect da power of da juju onto yourself.$B$BC\'mon, give it a try. Bring da e\'ko ta Mau\'ari an\' we have some fun. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Good day to ye $g lad : lass;. Can I be of service?' WHERE entry=3395; /* Text0_0: Good day to ye $g lad : lass;. Can I be of service? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Here for training eh? Just began my training meself, but I would be glad ta teach ye what I can.' WHERE entry=3396; /* Text0_0: Here for training eh? Just began my training meself, but I would be glad ta teach ye what I can. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ye learn fast $g lad : lass;, much faster than I can keep up with. If ye want ta continue yer training, I suggest ye see my teacher. His name\'s Rotgath, Rotgath Stonebeard and ye\'ll find him in Ironforge at The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=3397; /* Text0_0: Ye learn fast $g lad : lass;, much faster than I can keep up with. If ye want ta continue yer training, I suggest ye see my teacher. His name\'s Rotgath, Rotgath Stonebeard and ye\'ll find him in Ironforge at The Great Forge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Eh? I don\'t have time ta chat, my da\' wants me ta finish this order fer him.' WHERE entry=3398; /* Text0_0: Eh? I don\'t have time ta chat, my da\' wants me ta finish this order fer him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ye\'ve got a little skill on ye. Enough to learn ye a few things I wager. Let\'s see what I can teach ye, shall we?' WHERE entry=3399; /* Text0_0: Ye\'ve got a little skill on ye. Enough to learn ye a few things I wager. Let\'s see what I can teach ye, shall we? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ye know more than I do, that\'s a certainty. Tell ye what though, go talk with me da\'. He\'ll want ye ta prove yerself, but he is a fine teacher indeed. His name\'s Rotgath, and ye\'ll find him near the anvils workin steel for ol\' Bengus.' WHERE entry=3400; /* Text0_0: Ye know more than I do, that\'s a certainty. Tell ye what though, go talk with me da\'. He\'ll want ye ta prove yerself, but he is a fine teacher indeed. His name\'s Rotgath, and ye\'ll find him near the anvils workin steel for ol\' Bengus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well my friend, ye have more skill than I do. Why don\'t ye go find me old friend Rotgath Stonebeard. He stayed in Ironforge when I left to join Jaina\'s army. I\'m sure he\'ll be able ta teach ye somethin, or at least know someone who can. If he\'s still around, I\'m sure he\'ll be at The Great Forge.' WHERE entry=3401; /* Text0_0: Well my friend, ye have more skill than I do. Why don\'t ye go find me old friend Rotgath Stonebeard. He stayed in Ironforge when I left to join Jaina\'s army. I\'m sure he\'ll be able ta teach ye somethin, or at least know someone who can. If he\'s still around, I\'m sure he\'ll be at The Great Forge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The creatures in Winterspring are a good place ta start.$B$BHoweva\', der may also be other places you can look...' WHERE entry=3402; /* Text0_1: The creatures in Winterspring are a good place ta start.$B$BHoweva\', der may also be other places you can look... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Of course I can help you with training. I\'m just a journeyman myself, but I\'m sure there\'s something I can show you.' WHERE entry=3403; /* Text0_0: Of course I can help you with training. I\'m just a journeyman myself, but I\'m sure there\'s something I can show you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I don\'t admit this lightly, but you are a far better smith than I am. If you want to learn more than my meager teachings then I suggest you seek out a Dwarf named Therum Deepforge in Stormwind. You will find him in the Dwarven District.' WHERE entry=3404; /* Text0_0: I don\'t admit this lightly, but you are a far better smith than I am. If you want to learn more than my meager teachings then I suggest you seek out a Dwarf named Therum Deepforge in Stormwind. You will find him in the Dwarven District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m sorry, I\'m a bit busy right now making horseshoes for Verner Osgood in Lakeshire.' WHERE entry=3405; /* Text0_0: I\'m sorry, I\'m a bit busy right now making horseshoes for Verner Osgood in Lakeshire. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do I look like I have the time to spend jawin?' WHERE entry=3406; /* Text0_0: Do I look like I have the time to spend jawin? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re not bad, but let me show you a few tricks you might find handy.' WHERE entry=3407; /* Text0_0: You\'re not bad, but let me show you a few tricks you might find handy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A far better blacksmith than I am, that\'s for sure. Though I\'ll deny it if you tell anyone I said that. You should go speak with Therum Deepforge. If anyone can teach you more, it\'s him.' WHERE entry=3408; /* Text0_0: A far better blacksmith than I am, that\'s for sure. Though I\'ll deny it if you tell anyone I said that. You should go speak with Therum Deepforge. If anyone can teach you more, it\'s him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I hear one comment about waterfowl, and you will be eating through a tube.' WHERE entry=3409; /* Text0_0: I hear one comment about waterfowl, and you will be eating through a tube. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Just swinging a hammer at an anvil doesn\'t make you a smith. Give me that and let me teach you something before you embarrass us all.' WHERE entry=3410; /* Text0_0: Just swinging a hammer at an anvil doesn\'t make you a smith. Give me that and let me teach you something before you embarrass us all. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Not bad. Go talk with Snarl, he just moved to Orgrimmar to study under Saru. Look for him in the Warrior district near Saru\'s smithy. Oh and he\'ll test you, so you better be as ready as you think you are.' WHERE entry=3411; /* Text0_0: Not bad. Go talk with Snarl, he just moved to Orgrimmar to study under Saru. Look for him in the Warrior district near Saru\'s smithy. Oh and he\'ll test you, so you better be as ready as you think you are. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Snarl calls me simple because I am too slow. I just want to do the job right, and that takes time.' WHERE entry=3412; /* Text0_0: Snarl calls me simple because I am too slow. I just want to do the job right, and that takes time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I can show you what you wish to know, but you must be patient. Take your time to work the steel and feel the way it shapes beneath your hammer. When you become one with the steel, then you will understand.' WHERE entry=3413; /* Text0_0: I can show you what you wish to know, but you must be patient. Take your time to work the steel and feel the way it shapes beneath your hammer. When you become one with the steel, then you will understand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You learn quickly, that is not a bad thing. Just be sure to do the job right, as long as it takes to do so. Now, I fear I must send you to Snarl to learn more. Learn what he can teach, but do not listen to his angry words. He gets that way when Saru\'s daughters laugh at him.' WHERE entry=3414; /* Text0_0: You learn quickly, that is not a bad thing. Just be sure to do the job right, as long as it takes to do so. Now, I fear I must send you to Snarl to learn more. Learn what he can teach, but do not listen to his angry words. He gets that way when Saru\'s daughters laugh at him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I listen and I listen but I don\'t hear these spirits that Karn speaks of. ' WHERE entry=3415; /* Text0_0: I listen and I listen but I don\'t hear these spirits that Karn speaks of. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Karn says we need to listen to the spirits of the forge and of the steel, that they will guide us. I hear nothing but a ringing in my ears. Here, take a hammer and let us try to hear the spirits together.' WHERE entry=3416; /* Text0_0: Karn says we need to listen to the spirits of the forge and of the steel, that they will guide us. I hear nothing but a ringing in my ears. Here, take a hammer and let us try to hear the spirits together. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I guess the spirits like you better than me, I still have not heard their call but you seem to have gathered their lessons well. Go speak to Karn, he will be excited to see one who hears them as he does.' WHERE entry=3417; /* Text0_0: I guess the spirits like you better than me, I still have not heard their call but you seem to have gathered their lessons well. Go speak to Karn, he will be excited to see one who hears them as he does. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Your interruption is costing me valuable time, this had better be good.' WHERE entry=3418; /* Text0_1: Your interruption is costing me valuable time, this had better be good. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ah yes, another who will stoke the fires and forge the weapons of war. Of course I will teach you how.' WHERE entry=3419; /* Text0_1: Ah yes, another who will stoke the fires and forge the weapons of war. Of course I will teach you how. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You have learned well my child. Go to the Undercity, find a smith named James Van Brunt. He will be able to teach you much that I cannot. I understand he spends his time near the Warriors training hall, forging their weapons and armor.' WHERE entry=3420; /* Text0_1: You have learned well my child. Go to the Undercity, find a smith named James Van Brunt. He will be able to teach you much that I cannot. I understand he spends his time near the Warriors training hall, forging their weapons and armor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I hope to one day forge weapons and armor from the bones of my enemies.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:' WHERE entry=3421; /* Text0_0: I hope to one day forge weapons and armor from the bones of my enemies. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are not trying to kill the anvil with your hammer, you are trying to create a weapon to kill your foes with. Let me show you what you are doing wrong.' WHERE entry=3422; /* Text0_0: You are not trying to kill the anvil with your hammer, you are trying to create a weapon to kill your foes with. Let me show you what you are doing wrong. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have learned much, more than I can teach. Go to James Van Brunt, he will teach you what I cannot.' WHERE entry=3423; /* Text0_0: You have learned much, more than I can teach. Go to James Van Brunt, he will teach you what I cannot. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='E\'ko is da unfocused form of the supernatural power, and Juju is da concentrated essence. By using a stong incantation, I can transform da E\'ko into Juju.  Once it becomes Juju, you can den use the Cache of Mau\'ari ta reflect da powers onto yourself.' WHERE entry=3424; /* Text0_1: E\'ko is da unfocused form of the supernatural power, and Juju is da concentrated essence. By using a stong incantation, I can transform da E\'ko into Juju.  Once it becomes Juju, you can den use the Cache of Mau\'ari ta reflect da powers onto yourself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ah am very surprised that one wit such a careless nature has gotten dis far...$B$BYah, you may have another charm, but Mau\'ari is very displeased wit your actions!$B$BGo, now. ' WHERE entry=3425; /* Text0_1: Ah am very surprised that one wit such a careless nature has gotten dis far...$B$BYah, you may have another charm, but Mau\'ari is very displeased wit your actions!$B$BGo, now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ye have some skill about ye with hammer and anvil, but not enough. Go speak to Dane Lindgren, he\'ll get ye ready to learn what I have to teach ye.' WHERE entry=3453; /* Text0_0: Ye have some skill about ye with hammer and anvil, but not enough. Go speak to Dane Lindgren, he\'ll get ye ready to learn what I have to teach ye. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I said ye had the blood of a blacksmith in ye, and I was right. Go to Ironforge, to The Great Forge, and find yerself a Dwarven smith by the name of Bengus Deepforge. My teacher, and one of the greatest smiths I\'ve ever known.' WHERE entry=3454; /* Text0_0: I said ye had the blood of a blacksmith in ye, and I was right. Go to Ironforge, to The Great Forge, and find yerself a Dwarven smith by the name of Bengus Deepforge. My teacher, and one of the greatest smiths I\'ve ever known. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The life of a smith is not an easy one, but it puts steel in yer bones and fire in yer heart. My da\' was a smith, my grandfather before him in the forges beneath Grim Batol. And now my son follows in our footsteps, that boy makes me proud.' WHERE entry=3456; /* Text0_0: The life of a smith is not an easy one, but it puts steel in yer bones and fire in yer heart. My da\' was a smith, my grandfather before him in the forges beneath Grim Batol. And now my son follows in our footsteps, that boy makes me proud. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Sorry $g lad : lass;, ye aren\'t quite up to the challenge of learning from me. Go see my son Groum, it would make his day to get a new apprentice.' WHERE entry=3457; /* Text0_0: Sorry $g lad : lass;, ye aren\'t quite up to the challenge of learning from me. Go see my son Groum, it would make his day to get a new apprentice. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yer skill is not without merit, but I need to put one last test to ye before I take ye on.' WHERE entry=3458; /* Text0_0: Yer skill is not without merit, but I need to put one last test to ye before I take ye on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Aye, I would love ta teach ye a thing or two about smithing. Grab an apron and a hammer and let\'s see what we can accomplish shall we?' WHERE entry=3459; /* Text0_0: Aye, I would love ta teach ye a thing or two about smithing. Grab an apron and a hammer and let\'s see what we can accomplish shall we? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A fast learner is what ye are, and a good smith to boot. I would sign off on yer work any day of the week. But I sense ye still have some learnin in ye. Go talk to Bengus Deepforge, he\'s a hard taskmaster but he\'s also one of the best.' WHERE entry=3460; /* Text0_0: A fast learner is what ye are, and a good smith to boot. I would sign off on yer work any day of the week. But I sense ye still have some learnin in ye. Go talk to Bengus Deepforge, he\'s a hard taskmaster but he\'s also one of the best. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Don\'t come out of the shadows like that. Next time give a girl some warning.'Text1_1_loc9='Ever since the shadows claimed Duskwood I haven\'t been able to sleep. I am kept awake by the ghostly sounds of screaming on the breeze. It sounds almost like lambs screaming, and they won\'t stop.' WHERE entry=3461; /* Text0_1: Don\'t come out of the shadows like that. Next time give a girl some warning. */ /* Text1_1: Ever since the shadows claimed Duskwood I haven\'t been able to sleep. I am kept awake by the ghostly sounds of screaming on the breeze. It sounds almost like lambs screaming, and they won\'t stop. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Hmm, your work is allright but it\'s nowhere near the quality I look for in a student. Go talk with Smith Argus in Goldshire, I\'m sure he can teach you some basics. Then when you\'re done, come on back to me and I\'ll give you a little test to make sure you are ready.' WHERE entry=3462; /* Text0_1: Hmm, your work is allright but it\'s nowhere near the quality I look for in a student. Go talk with Smith Argus in Goldshire, I\'m sure he can teach you some basics. Then when you\'re done, come on back to me and I\'ll give you a little test to make sure you are ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Yeah, I\'ve heard through the grapevine that I might be seeing you sooner or later. But I don\'t just take on anyone, I need to make sure you have what it takes first. You willing to take my little test and find out?' WHERE entry=3463; /* Text0_1: Yeah, I\'ve heard through the grapevine that I might be seeing you sooner or later. But I don\'t just take on anyone, I need to make sure you have what it takes first. You willing to take my little test and find out? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You do fine work, but it\'s a bit rough around the edges. Don\'t worry about it, it will come with practice. Speaking of which, how about we see what you\'ve been working on?' WHERE entry=3464; /* Text0_1: You do fine work, but it\'s a bit rough around the edges. Don\'t worry about it, it will come with practice. Speaking of which, how about we see what you\'ve been working on? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Now I\'m the one who feels rough around the edges, I honestly don\'t think there\'s anything left I can teach you. But you know who can? Bengus Deepforge in Ironforge, now there\'s a dwarf that knows his steel. Go look him up in The Great Forge of Ironforge, see if he\'s up to having a new trainee under him.' WHERE entry=3465; /* Text0_1: Now I\'m the one who feels rough around the edges, I honestly don\'t think there\'s anything left I can teach you. But you know who can? Bengus Deepforge in Ironforge, now there\'s a dwarf that knows his steel. Go look him up in The Great Forge of Ironforge, see if he\'s up to having a new trainee under him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If I prove myself to Saru he will have no choice but to let me fight for one of his daughters. Then we will see who is sneering.',Text1_0_loc9='Stay away from Sumi and Tumi. They are....spoken for.' WHERE entry=3466; /* Text0_0: If I prove myself to Saru he will have no choice but to let me fight for one of his daughters. Then we will see who is sneering. */ /* Text1_0: Stay away from Sumi and Tumi. They are....spoken for. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Come to me again with such pathetic work and I will send you home in a small iron box that I tempered in goat urine. Now go see that idiot Ug\'thok, he is better suited to your needs.' WHERE entry=3467; /* Text0_0: Come to me again with such pathetic work and I will send you home in a small iron box that I tempered in goat urine. Now go see that idiot Ug\'thok, he is better suited to your needs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='So you think you are good enough to learn from me? The great Snarl? You are no more than a lowly worm beneath my boot. However, taking on an underling might make me seem more appealing to Sumi and Tumi. Let\'s see what meager skills you possess.' WHERE entry=3468; /* Text0_0: So you think you are good enough to learn from me? The great Snarl? You are no more than a lowly worm beneath my boot. However, taking on an underling might make me seem more appealing to Sumi and Tumi. Let\'s see what meager skills you possess. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have nothing left that I can learn, now get out. And don\'t even think of approaching Saru, for one as unworthy as you he will use your blood to temper his steel.' WHERE entry=3470; /* Text0_0: You have nothing left that I can learn, now get out. And don\'t even think of approaching Saru, for one as unworthy as you he will use your blood to temper his steel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The spirits have brought you to me, and so I feel blessed by them. ' WHERE entry=3471; /* Text0_0: The spirits have brought you to me, and so I feel blessed by them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You need to heed the guidance of the spirits a little better young one. Your path lies with another, Thrag Stonehoof in Thunder Bluff. Perhaps you can learn something from one another.' WHERE entry=3472; /* Text0_0: You need to heed the guidance of the spirits a little better young one. Your path lies with another, Thrag Stonehoof in Thunder Bluff. Perhaps you can learn something from one another. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Tell me, do your feel prepared to face the challenge I have laid out for you? The spirits tell me that you will pass, but do you have faith in them or in yourself?' WHERE entry=3473; /* Text0_0: Tell me, do your feel prepared to face the challenge I have laid out for you? The spirits tell me that you will pass, but do you have faith in them or in yourself? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Our paths through life intersect only briefly and now is the time for ours to part ways. I consider myself blessed to have spent this time teaching you and now send you along to join paths with your next mentor. Seek out Saru Steelfury of Orgrimmar, he will teach what you need to learn.' WHERE entry=3475; /* Text0_0: Our paths through life intersect only briefly and now is the time for ours to part ways. I consider myself blessed to have spent this time teaching you and now send you along to join paths with your next mentor. Seek out Saru Steelfury of Orgrimmar, he will teach what you need to learn. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have great potential, but you must achieve understanding first, you must accept the spirits and listen to their calling. Only then will you be prepared for the path you must follow. Go speak with Thrag, I think perhaps you can learn a lot from one another.' WHERE entry=3476; /* Text0_0: You have great potential, but you must achieve understanding first, you must accept the spirits and listen to their calling. Only then will you be prepared for the path you must follow. Go speak with Thrag, I think perhaps you can learn a lot from one another. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have learned much, but I sense that there is more left for the spirits to teach you. I can place your foot on the path but cannot guide your steps. Go and find Saru Steelfury in Orgrimmar, the next stretch of your journey begins there.' WHERE entry=3478; /* Text0_0: You have learned much, but I sense that there is more left for the spirits to teach you. I can place your foot on the path but cannot guide your steps. Go and find Saru Steelfury in Orgrimmar, the next stretch of your journey begins there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You waste my time, go talk with my student Basil.' WHERE entry=3479; /* Text0_0: You waste my time, go talk with my student Basil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Very fine equipment you make, very fine indeed. Go to the Orc\'s home of Orgrimmar and seek out a smith named Saru Steelfury. One thing you must give the Orcs, they make beautiful instruments of death.' WHERE entry=3481; /* Text0_0: Very fine equipment you make, very fine indeed. Go to the Orc\'s home of Orgrimmar and seek out a smith named Saru Steelfury. One thing you must give the Orcs, they make beautiful instruments of death. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m sorry $g lad : lass; but ye just don\'t have the foundation to learn what I have to teach. But don\'t fret, go speak with my student Rotgath, he\'ll help ye out.' WHERE entry=3482; /* Text0_0: I\'m sorry $g lad : lass; but ye just don\'t have the foundation to learn what I have to teach. But don\'t fret, go speak with my student Rotgath, he\'ll help ye out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I can\'t say enough about yer work, truly amazing things that ye can do with a hammer and an anvil. Now, don\'t be tellin anyone that I suggested ye go find a goblin to teach ye but that\'s exactly what I\'m gonna do. Brikk Keencraft is his name, and last I heard he was operating a shop down in Booty bay.' WHERE entry=3484; /* Text0_0: I can\'t say enough about yer work, truly amazing things that ye can do with a hammer and an anvil. Now, don\'t be tellin anyone that I suggested ye go find a goblin to teach ye but that\'s exactly what I\'m gonna do. Brikk Keencraft is his name, and last I heard he was operating a shop down in Booty bay. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This isn\'t a game you toy with youngling! Go, speak with Snarl outside. He may be a serpent in my lair but he does know his way around an anvil.' WHERE entry=3485; /* Text0_0: This isn\'t a game you toy with youngling! Go, speak with Snarl outside. He may be a serpent in my lair but he does know his way around an anvil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I see you know more of the secret of steel than I do. That is good, for it is meant to be taken. Now you must travel to the jungle south of the human lands, to the goblin city of Booty Bay. There you will find a Goblin named Brikk Keencraft. I do not like Goblins but his knowledge of the secret of steel is unmatched by any I know of.' WHERE entry=3487; /* Text0_0: I see you know more of the secret of steel than I do. That is good, for it is meant to be taken. Now you must travel to the jungle south of the human lands, to the goblin city of Booty Bay. There you will find a Goblin named Brikk Keencraft. I do not like Goblins but his knowledge of the secret of steel is unmatched by any I know of. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yeah? Of course I\'m a smith. What, you think Dwarves are the only ones worth their weight in anvils? Fine, be that way. Go get a dwarf to help you!' WHERE entry=3488; /* Text0_0: Yeah? Of course I\'m a smith. What, you think Dwarves are the only ones worth their weight in anvils? Fine, be that way. Go get a dwarf to help you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Are you kidding me? You must be kidding me! Either that or you think I\'m a clown here to amuse you. Is that what you think? That I\'m a clown? Huh, is it! You think I\'m a clown don\'t you!' WHERE entry=3489; /* Text0_0: Are you kidding me? You must be kidding me! Either that or you think I\'m a clown here to amuse you. Is that what you think? That I\'m a clown? Huh, is it! You think I\'m a clown don\'t you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You act like this is the best junk I\'ve ever seen. Sure it\'s ok, but I see stuff this \'OK\' every day. Tell you what, you find a way to wow me, and I\'ll teach you things that make dwarves smile in their sleep.' WHERE entry=3490; /* Text0_0: You act like this is the best junk I\'ve ever seen. Sure it\'s ok, but I see stuff this \'OK\' every day. Tell you what, you find a way to wow me, and I\'ll teach you things that make dwarves smile in their sleep. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Though I hate to admit it, the bear did get the better of me. My oh my, that\'s one big ol\' bear!$b$bNonetheless, if you can take that bear down, it\'d be a feat to be proud of! It gave more than a few of our best hunters some trouble.$b$b<He claps you on the back.>$b$bBest the bear and we\'ll accept you as a regular member of the Farstrider Lodge.' WHERE entry=3493; /* Text0_0: Though I hate to admit it, the bear did get the better of me. My oh my, that\'s one big ol\' bear!$b$bNonetheless, if you can take that bear down, it\'d be a feat to be proud of! It gave more than a few of our best hunters some trouble.$b$b<He claps you on the back.>$b$bBest the bear and we\'ll accept you as a regular member of the Farstrider Lodge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Here at the Farstrider lodge, we prize hunting skills above all else. Wish to gain my approval? You\'ll have to earn it.$B$BYou look up to the challenge, $Glad:lass;!' WHERE entry=3494; /* Text0_0: Here at the Farstrider lodge, we prize hunting skills above all else. Wish to gain my approval? You\'ll have to earn it.$B$BYou look up to the challenge, $Glad:lass;! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve become quite the hunter, $N! Not only have you proven your skills, you also bested Daryl, which gets you extra points in my book!$B$BYou\'re welcome here any time.' WHERE entry=3495; /* Text0_0: You\'ve become quite the hunter, $N! Not only have you proven your skills, you also bested Daryl, which gets you extra points in my book!$B$BYou\'re welcome here any time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='With pleasure... just let me savor this moment for a minute longer.' WHERE entry=3496; /* Text0_0: With pleasure... just let me savor this moment for a minute longer. */
