ky above?  $B$BBah!  You go take the tram then... it\'s over in Tinker Town with the rest of the gnomish contraptions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The book tells of dragons uniting against another, more powerful dragon, named Deathwing. From what you can make out, the chromatic dragonflight had almost been unleashed upon the world. The Aspects were prepared.$B' WHERE entry=3815; /* Text0_0: The book tells of dragons uniting against another, more powerful dragon, named Deathwing. From what you can make out, the chromatic dragonflight had almost been unleashed upon the world. The Aspects were prepared.$B */
