UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We don\'t have a bank here in Brill, you\'ll have to go to the Undercity for that.  At the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south are elevators that will take you down into the Undercity.  Once there ask one of the Undercity Guardians for more precise directions.',Text0_1_loc9='We don\'t have a bank here in Brill, you\'ll have to go to the Undercity for that.  At the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south are elevators that will take you down into the Undercity.  Once there ask one of the Undercity Guardians for more precise directions.',Text1_0_loc9='What could you possibly need a bank for?  Very well, you\'ll need to go through the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  In the back are a set of elevators leading down into the Undercity.  When you get there stop any of those lumbering Abominations they like to call an Undercity Guardian and ask it for better directions.',Text1_1_loc9='What could you possibly need a bank for?  Very well, you\'ll need to go through the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  In the back are a set of elevators leading down into the Undercity.  When you get there stop any of those lumbering Abominations they like to call an Undercity Guardian and ask it for better directions.' WHERE entry=4074; /* Text0_0: We don\'t have a bank here in Brill, you\'ll have to go to the Undercity for that.  At the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south are elevators that will take you down into the Undercity.  Once there ask one of the Undercity Guardians for more precise directions. */ /* Text0_1: We don\'t have a bank here in Brill, you\'ll have to go to the Undercity for that.  At the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south are elevators that will take you down into the Undercity.  Once there ask one of the Undercity Guardians for more precise directions. */ /* Text1_0: What could you possibly need a bank for?  Very well, you\'ll need to go through the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south 