UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='While there\'s no Engineering Trainer in Brill, there is one down in the Undercity.  To get there head to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of town and take the elevator down.  Once you get there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions.',Text0_1_loc9='While there\'s no Engineering Trainer in Brill, there is one down in the Undercity.  To get there head to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of town and take the elevator down.  Once you get there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions.',Text1_0_loc9='Rifles, dynamite, bombs, exploding sheep... what\'s not to love?  To learn how to make these and many other exciting tools of the trade head to the Undercity, under the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  Take the elevators down at the back of the ruins.  Once you arrive speak to one of the Undercity Guardians about where the trainer is exactly.',Text1_1_loc9='Rifles, dynamite, bombs, exploding sheep... what\'s not to love?  To learn how to make these and many other exciting tools of the trade head to the Undercity, under the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  Take the elevators down at the back of the ruins.  Once you arrive speak to one of the Undercity Guardians about where the trainer is exactly.' WHERE entry=4086; /* Text0_0: While there\'s no Engineering Trainer in Brill, there is one down in the Undercity.  To get there head to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of town and take the elevator down.  Once you get there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions. */ /* Text0_1: While there\'s no Engineering Trainer in Brill, there is one down in the Undercity.  To get there head to the back of the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of town and take the elevator down.  Once you get there ask an Undercity Guardian for more specific directions. */ /* Text1_0: Rifles, dynamite, bombs, exploding sheep... what\'s not to love?  To learn how to make these and many other exciting tools of the trade head to the Undercity, under the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  Take the elevators down at the back of the ruins.  Once you arrive speak to one of the Undercity Guardians about where the trainer is exactly. */ /* Text1_1: Rifles, dynamite, bombs, exploding sheep... what\'s not to love?  To learn how to make these and many other exciting tools of the trade head to the Undercity, under the Ruins of Lordaeron to the south of Brill.  Take the elevators down at the back of the ruins.  Once you arrive speak to one of the Undercity Guardians about where the trainer is exactly. */
