UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You\'ve already done me a great service, $N. For that I thank you.$B$BThe least I can do now is tell you what brought me here: My long time friend Trey Lightforge and I came to Jaedenar to investigate the Shadow Council when they caught us unprepared. They took Trey deeper into Shadow Hold and put me in here after taking all of our equipment... I can still hear his screams from below, $N. They were... inhuman. I don\'t know what they\'ve done to him, but they will pay for it.' WHERE entry=4113; /* Text0_1: You\'ve already done me a great service, $N. For that I thank you.$B$BThe least I can do now is tell you what brought me here: My long time friend Trey Lightforge and I came to Jaedenar to investigate the Shadow Council when they caught us unprepared. They took Trey deeper into Shadow Hold and put me in here after taking all of our equipment... I can still hear his screams from below, $N. They were... inhuman. I don\'t know what they\'ve done to him, but they will pay for it. */
