UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Strength of the body is the power and swiftness of action.  You must keep yourself fit at all times, both physically and mentally.  The bear\'s girth highlights its strength, as it is a ferocious foe in combat.  The bear\'s girth, however, belies its lithe agility and sharp mind.  These are surprises you will use to your advantage.$B$BYou must rely on the strength of the bear\'s body in order to master the way of the Claw.' WHERE entry=4733; /* Text0_0: Strength of the body is the power and swiftness of action.  You must keep yourself fit at all times, both physically and mentally.  The bear\'s girth highlights its strength, as it is a ferocious foe in combat.  The bear\'s girth, however, belies its lithe agility and sharp mind.  These are surprises you will use to your advantage.$B$BYou must rely on the strength of the bear\'s body in order to master the way of the Claw. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Strength of the heart is what gives you the resolve to take action... action that is rooted in intents that are pure and forthright.  To keep the balance is not to be complacent or banal.$B$BYou must show resolve for that which you believe in, and you must be willing to fight for it.  The mother bear shows endless conviction in protecting her young, as does an elder bear protecting his den.  It is this resolve, this strength of heart, which you must come to know if you are to master the way of the Claw.' WHERE entry=4734; /* Text0_0: Strength of the heart is what gives you the resolve to take action... action that is rooted in intents that are pure and forthright.  To keep the balance is not to be complacent or banal.$B$BYou must show resolve for that which you believe in, and you must be willing to fight for it.  The mother bear shows endless conviction in protecting her young, as does an elder bear protecting his den.  It is this resolve, this strength of heart, which you must come to know if you are to master the way of the Claw. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It remains to be seen if you are ready, young one.  Even the wisest and oldest of druids are never truly ready when their ultimate time of testing comes.$B$BYou have heard my words, and now you must move on.  Heed what I have taught you.  There will be a time when you will have your strength tested.  You must face your foe as the bear would - with strength of body and with strength of heart.  Learn from the fight, young one.  Go... with my blessings.' WHERE entry=4735; /* Text0_0: It remains to be seen if you are ready, young one.  Even the wisest and oldest of druids are never truly ready when their ultimate time of testing comes.$B$BYou have heard my words, and now you must move on.  Heed what I have taught you.  There will be a time when you will have your strength tested.  You must face your foe as the bear would - with strength of body and with strength of heart.  Learn from the fight, young one.  Go... with my blessings. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, $c.  You are welcome in Nighthaven, as well as all of Moonglade.  The Cenarion Circle welcomes all beings who respect the authority and command of nature.$B$BWhile you are here, please be sure to preserve the balance in all things.  Disturbances are not welcome here, and our wardens are trained to cease all hostilities without question.' WHERE entry=4753; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.  You are welcome in Nighthaven, as well as all of Moonglade.  The Cenarion Circle welcomes all beings who respect the authority and command of nature.$B$BWhile you are here, please be sure to preserve the balance in all things.  Disturbances are not welcome here, and our wardens are trained to cease all hostilities without question. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings $N.',Text0_1_loc9='Do you require an illusion?$B$BShould your illusion falter in the midst of your quest, return to me and I shall reapply the guise.$B$BShould you fail in your endeavors, do not give up! Return to me. I shall assist you until you have completed your objectives.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=4773; /* Text0_0: Greetings $N. */ /* Text0_1: Do you require an illusion?$B$BShould your illusion falter in the midst of your quest, return to me and I shall reapply the guise.$B$BShould you fail in your endeavors, do not give up! Return to me. I shall assist you until you have completed your objectives. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Strive to keep the balance in all things, $c.  This is where true harmony lies.' WHERE entry=4774; /* Text0_0: Strive to keep the balance in all things, $c.  This is where true harmony lies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to teach you.$B$BIt never hurts to reaffirm one\'s place within what I like to call the Great Balance.  As preservers of this balance, we must strive to continually keep our minds clear and our hearts strong.  Training helps us in this regard.' WHERE entry=4775; /* Text0_0: Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to teach you.$B$BIt never hurts to reaffirm one\'s place within what I like to call the Great Balance.  As preservers of this balance, we must strive to continually keep our minds clear and our hearts strong.  Training helps us in this regard. */
