UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The times we live in are as fickle as the shifting winds, $c.  It is important to remember what is true and lasting in this world, and to preserve that.  Everything else is a waste.' WHERE entry=4933; /* Text0_0: The times we live in are as fickle as the shifting winds, $c.  It is important to remember what is true and lasting in this world, and to preserve that.  Everything else is a waste. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='No other race on Azeroth has suffered as much as our people, $c. To laugh in the face of death has become second nature for all of us.' WHERE entry=4934; /* Text0_0: No other race on Azeroth has suffered as much as our people, $c. To laugh in the face of death has become second nature for all of us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, $N, and welcome to Camp Narache. News of your arrival spread quickly among the tribe.' WHERE entry=4935; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $N, and welcome to Camp Narache. News of your arrival spread quickly among the tribe. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, the beauty of Shadowglen never ceases to delight my senses!' WHERE entry=4936; /* Text0_0: Ah, the beauty of Shadowglen never ceases to delight my senses! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, well aren\'t you a sturdy-looking one? Perhaps you can assist me with a thing or two. Not much help around here except for green apprentices, and they\'ve other things to worry about.' WHERE entry=4937; /* Text0_0: Ah, well aren\'t you a sturdy-looking one? Perhaps you can assist me with a thing or two. Not much help around here except for green apprentices, and they\'ve other things to worry about. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hey, citizen!  You look like a stout one.  We guards are spread a little thin out here, and I could use your help...' WHERE entry=4938; /* Text0_0: Hey, citizen!  You look like a stout one.  We guards are spread a little thin out here, and I could use your help... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Because you have aided me, I will tell you what I know of this land and of the things there are to see. My knowledge is not vast, but perhaps I can point out some things that might interest one such as yourself.' WHERE entry=4953; /* Text0_0: Because you have aided me, I will tell you what I know of this land and of the things there are to see. My knowledge is not vast, but perhaps I can point out some things that might interest one such as yourself. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My knowledge of night elf lore is limited, but it is said long ago--back when the night elves still held sacred the art of arcane spell casting--that Azshara was the greatest of their kind. A beautiful woman they named queen. Sadly, it was her addiction to the arcane that would one day be the catalyst for the most devastating events in this world\'s history.' WHERE entry=4954; /* Text0_0: My knowledge of night elf lore is limited, but it is said long ago--back when the night elves still held sacred the art of arcane spell casting--that Azshara was the greatest of their kind. A beautiful woman they named queen. Sadly, it was her addiction to the arcane that would one day be the catalyst for the most devastating events in this world\'s history. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Once a great city of the night elves, the Highborne once ruled there, practicing great and powerful arcane magics. They are cursed now, haunting the lands, and their ruined city has been victimized by the Spitelash naga. I understand that the naga search the ruins for powerful Highborne artifacts.' WHERE entry=4955; /* Text0_0: Once a great city of the night elves, the Highborne once ruled there, practicing great and powerful arcane magics. They are cursed now, haunting the lands, and their ruined city has been victimized by the Spitelash naga. I understand that the naga search the ruins for powerful Highborne artifacts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A powerful human mage is rumored to live to the north; he keeps watch over the land for some unknown reason. I have not traveled there myself, but it is said that visitors are welcome and can even earn favor with him if they are willing to do errands for him.' WHERE entry=4956; /* Text0_0: A powerful human mage is rumored to live to the north; he keeps watch over the land for some unknown reason. I have not traveled there myself, but it is said that visitors are welcome and can even earn favor with him if they are willing to do errands for him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve seen terrible things happen to the furbolg over the last few years--they were victims on many fronts. But it\'s unclear to me what\'s become of this tribe. Are they corrupted by the same plague that\'s touched Felwood? Or perhaps they are simply angry at what\'s happened to their once peaceful people and now seek to defend themselves. Either way, most of them appear hostile to those who come into the area.' WHERE entry=4957; /* Text0_0: I\'ve seen terrible things happen to the furbolg over the last few years--they were victims on many fronts. But it\'s unclear to me what\'s become of this tribe. Are they corrupted by the same plague that\'s touched Felwood? Or perhaps they are simply angry at what\'s happened to their once peaceful people and now seek to defend themselves. Either way, most of them appear hostile to those who come into the area. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The blue dragons themselves aren\'t here, but followers of Malygos are. I do not know why, but I can tell you this: wherever the blue dragons are, expect to find arcane magic. I wouldn\'t be surprised if the dragonspawn are here protecting something... perhaps something the Highborne left behind.' WHERE entry=4958; /* Text0_0: The blue dragons themselves aren\'t here, but followers of Malygos are. I do not know why, but I can tell you this: wherever the blue dragons are, expect to find arcane magic. I wouldn\'t be surprised if the dragonspawn are here protecting something... perhaps something the Highborne left behind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I should find some hired help; I don\'t like sitting here all day selling fish supplies. I\'d much rather go fishing, and then sell supplies.' WHERE entry=4959; /* Text0_1: I should find some hired help; I don\'t like sitting here all day selling fish supplies. I\'d much rather go fishing, and then sell supplies. */
