UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Where are you going?  Well if you\'re looking to get there quickly, then look no further!' WHERE entry=5009; /* Text0_0: Where are you going?  Well if you\'re looking to get there quickly, then look no further! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I try to keep Sentinel Hill stocked, and that\'s not easy with all the action we see.' WHERE entry=5010; /* Text0_0: I try to keep Sentinel Hill stocked, and that\'s not easy with all the action we see. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A mere three hundred years ago, a reckless dwarf named Thaurissan summoned the master from his fiery realm. His return to this paltry world devastated the surrounding lands and created this volcanic Core. Mighty Ragnaros has slept under this mountain ever since. $B',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:' WHERE entry=5011; /* Text0_0: A mere three hundred years ago, a reckless dwarf named Thaurissan summoned the master from his fiery realm. His return to this paltry world devastated the surrounding lands and created this volcanic Core. Mighty Ragnaros has slept under this mountain ever since. $B */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We, his sworn servants, do his bidding and enforce his iron-rule. Cut off from the energies of his fiery realm, Ragnaros is but a shadow of his true self. However, he has more than enough strength to be your end.      $B',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:' WHERE entry=5012; /* Text0_0: We, his sworn servants, do his bidding and enforce his iron-rule. Cut off from the energies of his fiery realm, Ragnaros is but a shadow of his true self. However, he has more than enough strength to be your end.      $B */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Good day, $gsir:ma\'am;. I\'d shake your hand, but as you see, I\'m in the middle of something. May I be of assistance?' WHERE entry=5013; /* Text0_0: Good day, $gsir:ma\'am;. I\'d shake your hand, but as you see, I\'m in the middle of something. May I be of assistance? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve made a good start, but you still have a great deal to learn, $N.' WHERE entry=5014; /* Text0_0: You\'ve made a good start, but you still have a great deal to learn, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve already learned everything I can teach you, $N. Talk to the night elf Lilyssia Nightbreeze in the Mage Quarter of Stormwind if you want to continue your studies. I hear she\'s a good teacher.' WHERE entry=5015; /* Text0_0: You\'ve already learned everything I can teach you, $N. Talk to the night elf Lilyssia Nightbreeze in the Mage Quarter of Stormwind if you want to continue your studies. I hear she\'s a good teacher. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Shut inside this little house, I dream of joining the battles that rage outside the city walls. Still, duty compels me to share my knowledge with others who fight in my stead... for now.' WHERE entry=5016; /* Text0_1: Shut inside this little house, I dream of joining the battles that rage outside the city walls. Still, duty compels me to share my knowledge with others who fight in my stead... for now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ishnu-alah, $gbrother:sister;. Have you any tidings from abroad? My heart yearns for news of Teldrassil.' WHERE entry=5019; /* Text0_0: Ishnu-alah, $gbrother:sister;. Have you any tidings from abroad? My heart yearns for news of Teldrassil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am honored to share my knowledge with you, $N. See that you use it well.' WHERE entry=5020; /* Text0_0: I am honored to share my knowledge with you, $N. See that you use it well. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You must choose a more experienced teacher, for you have surpassed my abilities. I advise you to speak with Lilyssia Nightbreeze here: she has much knowledge to offer.' WHERE entry=5021; /* Text0_0: You must choose a more experienced teacher, for you have surpassed my abilities. I advise you to speak with Lilyssia Nightbreeze here: she has much knowledge to offer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The druids say that it is only a matter of time until nature itself drives the Horde from Kalimdor. Yet corruption continues to spread throughout our lands, even here on Teldrassil.' WHERE entry=5022; /* Text0_1: The druids say that it is only a matter of time until nature itself drives the Horde from Kalimdor. Yet corruption continues to spread throughout our lands, even here on Teldrassil. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Well done! Your understanding of potions is coming along nicely.' WHERE entry=5023; /* Text0_1: Well done! Your understanding of potions is coming along nicely. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Unfortunately, there is little I can teach someone with your experience, my friend. Seek out the night elf Sylvanna Forestmoon, who resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.' WHERE entry=5024; /* Text0_1: Unfortunately, there is little I can teach someone with your experience, my friend. Seek out the night elf Sylvanna Forestmoon, who resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Elune-adore, my $gbrother:sister;. You are welcome here. Speak, and I will do what I can to aid you.' WHERE entry=5025; /* Text0_1: Elune-adore, my $gbrother:sister;. You are welcome here. Speak, and I will do what I can to aid you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Is it not astonishing what one can create from the plants of the forest? Truly, Elune has blessed us with her bounty.' WHERE entry=5026; /* Text0_1: Is it not astonishing what one can create from the plants of the forest? Truly, Elune has blessed us with her bounty. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You are kind to seek me out, but your skills are beyond my own. Have a word with Sylvanna Forestmoon, just over there. She\'s been looking for another student.' WHERE entry=5027; /* Text0_1: You are kind to seek me out, but your skills are beyond my own. Have a word with Sylvanna Forestmoon, just over there. She\'s been looking for another student. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Did my sweet lass Kali send you down to me? The apple of my eye, she is.' WHERE entry=5028; /* Text0_0: Did my sweet lass Kali send you down to me? The apple of my eye, she is. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I don\'t suppose you\'re here to talk about my lovely Kali. Fine, then. Potions it is. Anyone ever tell ye you\'ve got a one-track mind?' WHERE entry=5029; /* Text0_0: I don\'t suppose you\'re here to talk about my lovely Kali. Fine, then. Potions it is. Anyone ever tell ye you\'ve got a one-track mind? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ye\'re beyond my skill to teach, $N. Go pester Tally Berryfizz; she\'s a gnome living in Tinker Town of Ironforge. Oh, and since you\'re headed up anyway, give Kali my love.' WHERE entry=5030; /* Text0_0: Ye\'re beyond my skill to teach, $N. Go pester Tally Berryfizz; she\'s a gnome living in Tinker Town of Ironforge. Oh, and since you\'re headed up anyway, give Kali my love. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t let those big, innocent eyes fool ye. Tally\'s an expert, all right: I learn something new every day. Why d\'you think I\'m here in Tinker Town? Do I look like an engineer to you? Aye, I didn\'t think so.' WHERE entry=5031; /* Text0_0: Don\'t let those big, innocent eyes fool ye. Tally\'s an expert, all right: I learn something new every day. Why d\'you think I\'m here in Tinker Town? Do I look like an engineer to you? Aye, I didn\'t think so. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Put your back into it, $glad:lass;. Hard work and determination--that\'s the way! Don\'t let anyone tell you book learnin\' is all ye need.' WHERE entry=5032; /* Text0_0: Put your back into it, $glad:lass;. Hard work and determination--that\'s the way! Don\'t let anyone tell you book learnin\' is all ye need. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Och, there\'s nothing I can teach ye, $N. Have a word with Tally Berryfizz over there. She can hardly reach the tables, but when she starts brewing a potion, watch out!' WHERE entry=5033; /* Text0_0: Och, there\'s nothing I can teach ye, $N. Have a word with Tally Berryfizz over there. She can hardly reach the tables, but when she starts brewing a potion, watch out! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You got the look of someone wantin\' adventure. Me, I had enough of that by the time we trolls came here. Now I take each day as it comes, an\' I train other folks to handle adventures for me.' WHERE entry=5034; /* Text0_0: You got the look of someone wantin\' adventure. Me, I had enough of that by the time we trolls came here. Now I take each day as it comes, an\' I train other folks to handle adventures for me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ready for another lesson? All right, then. First, relax. You gotta stay loose to stir a potion just right.' WHERE entry=5035; /* Text0_0: Ready for another lesson? All right, then. First, relax. You gotta stay loose to stir a potion just right. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You got questions, but they be too big for me to answer, $N. You be needin\' to have words with the orc Yelmak in the Drag of Orgrimmar. He\'ll help you out.' WHERE entry=5036; /* Text0_0: You got questions, but they be too big for me to answer, $N. You be needin\' to have words with the orc Yelmak in the Drag of Orgrimmar. He\'ll help you out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='All the bottles on this table are potions I brewed today. And they say a watched pot never boils. Ha!' WHERE entry=5037; /* Text0_0: All the bottles on this table are potions I brewed today. And they say a watched pot never boils. Ha! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='They called me stupid, but I\'ll show them. I\'m going to watch every pot I have and prove that they can all boil stuff anyway. Yeah, I\'m on a roll! Who\'s stupid now, huh? Huh!?' WHERE entry=5038; /* Text0_0: They called me stupid, but I\'ll show them. I\'m going to watch every pot I have and prove that they can all boil stuff anyway. Yeah, I\'m on a roll! Who\'s stupid now, huh? Huh!? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Can\'t help you. You know more about potions than I do. Besides, I have pots to watch. Talk to Yelmak over there. He knows a lot about potions.' WHERE entry=5039; /* Text0_0: Can\'t help you. You know more about potions than I do. Besides, I have pots to watch. Talk to Yelmak over there. He knows a lot about potions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Bena works like one possessed. Day and night I have seen her bent over these potions, often going without sleep or food. I know our undead allies need help, but I begin to fear she will do herself an injury.' WHERE entry=5040; /* Text0_0: Bena works like one possessed. Day and night I have seen her bent over these potions, often going without sleep or food. I know our undead allies need help, but I begin to fear she will do herself an injury. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I must have broken hundreds of vials when I first began brewing potions. The glass was so fragile in my clumsy hands. I hope you are more cautious than I was.' WHERE entry=5041; /* Text0_0: I must have broken hundreds of vials when I first began brewing potions. The glass was so fragile in my clumsy hands. I hope you are more cautious than I was. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your capacity for learning has outstripped mine. You will need to talk to Bena Winterhoof over there for further instruction. Please don\'t take too much of her time, though. She needs her rest.' WHERE entry=5042; /* Text0_0: Your capacity for learning has outstripped mine. You will need to talk to Bena Winterhoof over there for further instruction. Please don\'t take too much of her time, though. She needs her rest. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Nice to see a friendly face. I don\'t get much chitchat from Apothecary Johaan unless he wants something. He\'s been out of the grave too long. Someday I\'ll be like that, I hear. Creepy. Maybe by then I won\'t care.' WHERE entry=5043; /* Text0_1: Nice to see a friendly face. I don\'t get much chitchat from Apothecary Johaan unless he wants something. He\'s been out of the grave too long. Someday I\'ll be like that, I hear. Creepy. Maybe by then I won\'t care. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Here to learn about potions? I\'ve got plenty to teach you. I might be dead, but I haven\'t lost my brains. Yet.' WHERE entry=5044; /* Text0_1: Here to learn about potions? I\'ve got plenty to teach you. I might be dead, but I haven\'t lost my brains. Yet. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I appreciate the company, but let\'s face it: you have more experience with potions than I do. Talk to Doctor Marsh instead if you want training. He\'s a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.' WHERE entry=5045; /* Text0_1: I appreciate the company, but let\'s face it: you have more experience with potions than I do. Talk to Doctor Marsh instead if you want training. He\'s a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Once, it is true, I was human. What might otherwise be a shortcoming works to our advantage, $N, for I know human weaknesses intimately.' WHERE entry=5046; /* Text0_0: Once, it is true, I was human. What might otherwise be a shortcoming works to our advantage, $N, for I know human weaknesses intimately. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Very well. Cut another lump of flesh from one of these specimens. Let us test what you\'ve learned so far, and we can progress from there.' WHERE entry=5047; /* Text0_0: Very well. Cut another lump of flesh from one of these specimens. Let us test what you\'ve learned so far, and we can progress from there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your knowledge of potions has exceeded mine, but you still have much to learn. Go up the stairs to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. He will teach you true sufferi--ahem. He is a Forsaken who will train you further.' WHERE entry=5048; /* Text0_0: Your knowledge of potions has exceeded mine, but you still have much to learn. Go up the stairs to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. He will teach you true sufferi--ahem. He is a Forsaken who will train you further. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Stop giving me that look. I may not be an adventurer like you, but that doesn\'t mean I can\'t have a few muscles. All that stirring makes your arms strong.' WHERE entry=5049; /* Text0_0: Stop giving me that look. I may not be an adventurer like you, but that doesn\'t mean I can\'t have a few muscles. All that stirring makes your arms strong. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There\'s nothing more I can teach you. I\'ve heard of a night elf who might be able to, though. Her name is Ainethil, and she lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.' WHERE entry=5050; /* Text0_0: There\'s nothing more I can teach you. I\'ve heard of a night elf who might be able to, though. Her name is Ainethil, and she lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m sorry, $N, but I have no time to spend on novices. You want someone closer to your own skill level. Try the night elf Milla Fairancora, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.' WHERE entry=5051; /* Text0_0: I\'m sorry, $N, but I have no time to spend on novices. You want someone closer to your own skill level. Try the night elf Milla Fairancora, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You want my help? You got it. What do you need?' WHERE entry=5053; /* Text0_0: You want my help? You got it. What do you need? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Don\'t let the beady eyes and bushy beard fool you. Vosur\'s a talented apprentice and a good friend, even if I do get a crick in my neck when I talk to him.' WHERE entry=5054; /* Text0_1: Don\'t let the beady eyes and bushy beard fool you. Vosur\'s a talented apprentice and a good friend, even if I do get a crick in my neck when I talk to him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Um, you already know everything I could teach you. Maybe it\'s time for you to talk to someone else. Try the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She\'s got some real talent!' WHERE entry=5055; /* Text0_1: Um, you already know everything I could teach you. Maybe it\'s time for you to talk to someone else. Try the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She\'s got some real talent! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='That\'s nice, $N. Go show whatever it is to Vosur over there. He\'ll answer any questions you have.' WHERE entry=5057; /* Text0_1: That\'s nice, $N. Go show whatever it is to Vosur over there. He\'ll answer any questions you have. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Who are you and why are you bothering me? Oh, right--potions student. Right. What can I do for you?' WHERE entry=5058; /* Text0_1: Who are you and why are you bothering me? Oh, right--potions student. Right. What can I do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ishnu-dal-dieb, $N. Have you come here in search of knowledge?' WHERE entry=5059; /* Text0_1: Ishnu-dal-dieb, $N. Have you come here in search of knowledge? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Teaching is not a one-sided trade, $N. As I teach you, I learn more myself, and my understanding grows.' WHERE entry=5060; /* Text0_1: Teaching is not a one-sided trade, $N. As I teach you, I learn more myself, and my understanding grows. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Although I am flattered by your confidence in my abilities, teaching you is beyond my skill. You must go to the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus, and speak with the night elf Ainethil. She can help you.' WHERE entry=5063; /* Text0_1: Although I am flattered by your confidence in my abilities, teaching you is beyond my skill. You must go to the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus, and speak with the night elf Ainethil. She can help you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Even slight alterations to a potion\'s ingredients can change it fundamentally. Patience and precision, young one: they will serve you well in all walks of life.' WHERE entry=5064; /* Text0_1: Even slight alterations to a potion\'s ingredients can change it fundamentally. Patience and precision, young one: they will serve you well in all walks of life. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='My skill at creating potions is inferior to yours. You are ready to speak with Ainethil, just over there. She will understand that you are ready for further instruction.' WHERE entry=5065; /* Text0_1: My skill at creating potions is inferior to yours. You are ready to speak with Ainethil, just over there. She will understand that you are ready for further instruction. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ah, to be young again, and to have discovered potions for the first time. Thank you for refreshing my memory, $N. Now go share that youthful enthusiasm with Milla Fairancora over there.' WHERE entry=5067; /* Text0_1: Ah, to be young again, and to have discovered potions for the first time. Thank you for refreshing my memory, $N. Now go share that youthful enthusiasm with Milla Fairancora over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I have learned much of potions over the long years, $N, and that knowledge is at your disposal. You have only to ask.' WHERE entry=5068; /* Text0_1: I have learned much of potions over the long years, $N, and that knowledge is at your disposal. You have only to ask. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m busy, $N. Tell Whuut to handle whatever it is. That young pup has been stewing all day long. He spends much more time like that, and he\'s going to hurt something.' WHERE entry=5069; /* Text0_0: I\'m busy, $N. Tell Whuut to handle whatever it is. That young pup has been stewing all day long. He spends much more time like that, and he\'s going to hurt something. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m honored to meet you, $N, but your skill at potions is greater than my own. Go see Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He can help you from now on.' WHERE entry=5070; /* Text0_0: I\'m honored to meet you, $N, but your skill at potions is greater than my own. Go see Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He can help you from now on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re talking to the wrong orc. I don\'t train novices. Talk to young Whuut over there... and use small words.' WHERE entry=5072; /* Text0_0: You\'re talking to the wrong orc. I don\'t train novices. Talk to young Whuut over there... and use small words. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Another student, eh? All right. I\'ll see what I can do to help you out.' WHERE entry=5073; /* Text0_0: Another student, eh? All right. I\'ll see what I can do to help you out. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Glyx and I have an understanding: he keeps me supplied, and I keep him rich. Seriously! What that pirate charges me for a measly pouch of crumpled kingsblood... it\'s enough to make a grown goblin cry.' WHERE entry=5074; /* Text0_0: Glyx and I have an understanding: he keeps me supplied, and I keep him rich. Seriously! What that pirate charges me for a measly pouch of crumpled kingsblood... it\'s enough to make a grown goblin cry. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve got plenty of great recipes for you to take a look at, and at discounted prices, too!' WHERE entry=5075; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got plenty of great recipes for you to take a look at, and at discounted prices, too! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Ainethil, a night elf lady who lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.' WHERE entry=5078; /* Text0_0: You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Ainethil, a night elf lady who lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='When I first saw the undead, I wept, for I could not imagine their horror and loneliness. The Earth Mother spoke to me then; she sang in my blood. And she told me, "Save them."' WHERE entry=5079; /* Text0_1: When I first saw the undead, I wept, for I could not imagine their horror and loneliness. The Earth Mother spoke to me then; she sang in my blood. And she told me, "Save them." */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Can you not sense the anguish of the Earth Mother for her lost children, the undead? Speak quickly, $N. Every second costs me dearly. We must help them find their way back to her!' WHERE entry=5080; /* Text0_1: Can you not sense the anguish of the Earth Mother for her lost children, the undead? Speak quickly, $N. Every second costs me dearly. We must help them find their way back to her! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I cannot in good conscience spend time training novices while our allies, the undead, are suffering so terribly. Please speak with Kray over there instead; he can help you for now.' WHERE entry=5081; /* Text0_1: I cannot in good conscience spend time training novices while our allies, the undead, are suffering so terribly. Please speak with Kray over there instead; he can help you for now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Your potion-making skills are beyond mine. Seek out the undead Doctor Herbert Halsey in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He has the skill to train you further, and you can witness firsthand his people\'s plight.' WHERE entry=5083; /* Text0_1: Your potion-making skills are beyond mine. Seek out the undead Doctor Herbert Halsey in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He has the skill to train you further, and you can witness firsthand his people\'s plight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Another interruption. How am I supposed to get any work done like this? Don\'t answer that; do I look as if I care what you have to say? Why don\'t you go bother Mr. High-And-Mighty instead?' WHERE entry=5084; /* Text0_0: Another interruption. How am I supposed to get any work done like this? Don\'t answer that; do I look as if I care what you have to say? Why don\'t you go bother Mr. High-And-Mighty instead? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Me, train you? Come on--we both know I can\'t. It\'s this teaching, you see. My own skills suffer. You want training, go to Doctor Herbert Halsey, a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.' WHERE entry=5085; /* Text0_0: Me, train you? Come on--we both know I can\'t. It\'s this teaching, you see. My own skills suffer. You want training, go to Doctor Herbert Halsey, a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t waste my time. I have research projects older than you. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He\'s a Forsaken who can probably manage to teach you the basics.' WHERE entry=5087; /* Text0_0: Don\'t waste my time. I have research projects older than you. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He\'s a Forsaken who can probably manage to teach you the basics. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Another student. Wonderful. This is why Lydon belongs to the Royal Society of Snobs and gets to do research, and I\'m stuck being an instructor. If I win another teaching award, I\'ll never live it down!' WHERE entry=5088; /* Text0_0: Another student. Wonderful. This is why Lydon belongs to the Royal Society of Snobs and gets to do research, and I\'m stuck being an instructor. If I win another teaching award, I\'ll never live it down! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='With Algernon to keep me supplied, I can do all my work here without hunting for a single herb. If I never have to see the wonders of nature again, it won\'t be too soon.' WHERE entry=5089; /* Text0_0: With Algernon to keep me supplied, I can do all my work here without hunting for a single herb. If I never have to see the wonders of nature again, it won\'t be too soon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I have no more knowledge to bestow upon you. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Herbert Halsey. He is a Forsaken who can teach you more advanced techniques.' WHERE entry=5090; /* Text0_0: I have no more knowledge to bestow upon you. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Herbert Halsey. He is a Forsaken who can teach you more advanced techniques. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m not amused by your audacity in coming to me for training. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Martin Felben. He is a Forsaken who can teach you the basics.' WHERE entry=5092; /* Text0_0: I\'m not amused by your audacity in coming to me for training. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Martin Felben. He is a Forsaken who can teach you the basics. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Here to learn? Very well. I suppose you can\'t cause our allies much harm if I teach you. Just as long as you actually do manage to harm our enemies.' WHERE entry=5093; /* Text0_0: Here to learn? Very well. I suppose you can\'t cause our allies much harm if I teach you. Just as long as you actually do manage to harm our enemies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what.' WHERE entry=5094; /* Text0_1: This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further.' WHERE entry=5095; /* Text0_1: It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there.' WHERE entry=5097; /* Text0_1: Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments.' WHERE entry=5098; /* Text0_1: Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My colleagues and I are gathering the deadliest substances we know and testing their effects on our enemies. Once I have everything I need, I shall brew such plagues as this world has never seen.' WHERE entry=5099; /* Text0_0: My colleagues and I are gathering the deadliest substances we know and testing their effects on our enemies. Once I have everything I need, I shall brew such plagues as this world has never seen. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Incredible. Your potions display a knowledge that rivals my own. I cannot train you further, but talk to the orc Rogvar of Stonard in the Swamp of Sorrows. He\'s known for his cutting-edge experiments.' WHERE entry=5100; /* Text0_0: Incredible. Your potions display a knowledge that rivals my own. I cannot train you further, but talk to the orc Rogvar of Stonard in the Swamp of Sorrows. He\'s known for his cutting-edge experiments. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You don\'t yet have the skill to study with me. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben over there, or go up the ramp to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. They are Forsaken who can give you the training you need.' WHERE entry=5102; /* Text0_0: You don\'t yet have the skill to study with me. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben over there, or go up the ramp to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. They are Forsaken who can give you the training you need. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ready for training? Then try to keep up, $N. We\'ve got a lot of ground to cover.' WHERE entry=5103; /* Text0_0: Ready for training? Then try to keep up, $N. We\'ve got a lot of ground to cover. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world.' WHERE entry=5104; /* Text0_1: Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill.' WHERE entry=5105; /* Text0_1: Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content.' WHERE entry=5106; /* Text0_1: Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Warchief Thrall himself asked me to come out here. I was honored to obey, and it\'s no hardship. I couldn\'t have asked for a better posting than Stonard. Just about any herb I might need grows in the muck here.' WHERE entry=5108; /* Text0_0: Warchief Thrall himself asked me to come out here. I was honored to obey, and it\'s no hardship. I couldn\'t have asked for a better posting than Stonard. Just about any herb I might need grows in the muck here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hmm, well, I can see that you have a little skill at making potions. Whether you\'re worthy to be my student remains to be seen, however. I have a job for you. Impress me.' WHERE entry=5110; /* Text0_0: Hmm, well, I can see that you have a little skill at making potions. Whether you\'re worthy to be my student remains to be seen, however. I have a job for you. Impress me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='How dare you ask me for training, maggot? What were you hoping for, you slack-jawed yokel, a lecture on the proper uses of silverleaf? Out! You\'re lucky I don\'t thrash you senseless for wasting my time.' WHERE entry=5111; /* Text0_0: How dare you ask me for training, maggot? What were you hoping for, you slack-jawed yokel, a lecture on the proper uses of silverleaf? Out! You\'re lucky I don\'t thrash you senseless for wasting my time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Just a minor adjustment here... ah there we go!' WHERE entry=5112; /* Text0_0: Just a minor adjustment here... ah there we go! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I would train ye if I could, but ye need the services of someone a bit more... what\'s the word? Brainy! Look for Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge. Tell \'er Bronk sent ye!' WHERE entry=5113; /* Text0_0: I would train ye if I could, but ye need the services of someone a bit more... what\'s the word? Brainy! Look for Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge. Tell \'er Bronk sent ye! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Lookin\' to be an engineer, eh? Well, by Muradin, ye\'ve come to the right place!' WHERE entry=5114; /* Text0_0: Lookin\' to be an engineer, eh? Well, by Muradin, ye\'ve come to the right place! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Where\'s my spinner? I just had it here somewhere...' WHERE entry=5115; /* Text0_0: Where\'s my spinner? I just had it here somewhere... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your current aptitude exceeds my instructional capabilities. You should enquire further with my fellow Gnome Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge!' WHERE entry=5116; /* Text0_0: Your current aptitude exceeds my instructional capabilities. You should enquire further with my fellow Gnome Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I would be delighted to aid you in the commencement of your pursuit! Let me grab my spinner and we\'ll get started...' WHERE entry=5117; /* Text0_0: I would be delighted to aid you in the commencement of your pursuit! Let me grab my spinner and we\'ll get started... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I heard the new Henweigh 6000 will be rolling off the assembly line soon. I can barely contain my excitement!' WHERE entry=5118; /* Text0_1: I heard the new Henweigh 6000 will be rolling off the assembly line soon. I can barely contain my excitement! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Well... I hate to admit it, but my sister\'s the one you\'ll have to talk to if you want to continue training. I don\'t know as much as she does... yet! She\'s standing over by the rocket car.' WHERE entry=5119; /* Text0_1: Well... I hate to admit it, but my sister\'s the one you\'ll have to talk to if you want to continue training. I don\'t know as much as she does... yet! She\'s standing over by the rocket car. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I\'d love to teach you! Show my sister she\'s not the only one who knows a thing or two about engineering...' WHERE entry=5120; /* Text0_1: I\'d love to teach you! Show my sister she\'s not the only one who knows a thing or two about engineering... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Hello there! My name\'s Jenna! And you?' WHERE entry=5121; /* Text0_1: Hello there! My name\'s Jenna! And you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Oh, you\'ve got oodles of things to learn still. I would teach you everything if I could, but I\'m still learning too! Why don\'t you talk to Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge, she\'ll help you further your education!' WHERE entry=5122; /* Text0_1: Oh, you\'ve got oodles of things to learn still. I would teach you everything if I could, but I\'m still learning too! Why don\'t you talk to Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge, she\'ll help you further your education! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You want to train? With me? Fantastic! The only thing better than assembling bullets and explosive devices is to share that knowledge with someone else! Let\'s get started!' WHERE entry=5123; /* Text0_1: You want to train? With me? Fantastic! The only thing better than assembling bullets and explosive devices is to share that knowledge with someone else! Let\'s get started! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ah, what a beautiful day to blow something up!' WHERE entry=5124; /* Text0_1: Ah, what a beautiful day to blow something up! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You need to start learning things that are beyond my expertise! Talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in front of the tent there. He\'ll set you on the right course!' WHERE entry=5125; /* Text0_1: You need to start learning things that are beyond my expertise! Talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in front of the tent there. He\'ll set you on the right course! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='This kind of work isn\'t for the faint of heart. I have an uncle who lost a hand! Poor old Stumpy... anyway, if you\'re still interested I might be able to show you a few things.' WHERE entry=5126; /* Text0_1: This kind of work isn\'t for the faint of heart. I have an uncle who lost a hand! Poor old Stumpy... anyway, if you\'re still interested I might be able to show you a few things. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What? You want something?' WHERE entry=5127; /* Text0_0: What? You want something? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I can\'t help ya\'! You\'re ready to see someone who\'s been at it longer than I have! Let\'s see... you\'re an Alliance type, so you need to talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in Stormwind.' WHERE entry=5128; /* Text0_0: I can\'t help ya\'! You\'re ready to see someone who\'s been at it longer than I have! Let\'s see... you\'re an Alliance type, so you need to talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in Stormwind. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yeah, I\'ll show you a few things. We\'ll see how you do, maybe you\'ll surprise me!' WHERE entry=5129; /* Text0_0: Yeah, I\'ll show you a few things. We\'ll see how you do, maybe you\'ll surprise me! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='(Sniff, sniff) You smell that? Don\'t you just LOVE the smell of grease?' WHERE entry=5130; /* Text0_0: (Sniff, sniff) You smell that? Don\'t you just LOVE the smell of grease? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m afraid you\'re out of my league, friend! You should go see Nogg in Orgrimmar, he\'ll take you to the next level!' WHERE entry=5131; /* Text0_0: I\'m afraid you\'re out of my league, friend! You should go see Nogg in Orgrimmar, he\'ll take you to the next level! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I like to build stuff. Of course, I like to blow stuff up even more!' WHERE entry=5133; /* Text0_0: I like to build stuff. Of course, I like to blow stuff up even more! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You know who can really show you some things? Nogg! You go find him in Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=5134; /* Text0_0: You know who can really show you some things? Nogg! You go find him in Orgrimmar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I know a few things. You want me to show you?' WHERE entry=5135; /* Text0_0: I know a few things. You want me to show you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Who says Orcs aren\'t smart? It takes a lot of brains to be an engineer!' WHERE entry=5136; /* Text0_0: Who says Orcs aren\'t smart? It takes a lot of brains to be an engineer! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You know who\'s really smart? Nogg! Smarter than me, even. You go tell Nogg Thund sent you! You can find him by the control panel over there.' WHERE entry=5137; /* Text0_0: You know who\'s really smart? Nogg! Smarter than me, even. You go tell Nogg Thund sent you! You can find him by the control panel over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You think you\'re smart enough? You think you got what it takes? Let\'s find out!' WHERE entry=5138; /* Text0_0: You think you\'re smart enough? You think you got what it takes? Let\'s find out! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Dark Lady has said that knowledge will be our greatest weapon in this war.' WHERE entry=5139; /* Text0_0: The Dark Lady has said that knowledge will be our greatest weapon in this war. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are ready for greater things! See Franklin Lloyd, to my right. He will guide you from now on.' WHERE entry=5140; /* Text0_0: You are ready for greater things! See Franklin Lloyd, to my right. He will guide you from now on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Engineering will provide you with the skills and knowledge to dismantle your opponents! Let me show you how...' WHERE entry=5141; /* Text0_0: Engineering will provide you with the skills and knowledge to dismantle your opponents! Let me show you how... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m never too busy to speak to a stranger! Almost never, anyway...' WHERE entry=5142; /* Text0_0: I\'m never too busy to speak to a stranger! Almost never, anyway... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re working your way up??? higher than me, at this point! You should talk to Springspindle Fizzlegear in Ironforge! (He\'ll? She\'ll?) show you more than I ever could!' WHERE entry=5143; /* Text0_0: You\'re working your way up??? higher than me, at this point! You should talk to Springspindle Fizzlegear in Ironforge! (He\'ll? She\'ll?) show you more than I ever could! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I can show you a few tricks... if you don\'t mind doing a little something first, that is.' WHERE entry=5144; /* Text0_0: I can show you a few tricks... if you don\'t mind doing a little something first, that is. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hmm well, I can\'t help you quite yet! You have to learn the basics first. Why don\'t you go see Sprite Jumpsprocket in Stormwind!' WHERE entry=5145; /* Text0_0: Hmm well, I can\'t help you quite yet! You have to learn the basics first. Why don\'t you go see Sprite Jumpsprocket in Stormwind! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Fantastic! Aren\'t you the industrious one? Well, let\'s get started, shall we?' WHERE entry=5146; /* Text0_0: Fantastic! Aren\'t you the industrious one? Well, let\'s get started, shall we? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Let\'s see... fourteen plus seven, carry the two... oh, yes?' WHERE entry=5147; /* Text0_0: Let\'s see... fourteen plus seven, carry the two... oh, yes? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well, you\'re just zooming right along! I can\'t teach you anything you don\'t already know, but Springspindle Fizzlegear sure can! You can find Sprinspindle in Ironforge. Good luck!' WHERE entry=5148; /* Text0_0: Well, you\'re just zooming right along! I can\'t teach you anything you don\'t already know, but Springspindle Fizzlegear sure can! You can find Sprinspindle in Ironforge. Good luck! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Quid pro quo! I\'ll teach you what I know, but first I want you to perform a small task?' WHERE entry=5149; /* Text0_0: Quid pro quo! I\'ll teach you what I know, but first I want you to perform a small task? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You can learn from me in time, but not yet! Why don\'t you start out by talking to Sprite Jumpsprocket to my right here. You can check in with me after you\'ve gotten your feet wet!' WHERE entry=5150; /* Text0_0: You can learn from me in time, but not yet! Why don\'t you start out by talking to Sprite Jumpsprocket to my right here. You can check in with me after you\'ve gotten your feet wet! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You certainly did not disappoint! Now that we\'ve gotten that out of the way, your instruction may begin!' WHERE entry=5151; /* Text0_0: You certainly did not disappoint! Now that we\'ve gotten that out of the way, your instruction may begin! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The plans for my twenty-foot tall turkey baster are nearly complete! Now all I need is a twenty-foot tall turkey...' WHERE entry=5152; /* Text0_1: The plans for my twenty-foot tall turkey baster are nearly complete! Now all I need is a twenty-foot tall turkey... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Don\'t tell anyone else I said this, but even I don\'t know everything! If you want to keep learning, you should talk to the owner of the shop, Springspindle Fizzlegear.' WHERE entry=5153; /* Text0_1: Don\'t tell anyone else I said this, but even I don\'t know everything! If you want to keep learning, you should talk to the owner of the shop, Springspindle Fizzlegear. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You\'ll need to prove your worthiness before I go giving away my secrets! I\'ve got just the test for you...' WHERE entry=5154; /* Text0_1: You\'ll need to prove your worthiness before I go giving away my secrets! I\'ve got just the test for you... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Close, but no cigar! I\'m afraid you\'ll have to talk to my sis, Jemma first. After she\'s gone over the basics with you, come see me and I\'ll show you the juicy stuff!' WHERE entry=5155; /* Text0_1: Close, but no cigar! I\'m afraid you\'ll have to talk to my sis, Jemma first. After she\'s gone over the basics with you, come see me and I\'ll show you the juicy stuff! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Not bad, for a beginner! I guess it couldn\'t hurt for me to show you a few things...' WHERE entry=5156; /* Text0_1: Not bad, for a beginner! I guess it couldn\'t hurt for me to show you a few things... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If there were just a few more hours in a day...' WHERE entry=5157; /* Text0_0: If there were just a few more hours in a day... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have earned the privilege of training with a higher instructor. Go see my pal Roxxik there.' WHERE entry=5158; /* Text0_0: You have earned the privilege of training with a higher instructor. Go see my pal Roxxik there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Every day is a test, and this day is no different. If you pass this test, I will share some of my knowledge...' WHERE entry=5159; /* Text0_0: Every day is a test, and this day is no different. If you pass this test, I will share some of my knowledge... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have not yet earned the right to train with me. See Thund first, over by the table. Come back when he says you\'re ready!' WHERE entry=5160; /* Text0_0: You have not yet earned the right to train with me. See Thund first, over by the table. Come back when he says you\'re ready! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have passed your test, well done! Your training may now continue.' WHERE entry=5161; /* Text0_0: You have passed your test, well done! Your training may now continue. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I don\'t have time for idle gossip, I\'m a professional!' WHERE entry=5162; /* Text0_0: I don\'t have time for idle gossip, I\'m a professional! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What do you think I could teach you? Roxxik would do a much better job. You can find him in Orgrimmar. Now be off!' WHERE entry=5163; /* Text0_0: What do you think I could teach you? Roxxik would do a much better job. You can find him in Orgrimmar. Now be off! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Let\'s see how competent you are, shall we? If you perform this task to my liking, I\'ll spend the time to teach you!' WHERE entry=5164; /* Text0_0: Let\'s see how competent you are, shall we? If you perform this task to my liking, I\'ll spend the time to teach you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This is a waste of time, mine and yours! Go see Graham Van Talen if you want to begin your instruction! He\'s standing to my left over there.' WHERE entry=5165; /* Text0_0: This is a waste of time, mine and yours! Go see Graham Van Talen if you want to begin your instruction! He\'s standing to my left over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If my calculations are correct, the wheel will soon be obsolete!' WHERE entry=5167; /* Text0_0: If my calculations are correct, the wheel will soon be obsolete! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have certainly come a long way in your training. There is only one instructor who can train you further. Find Buzzek Bracketswing in Gadgetzan!' WHERE entry=5168; /* Text0_0: You have certainly come a long way in your training. There is only one instructor who can train you further. Find Buzzek Bracketswing in Gadgetzan! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The things I would teach you would turn your brain to jelly! Come back when you\'ve learned sufficiently!' WHERE entry=5170; /* Text0_0: The things I would teach you would turn your brain to jelly! Come back when you\'ve learned sufficiently! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Excellent, you have proven yourself worthy! Now for the next phase of your instruction...' WHERE entry=5171; /* Text0_0: Excellent, you have proven yourself worthy! Now for the next phase of your instruction... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Sometimes I surprise even myself!' WHERE entry=5172; /* Text0_0: Sometimes I surprise even myself! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I can\'t teach what I don\'t know! If only there was someone else who knew more than I do... wait, there is! Go see Buzzek Bracketswing in Gadgetzan!' WHERE entry=5173; /* Text0_0: I can\'t teach what I don\'t know! If only there was someone else who knew more than I do... wait, there is! Go see Buzzek Bracketswing in Gadgetzan! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Nice try, but you\'ll need some more experience before training with me! Back to the trenches!' WHERE entry=5175; /* Text0_0: Nice try, but you\'ll need some more experience before training with me! Back to the trenches! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Nice going! I knew I was right about you, no matter what those other people said. Ha! I\'m kidding! Okay, on with your lessons.' WHERE entry=5176; /* Text0_0: Nice going! I knew I was right about you, no matter what those other people said. Ha! I\'m kidding! Okay, on with your lessons. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve been working on a way to transport oil underground between major cities, but everyone tells me it\'s a pipe dream.' WHERE entry=5177; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been working on a way to transport oil underground between major cities, but everyone tells me it\'s a pipe dream. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Show me what you got! You won\'t be sorry, I promise!' WHERE entry=5179; /* Text0_0: Show me what you got! You won\'t be sorry, I promise! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I would never turn away someone who\'s ready to train with me. Unfortunately, you\'re not! You\'ve still got a ways to go kid!' WHERE entry=5180; /* Text0_0: I would never turn away someone who\'s ready to train with me. Unfortunately, you\'re not! You\'ve still got a ways to go kid! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Hail, traveler! What brings you to my doorstep?' WHERE entry=5181; /* Text0_1: Hail, traveler! What brings you to my doorstep? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I\'m afraid I have nothing to teach to someone with your experience. But you haven\'t reached the end of the road yet. Speak to Lucan Cordell, behind the counter there. He\'ll guide you through the next phase of your journey.' WHERE entry=5182; /* Text0_1: I\'m afraid I have nothing to teach to someone with your experience. But you haven\'t reached the end of the road yet. Speak to Lucan Cordell, behind the counter there. He\'ll guide you through the next phase of your journey. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Hmm... well you seem capable enough. If you truly desire to learn, then nothing will stand in your way! I will guide you through your first steps on what I hope will be a long and fulfilling path.' WHERE entry=5183; /* Text0_1: Hmm... well you seem capable enough. If you truly desire to learn, then nothing will stand in your way! I will guide you through your first steps on what I hope will be a long and fulfilling path. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There are ways to strengthen steel beyond the hammer and forge, young wanderer.' WHERE entry=5184; /* Text0_0: There are ways to strengthen steel beyond the hammer and forge, young wanderer. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ye\'re a fine enchanter indeed! Now it\'s time fer ye to move on. I want ye to talk to Gimble Thistlefuzz, upstairs. He\'s a bit of a character, but he\'ll steer ye in the right direction from here on out!' WHERE entry=5185; /* Text0_0: Ye\'re a fine enchanter indeed! Now it\'s time fer ye to move on. I want ye to talk to Gimble Thistlefuzz, upstairs. He\'s a bit of a character, but he\'ll steer ye in the right direction from here on out! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, ye\'re an inquisitive one, are ye\'? Excellent! Pay close attention, this just might save yer skin when the goin\' gets rough!' WHERE entry=5186; /* Text0_0: Ah, ye\'re an inquisitive one, are ye\'? Excellent! Pay close attention, this just might save yer skin when the goin\' gets rough! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The Goddess has granted me wisdom, stranger. If it is her will, I shall pass it on to you.' WHERE entry=5187; /* Text0_1: The Goddess has granted me wisdom, stranger. If it is her will, I shall pass it on to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Your skills are beyond my reach. It is time for you to face new challenges. Taladan will help you prepare. He is standing by the table there.' WHERE entry=5188; /* Text0_1: Your skills are beyond my reach. It is time for you to face new challenges. Taladan will help you prepare. He is standing by the table there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I will teach you what I can. Each lesson is a gift from the Goddess herself. Use her gifts wisely, and you shall not falter.' WHERE entry=5189; /* Text0_1: I will teach you what I can. Each lesson is a gift from the Goddess herself. Use her gifts wisely, and you shall not falter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Elune\'s secrets are many, but they are not to be shared with just anyone.' WHERE entry=5190; /* Text0_1: Elune\'s secrets are many, but they are not to be shared with just anyone. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You have truly accelled in your knowledge of enchanting. There is much more to learn, if you are willing. Speak to Taladan, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus.' WHERE entry=5191; /* Text0_1: You have truly accelled in your knowledge of enchanting. There is much more to learn, if you are willing. Speak to Taladan, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Open your mind, wanderer, and we shall begin.' WHERE entry=5192; /* Text0_1: Open your mind, wanderer, and we shall begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I do not have time to waste, stranger. State your business or be off!' WHERE entry=5193; /* Text0_0: I do not have time to waste, stranger. State your business or be off! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Eh, well you\'ve made it this far... go see Lavinia Crowe by the other bookshelf there. If you don\'t mess things up with her, maybe you can learn some more.' WHERE entry=5194; /* Text0_0: Eh, well you\'ve made it this far... go see Lavinia Crowe by the other bookshelf there. If you don\'t mess things up with her, maybe you can learn some more. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You don\'t look like much to me, but who knows, maybe there\'s an enchanter hidden in there somewhere!',Text0_1_loc9='You don\'t look like much to me, but who knows, maybe there\'s an enchanter hidden in there somewhere!' WHERE entry=5195; /* Text0_0: You don\'t look like much to me, but who knows, maybe there\'s an enchanter hidden in there somewhere! */ /* Text0_1: You don\'t look like much to me, but who knows, maybe there\'s an enchanter hidden in there somewhere! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What I wouldn\'t give to be out on the open plains on a day like this... but my duty binds me.' WHERE entry=5196; /* Text0_0: What I wouldn\'t give to be out on the open plains on a day like this... but my duty binds me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I cannot teach you anything you don\'t already know. However, the knowledge of my father far surpasses my own. Go inside and speak to him. Good luck!' WHERE entry=5197; /* Text0_0: I cannot teach you anything you don\'t already know. However, the knowledge of my father far surpasses my own. Go inside and speak to him. Good luck! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There are many secrets that may be unlocked with patience and determination. Now, let us begin...' WHERE entry=5198; /* Text0_0: There are many secrets that may be unlocked with patience and determination. Now, let us begin... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Throm-ka! What you looking for, stranger?' WHERE entry=5199; /* Text0_0: Throm-ka! What you looking for, stranger? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You come to wrong place. Talk to the expert Godan over there. You learn more from him.' WHERE entry=5200; /* Text0_0: You come to wrong place. Talk to the expert Godan over there. You learn more from him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='To die in battle is glorious! But, with what I teach you, maybe you not die so quickly, hm?' WHERE entry=5201; /* Text0_0: To die in battle is glorious! But, with what I teach you, maybe you not die so quickly, hm? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Who are you? What do you want from me?' WHERE entry=5202; /* Text0_0: Who are you? What do you want from me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What do I look like, the Grand Poobah of enchanters? Your skills require the guidance of an Artisan! Go find Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora.' WHERE entry=5203; /* Text0_0: What do I look like, the Grand Poobah of enchanters? Your skills require the guidance of an Artisan! Go find Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Great, let\'s get started... ha! Fooled you! Surely you didn\'t think it would be that simple. You\'ll need to prove your mettle just like everyone else!' WHERE entry=5204; /* Text0_0: Great, let\'s get started... ha! Fooled you! Surely you didn\'t think it would be that simple. You\'ll need to prove your mettle just like everyone else! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re joking, right? I believe you\'re looking for the OTHER short fellow, Thonys Pillarstone. He\'s downstairs. Now skedaddle!' WHERE entry=5205; /* Text0_0: You\'re joking, right? I believe you\'re looking for the OTHER short fellow, Thonys Pillarstone. He\'s downstairs. Now skedaddle! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Okay, well??? don\'t get cocky! Since you have demonstrated  your competence though, we may now begin!' WHERE entry=5206; /* Text0_0: Okay, well??? don\'t get cocky! Since you have demonstrated  your competence though, we may now begin! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you have what it takes, I will be happy to show you the way.' WHERE entry=5207; /* Text0_0: If you have what it takes, I will be happy to show you the way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A true professional know his limitations, and I\'m not ashamed to admit that your skills exceed mine. I want you to pay a visit to Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora. She is well-renowned, and with good reason.' WHERE entry=5208; /* Text0_0: A true professional know his limitations, and I\'m not ashamed to admit that your skills exceed mine. I want you to pay a visit to Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora. She is well-renowned, and with good reason. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You seem confident. Surely you wouldn\'t mind a test of your skills?' WHERE entry=5209; /* Text0_0: You seem confident. Surely you wouldn\'t mind a test of your skills? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are not ready. Speak to Betty Quinn, she\'s standing by the stairs over there. Return to me when you have achieved a higher enlightenment.' WHERE entry=5210; /* Text0_0: You are not ready. Speak to Betty Quinn, she\'s standing by the stairs over there. Return to me when you have achieved a higher enlightenment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your confidence is well-founded, traveler. Now your true education may begin!' WHERE entry=5211; /* Text0_0: Your confidence is well-founded, traveler. Now your true education may begin! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you seek to hunt naga, then you will need all the help you can get. Deep in the water you can find bubbly fissures that produce enough air bubbles that will allow you to breath underwater. Swim up close so that you can use the bubbles.' WHERE entry=5212; /* Text0_0: If you seek to hunt naga, then you will need all the help you can get. Deep in the water you can find bubbly fissures that produce enough air bubbles that will allow you to breath underwater. Swim up close so that you can use the bubbles. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is true I have skills to teach to those who are worthy. Would that be you?' WHERE entry=5213; /* Text0_0: It is true I have skills to teach to those who are worthy. Would that be you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are an exceptional enchanter. Beyond my talents as a teacher, I fear. Seek out Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora. Only she can qualify as your instructor now.' WHERE entry=5214; /* Text0_0: You are an exceptional enchanter. Beyond my talents as a teacher, I fear. Seek out Kitta Firewind at the Tower of Azora. Only she can qualify as your instructor now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I believe you are up to this task, will you accept the challenge?' WHERE entry=5215; /* Text0_0: I believe you are up to this task, will you accept the challenge? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have not yet learned the basics, wanderer. Have you spoken to my assistant, Lalina Summermoon? Perhaps you should.' WHERE entry=5216; /* Text0_0: You have not yet learned the basics, wanderer. Have you spoken to my assistant, Lalina Summermoon? Perhaps you should. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Fine work! You are truly deserving of the knowledge I shall bestow upon you!' WHERE entry=5217; /* Text0_0: Fine work! You are truly deserving of the knowledge I shall bestow upon you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='If you are seeking a truly rewarding pursuit, then a life of enchanting is for you!' WHERE entry=5218; /* Text0_1: If you are seeking a truly rewarding pursuit, then a life of enchanting is for you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I know many things, stranger, but your knowledge rivals my own. Enchanters who wish to hone their skills further are known to travel to the Tower of Azora, where an artisan named Kitta Firewind resides.' WHERE entry=5219; /* Text0_1: I know many things, stranger, but your knowledge rivals my own. Enchanters who wish to hone their skills further are known to travel to the Tower of Azora, where an artisan named Kitta Firewind resides. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Why don\'t we see just what you\'re capable of? If you complete the task I shall be happy to further your training!' WHERE entry=5220; /* Text0_1: Why don\'t we see just what you\'re capable of? If you complete the task I shall be happy to further your training! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Enchanting has run in our family for generations. I learned at an early age, just as my son is doing now.' WHERE entry=5223; /* Text0_0: Enchanting has run in our family for generations. I learned at an early age, just as my son is doing now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There is one whose knowledge exceeds my own. You are ready to seek her out. Go to Sun Rock Retreat in Stonetalon Mountains. Find Hgarth, and continue your training.' WHERE entry=5224; /* Text0_0: There is one whose knowledge exceeds my own. You are ready to seek her out. Go to Sun Rock Retreat in Stonetalon Mountains. Find Hgarth, and continue your training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I will teach you soon. I require a demonstration of your loyalty, first.' WHERE entry=5225; /* Text0_0: I will teach you soon. I require a demonstration of your loyalty, first. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Surely Mot didn\'t send you to me? He knows better. You are not yet capable of understanding what I would teach you. See my son Mot, just outside there, and finish training with him.' WHERE entry=5226; /* Text0_0: Surely Mot didn\'t send you to me? He knows better. You are not yet capable of understanding what I would teach you. See my son Mot, just outside there, and finish training with him. */
