UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='This hide isn\'t ready to work with yet. I wish it didn\'t take so long to make leather. There has to be some way to cut down on all this waiting. It can\'t be good for my health, you know?' WHERE entry=5276; /* Text0_1: This hide isn\'t ready to work with yet. I wish it didn\'t take so long to make leather. There has to be some way to cut down on all this waiting. It can\'t be good for my health, you know? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Aww, what rotten luck! My skills aren\'t good enough to be of any use to you. Oh well. Talk to Fimble Finespindle over there by the loom. He\'s been working with leather for longer than I have.' WHERE entry=5277; /* Text0_1: Aww, what rotten luck! My skills aren\'t good enough to be of any use to you. Oh well. Talk to Fimble Finespindle over there by the loom. He\'s been working with leather for longer than I have. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Oh, goody, something else to do while I wait! You\'re a real life-saver, $N!' WHERE entry=5278; /* Text0_1: Oh, goody, something else to do while I wait! You\'re a real life-saver, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You like the rug? I killed and skinned the beast myself. May all the centaur fall as easily.' WHERE entry=5279; /* Text0_1: You like the rug? I killed and skinned the beast myself. May all the centaur fall as easily. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I have nothing more to teach you. Talk to Karolek if you wish to further your leatherworking skills.' WHERE entry=5280; /* Text0_1: I have nothing more to teach you. Talk to Karolek if you wish to further your leatherworking skills. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Too bad we can\'t skin the humans and their allies. All that skin is just going to waste. Still, who\'d want to wear the flimsy leather you could make out of it?' WHERE entry=5281; /* Text0_1: Too bad we can\'t skin the humans and their allies. All that skin is just going to waste. Still, who\'d want to wear the flimsy leather you could make out of it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Skin, glorious skin. It holds your insides... in. You might\'ve noticed my skin\'s not doing so well. To think I used to worry about my pores. Hardly any skin left to worry about these days. In a way, it\'s very freeing.' WHERE entry=5282; /* Text0_1: Skin, glorious skin. It holds your insides... in. You might\'ve noticed my skin\'s not doing so well. To think I used to worry about my pores. Hardly any skin left to worry about these days. In a way, it\'s very freeing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You\'ve got the hang of it. I can\'t teach you any more, but talk to Arthur Moore, a Forsaken who works in the Rogues\' Quarter of the Undercity. Tell him I sent you.' WHERE entry=5283; /* Text0_1: You\'ve got the hang of it. I can\'t teach you any more, but talk to Arthur Moore, a Forsaken who works in the Rogues\' Quarter of the Undercity. Tell him I sent you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Before the plague came, I knew nothing about leather. Now I know enough to teach others. Death\'s left me with a lot of time on my hands.' WHERE entry=5284; /* Text0_1: Before the plague came, I knew nothing about leather. Now I know enough to teach others. Death\'s left me with a lot of time on my hands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Meat, skin, bones... a good hunter lets nothing go to waste. Every scrap of leather can be salvaged, perhaps to reinforce an ally\'s armor. Thus, each of us is strong alone, but together we become invincible.' WHERE entry=5285; /* Text0_0: Meat, skin, bones... a good hunter lets nothing go to waste. Every scrap of leather can be salvaged, perhaps to reinforce an ally\'s armor. Thus, each of us is strong alone, but together we become invincible. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have outgrown any teachings I could offer. Go with the blessing of the Earth Mother. Seek out the tauren Tarn in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Be guided by his wisdom.' WHERE entry=5286; /* Text0_0: You have outgrown any teachings I could offer. Go with the blessing of the Earth Mother. Seek out the tauren Tarn in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Be guided by his wisdom. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We live and die, and the land remains, eternal, unmoved by our passage. Thus, land cannot belong to us, $N. Instead, we belong to it. Therefore we protect the land, for without it we cannot hope to survive.' WHERE entry=5287; /* Text0_0: We live and die, and the land remains, eternal, unmoved by our passage. Thus, land cannot belong to us, $N. Instead, we belong to it. Therefore we protect the land, for without it we cannot hope to survive. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The caverns below us are a source of strange and wondrous hides, but you must take care if you venture into their depths, $N. Remember that your own skin is far more valuable.' WHERE entry=5288; /* Text0_0: The caverns below us are a source of strange and wondrous hides, but you must take care if you venture into their depths, $N. Remember that your own skin is far more valuable. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your understanding of leather is deeper than my own. Perhaps you should visit the tauren Krulmoo Fullmoon in Camp Taurajo of the Barrens. He has much knowledge to offer a student of your talents.' WHERE entry=5289; /* Text0_0: Your understanding of leather is deeper than my own. Perhaps you should visit the tauren Krulmoo Fullmoon in Camp Taurajo of the Barrens. He has much knowledge to offer a student of your talents. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Cairne himself lives here, they say. Once I have finished crafting a fitting gift, I will seek him out. Perhaps he will have words of wisdom for me.' WHERE entry=5291; /* Text0_0: Cairne himself lives here, they say. Once I have finished crafting a fitting gift, I will seek him out. Perhaps he will have words of wisdom for me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your talent is beyond my own, friend. Speak with Tarn here; his knowledge of leather is much greater than mine. I\'m sure he would welcome another student.' WHERE entry=5292; /* Text0_0: Your talent is beyond my own, friend. Speak with Tarn here; his knowledge of leather is much greater than mine. I\'m sure he would welcome another student. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Cleanse your hands before you begin any project. Staining the leather with blood or dirt would take away from its natural beauty.' WHERE entry=5293; /* Text0_0: Cleanse your hands before you begin any project. Staining the leather with blood or dirt would take away from its natural beauty. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='When I clawed my way out of the grave, I thought my family would welcome me with open arms. Instead, they drove me from the village, screaming in a language I could no longer understand.' WHERE entry=5294; /* Text0_0: When I clawed my way out of the grave, I thought my family would welcome me with open arms. Instead, they drove me from the village, screaming in a language I could no longer understand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I can\'t help you; your work is beyond my own. Talk to Arthur Moore, over there by the coffins. He\'ll be able to train you further.' WHERE entry=5295; /* Text0_0: I can\'t help you; your work is beyond my own. Talk to Arthur Moore, over there by the coffins. He\'ll be able to train you further. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Take every word I say and commit it to memory. Until our enemies have been eradicated, we must never shirk a chance to further our knowledge. Reinforce your armor, and never relax your guard.' WHERE entry=5296; /* Text0_0: Take every word I say and commit it to memory. Until our enemies have been eradicated, we must never shirk a chance to further our knowledge. Reinforce your armor, and never relax your guard. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You are beyond my limited abilities. Seek out the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She can teach you more. I only wish that I could go with you.' WHERE entry=5314; /* Text0_1: You are beyond my limited abilities. Seek out the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She can teach you more. I only wish that I could go with you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='My teachings would be too advanced for you at this stage. If you wish to learn more of potions, speak with Tel\'Athir here instead.' WHERE entry=5316; /* Text0_1: My teachings would be too advanced for you at this stage. If you wish to learn more of potions, speak with Tel\'Athir here instead. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Listen carefully, $N, for I have much knowledge to impart.' WHERE entry=5317; /* Text0_1: Listen carefully, $N, for I have much knowledge to impart. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Even I have my limitations! Go talk to Lavinia Crowe in Undercity if you wish to further your training.' WHERE entry=5318; /* Text0_0: Even I have my limitations! Go talk to Lavinia Crowe in Undercity if you wish to further your training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Not bad... I suppose training you is not out of the question. Very well! Let\'s begin...' WHERE entry=5319; /* Text0_0: Not bad... I suppose training you is not out of the question. Very well! Let\'s begin... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Randal\'s a bit of a dandy, but he\'s dependable, which is more than I can say for a lot of the students I take on. Still, I guess I can\'t blame them for wanting a bit of adventure.' WHERE entry=5320; /* Text0_0: Randal\'s a bit of a dandy, but he\'s dependable, which is more than I can say for a lot of the students I take on. Still, I guess I can\'t blame them for wanting a bit of adventure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Sorry, but you\'ve reached the limit of what I can teach. If you want to learn more, go see Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s pretty talented, so I hear.' WHERE entry=5321; /* Text0_0: Sorry, but you\'ve reached the limit of what I can teach. If you want to learn more, go see Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s pretty talented, so I hear. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Come back to me when you\'ve had more training. Randal Worth over there can help you with that.' WHERE entry=5323; /* Text0_0: Come back to me when you\'ve had more training. Randal Worth over there can help you with that. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hmm, I guess I can take on another student. Well, don\'t just stand there. Tell me what you\'re looking to learn.' WHERE entry=5324; /* Text0_0: Hmm, I guess I can take on another student. Well, don\'t just stand there. Tell me what you\'re looking to learn. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Darianna shows promise, but she is so full of energy that it is hard for her to stay still and listen. With her strength and agility, I fear it won\'t be long before she is called to fight. We must teach her quickly.' WHERE entry=5325; /* Text0_0: Darianna shows promise, but she is so full of energy that it is hard for her to stay still and listen. With her strength and agility, I fear it won\'t be long before she is called to fight. We must teach her quickly. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you are here for further training, you have overestimated my abilities. Have a word with Telonis over there; he can help you.' WHERE entry=5326; /* Text0_0: If you are here for further training, you have overestimated my abilities. Have a word with Telonis over there; he can help you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='In time you will be ready for what I have to teach, $N. Until then, please ask Darianna over there to help you with your training.' WHERE entry=5328; /* Text0_0: In time you will be ready for what I have to teach, $N. Until then, please ask Darianna over there to help you with your training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Many animals lost their lives so that we could gain these materials. Do not take their sacrifice lightly, $N. Handle the leather with the respect it deserves.' WHERE entry=5329; /* Text0_0: Many animals lost their lives so that we could gain these materials. Do not take their sacrifice lightly, $N. Handle the leather with the respect it deserves. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Lots to do! Haven\'t been this busy since my cousin accidentally vaporized all the cloth and leather in Gnomeregan. My, it was drafty for a while! Ah, $N, those were the days....' WHERE entry=5330; /* Text0_0: Lots to do! Haven\'t been this busy since my cousin accidentally vaporized all the cloth and leather in Gnomeregan. My, it was drafty for a while! Ah, $N, those were the days.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Nope, can\'t help you, I\'m afraid. Your skills have mine beat! If you want to learn more, talk to the night elf Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s amazing!' WHERE entry=5331; /* Text0_0: Nope, can\'t help you, I\'m afraid. Your skills have mine beat! If you want to learn more, talk to the night elf Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He\'s amazing! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well, I declare! It\'s a new student! I\'ll gladly teach you everything I know once you have a little more skill. Go talk to Gretta Finespindle over there, would you? She\'ll have you up to speed in no time.' WHERE entry=5333; /* Text0_0: Well, I declare! It\'s a new student! I\'ll gladly teach you everything I know once you have a little more skill. Go talk to Gretta Finespindle over there, would you? She\'ll have you up to speed in no time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your skills are coming along nicely. Soon you\'ll be running a leather shop of your own. I\'ll be glad for the help, $N. My hands are only so fast, you know? There\'s so much work to do!' WHERE entry=5334; /* Text0_0: Your skills are coming along nicely. Soon you\'ll be running a leather shop of your own. I\'ll be glad for the help, $N. My hands are only so fast, you know? There\'s so much work to do! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The strongest hides come from those kodo that have laid themselves to rest in this wasteland.' WHERE entry=5335; /* Text0_0: The strongest hides come from those kodo that have laid themselves to rest in this wasteland. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I cannot aid you with further lessons: your skills have surpassed mine. Go and see the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She offers more advanced training.' WHERE entry=5336; /* Text0_0: I cannot aid you with further lessons: your skills have surpassed mine. Go and see the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She offers more advanced training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I do not offer apprentice training. Look for the tauren Waldor in the Wailing Caverns, here in the Barrens. He can assist you with whatever you need.' WHERE entry=5338; /* Text0_0: I do not offer apprentice training. Look for the tauren Waldor in the Wailing Caverns, here in the Barrens. He can assist you with whatever you need. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Have you come for further training? Shake the dust of the road from your garments, then, and let us get to work.' WHERE entry=5339; /* Text0_0: Have you come for further training? Shake the dust of the road from your garments, then, and let us get to work. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My axe has seen many battles, and I like to keep it handy. Enemy forces have fought their way into our capital several times now, but have no fear: we have always driven them back.' WHERE entry=5340; /* Text0_0: My axe has seen many battles, and I like to keep it handy. Enemy forces have fought their way into our capital several times now, but have no fear: we have always driven them back. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I cannot help you with further training: your skill at working with leather rivals my own. You should speak with Una, over there. I will vouch for your skill if need be.' WHERE entry=5341; /* Text0_0: I cannot help you with further training: your skill at working with leather rivals my own. You should speak with Una, over there. I will vouch for your skill if need be. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your skills are insufficient to learn what I teach. Try talking to Mak over there instead. He can help you out until you\'re ready for more advanced lessons.' WHERE entry=5343; /* Text0_0: Your skills are insufficient to learn what I teach. Try talking to Mak over there instead. He can help you out until you\'re ready for more advanced lessons. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am pleased with your progress so far. Surely the Earth Mother has inspired your hands.' WHERE entry=5344; /* Text0_0: I am pleased with your progress so far. Surely the Earth Mother has inspired your hands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We have only a small foothold on this continent for now, but the humans can\'t fight us off forever. Then they\'ll pay for enslaving us. We\'ll cut their lying tongues out for their treachery.' WHERE entry=5345; /* Text0_0: We have only a small foothold on this continent for now, but the humans can\'t fight us off forever. Then they\'ll pay for enslaving us. We\'ll cut their lying tongues out for their treachery. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'d train you if I could, but you\'re too much for me. Tell you what: go talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s got some real talent.' WHERE entry=5346; /* Text0_0: I\'d train you if I could, but you\'re too much for me. Tell you what: go talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s got some real talent. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve got more guts than brains, coming to me without the proper training. Go talk to somebody closer to your skill level, like the orc Kamari, who lives in the Drag of Orgrimmar.' WHERE entry=5348; /* Text0_0: You\'ve got more guts than brains, coming to me without the proper training. Go talk to somebody closer to your skill level, like the orc Kamari, who lives in the Drag of Orgrimmar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Am I busy? What\'s that supposed to mean? Do you think I just stand here all day, twiddling my thumbs? If you\'re here to buy something, talk to Handor.' WHERE entry=5350; /* Text0_0: Am I busy? What\'s that supposed to mean? Do you think I just stand here all day, twiddling my thumbs? If you\'re here to buy something, talk to Handor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You won\'t learn anything new from me; you know too much already. If you want more training, talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Send her my regards, eh?' WHERE entry=5351; /* Text0_0: You won\'t learn anything new from me; you know too much already. If you want more training, talk to the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. Send her my regards, eh? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You can\'t study my techniques until you\'ve learned the basics. Speak with Kamari if you are interested in training.' WHERE entry=5353; /* Text0_0: You can\'t study my techniques until you\'ve learned the basics. Speak with Kamari if you are interested in training. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The twists and turns of Orgrimmar are designed to thwart invaders. Can you imagine how quickly one of those puny gnomes would get lost in here? Ha! If it was lucky, I\'d track it down and keep it as a pet.' WHERE entry=5354; /* Text0_0: The twists and turns of Orgrimmar are designed to thwart invaders. Can you imagine how quickly one of those puny gnomes would get lost in here? Ha! If it was lucky, I\'d track it down and keep it as a pet. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Before my death, I was a librarian; I had nothing to do with wars and plagues. I never asked to become this. On the other hand, now that my mind is my own again, I\'m not about to surrender without a fight.' WHERE entry=5355; /* Text0_0: Before my death, I was a librarian; I had nothing to do with wars and plagues. I never asked to become this. On the other hand, now that my mind is my own again, I\'m not about to surrender without a fight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m pleased to say that your talents have outpaced my own. Go away now. Err, try the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s very skilled, I assure you.' WHERE entry=5356; /* Text0_0: I\'m pleased to say that your talents have outpaced my own. Go away now. Err, try the tauren Una in the northwestern shops of Thunder Bluff\'s central plateau. She\'s very skilled, I assure you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If I taught novices, there\'d be a lot more students visiting me, and things would get noisy. Go talk to Dan Golthas over there. He\'s a little intense, but he means well, and he\'s a decent teacher.' WHERE entry=5358; /* Text0_0: If I taught novices, there\'d be a lot more students visiting me, and things would get noisy. Go talk to Dan Golthas over there. He\'s a little intense, but he means well, and he\'s a decent teacher. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I first set up shop in the Magic Quarter, but it was pretty noisy there. This is a definite improvement, barring a few persistent students who still track me down, despite the fact that I\'ve relocated.' WHERE entry=5359; /* Text0_0: I first set up shop in the Magic Quarter, but it was pretty noisy there. This is a definite improvement, barring a few persistent students who still track me down, despite the fact that I\'ve relocated. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Elune has granted the night elves many gifts. In return, it is our responsibility to safeguard these forests from the demonic taint that the Horde always brings with it.' WHERE entry=5360; /* Text0_1: Elune has granted the night elves many gifts. In return, it is our responsibility to safeguard these forests from the demonic taint that the Horde always brings with it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Training you further is beyond my abilities. Speak to Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He is always glad to help talented students.' WHERE entry=5361; /* Text0_1: Training you further is beyond my abilities. Speak to Telonis in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. He is always glad to help talented students. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I only teach students who have already mastered the basics. You must seek out the night elf Darianna in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. Her skills will be a perfect complement to yours.' WHERE entry=5363; /* Text0_1: I only teach students who have already mastered the basics. You must seek out the night elf Darianna in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. Her skills will be a perfect complement to yours. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Always double-check your measurements before you begin to cut the leather. We cannot afford to waste materials.' WHERE entry=5364; /* Text0_1: Always double-check your measurements before you begin to cut the leather. We cannot afford to waste materials. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The waters of Westfall is where you must search, due west-northwest of where the Gold Coast Quarry meets with the shore.  An anchor shows where a boat has sunk beyond it, deep within the water.  The underwater pressure is fierce here; swimming too far will crush even the mightiest swimmer from fatigue.  $B$BLook for a natural formation to aid you, $N - a bubbly fissure is near here, offering deep-water swimmers a chance for renewed breath.$b' WHERE entry=5373; /* Text0_0: The waters of Westfall is where you must search, due west-northwest of where the Gold Coast Quarry meets with the shore.  An anchor shows where a boat has sunk beyond it, deep within the water.  The underwater pressure is fierce here; swimming too far will crush even the mightiest swimmer from fatigue.  $B$BLook for a natural formation to aid you, $N - a bubbly fissure is near here, offering deep-water swimmers a chance for renewed breath.$b */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='In the Silverpine Forest along the edges of the North Tide\'s Run, a derelict boat rests on the shore.  Out to the west of this lies what you seek; swim too far and the ocean will crush you from fatigue.  It resides on the ocean floor in a lockbox, waiting for you to claim it.$B$BYou\'ll be hard pressed to survive a dive to such depths without aid, so take heart; a bubbly fissure offers renewed breath to divers seeking this half of the pendant.  Use it wisely.' WHERE entry=5374; /* Text0_0: In the Silverpine Forest along the edges of the North Tide\'s Run, a derelict boat rests on the shore.  Out to the west of this lies what you seek; swim too far and the ocean will crush you from fatigue.  It resides on the ocean floor in a lockbox, waiting for you to claim it.$B$BYou\'ll be hard pressed to survive a dive to such depths without aid, so take heart; a bubbly fissure offers renewed breath to divers seeking this half of the pendant.  Use it wisely. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='In the northern part of Darkshore runs the Cliffspring River, flowing down from the lands now known as Felwood.  As the river flows out and empties out into the Mist\'s Edge, travel north to where deepest parts of the ocean begin.  A stone formation that some call the Stone Claw due it its shape is where you may find what you seek.$B$BBe warned - threshers gather by the Stone Claw, and will attack those who trespass on their territory.' WHERE entry=5375; /* Text0_1: In the northern part of Darkshore runs the Cliffspring River, flowing down from the lands now known as Felwood.  As the river flows out and empties out into the Mist\'s Edge, travel north to where deepest parts of the ocean begin.  A stone formation that some call the Stone Claw due it its shape is where you may find what you seek.$B$BBe warned - threshers gather by the Stone Claw, and will attack those who trespass on their territory. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='In the northeastern Barrens lies a pool of water sickened by pollution.  The locals call it the Sludge Fen; the Venture Company has turned the once crystal-blue waters into a mire of industrial byproducts and waste.  In the heart of this fen lies what you seek, $N.$B$BBe warned - the Venture Company does not tolerate trespassers, and they consider anyone who does not work for them as such.  You\'ll especially be a target as a protector of nature, something they vehemently oppose.' WHERE entry=5376; /* Text0_1: In the northeastern Barrens lies a pool of water sickened by pollution.  The locals call it the Sludge Fen; the Venture Company has turned the once crystal-blue waters into a mire of industrial byproducts and waste.  In the heart of this fen lies what you seek, $N.$B$BBe warned - the Venture Company does not tolerate trespassers, and they consider anyone who does not work for them as such.  You\'ll especially be a target as a protector of nature, something they vehemently oppose. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The grass is soft and lush. The air is fresh, full of light and song. Everything I\'ve seen suggests that Teldrassil is a dream come true. Why, then, is my heart full of foreboding?' WHERE entry=5393; /* Text0_0: The grass is soft and lush. The air is fresh, full of light and song. Everything I\'ve seen suggests that Teldrassil is a dream come true. Why, then, is my heart full of foreboding? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have advanced beyond my skill to teach you. Journey now to Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands and speak with the dwarf Drakk Stonehand. His work is magnificent, far better than my own.' WHERE entry=5394; /* Text0_0: You have advanced beyond my skill to teach you. Journey now to Aerie Peak in the Hinterlands and speak with the dwarf Drakk Stonehand. His work is magnificent, far better than my own. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I regret to say that I cannot aid you, $gnoble sir:gentle lady;, until you learn more of working with leather. Speak with Faldron or Darianna here instead. They can teach you the skill you require.' WHERE entry=5396; /* Text0_0: I regret to say that I cannot aid you, $gnoble sir:gentle lady;, until you learn more of working with leather. Speak with Faldron or Darianna here instead. They can teach you the skill you require. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do not try to force your will upon the leather. Rather, let its natural tendencies dictate what form and function it will take. This is not a battle to be won. Work with the leather, not against it.' WHERE entry=5397; /* Text0_0: Do not try to force your will upon the leather. Rather, let its natural tendencies dictate what form and function it will take. This is not a battle to be won. Work with the leather, not against it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The needle is small, but the thread is strong, and the stitches are fine. Our pact with Thrall and the others will hold. The Horde will not be driven from these lands.' WHERE entry=5398; /* Text0_1: The needle is small, but the thread is strong, and the stitches are fine. Our pact with Thrall and the others will hold. The Horde will not be driven from these lands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Even my talents have a limit, and you have reached it. Congratulations, $N. Your next stop should be Camp Mojache in Feralas. The tauren Hahrana Ironhide lives there; she is renowned for her skill.' WHERE entry=5399; /* Text0_1: Even my talents have a limit, and you have reached it. Congratulations, $N. Your next stop should be Camp Mojache in Feralas. The tauren Hahrana Ironhide lives there; she is renowned for her skill. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It\'s been so long since I was a novice myself that I don\'t think I\'d be the best teacher for you. Try talking to Tarn or Mak, right over there. One of them should be able to answer your questions.' WHERE entry=5401; /* Text0_1: It\'s been so long since I was a novice myself that I don\'t think I\'d be the best teacher for you. Try talking to Tarn or Mak, right over there. One of them should be able to answer your questions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Cairne has brought us to a land rich with possibilities for the future. We have been fortunate, and so in turn we pass on our good fortune to others. That is why I began teaching, $N.' WHERE entry=5402; /* Text0_1: Cairne has brought us to a land rich with possibilities for the future. We have been fortunate, and so in turn we pass on our good fortune to others. That is why I began teaching, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I can make amazing things with the materials I find out here. By Muradin\'s beard, there are fantastic creatures in these hills! Go have a whack at them, $N, and bring me back some tall tales.' WHERE entry=5403; /* Text0_0: I can make amazing things with the materials I find out here. By Muradin\'s beard, there are fantastic creatures in these hills! Go have a whack at them, $N, and bring me back some tall tales. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I love a good challenge; don\'t you? Aye, of course ye do. An\' that\'s why you\'re about to do exactly what I say.' WHERE entry=5405; /* Text0_0: I love a good challenge; don\'t you? Aye, of course ye do. An\' that\'s why you\'re about to do exactly what I say. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m not here to teach babes fresh out of the cradle. Ye\'ve nowhere near the amount of skill I require in my students. In fact, ye\'re a sad figure of a $glad:lass;, an\' I\'ll thank ye not to stand there jibber-jabberin\' at me.' WHERE entry=5406; /* Text0_0: I\'m not here to teach babes fresh out of the cradle. Ye\'ve nowhere near the amount of skill I require in my students. In fact, ye\'re a sad figure of a $glad:lass;, an\' I\'ll thank ye not to stand there jibber-jabberin\' at me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor.' WHERE entry=5407; /* Text0_1: All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I only wish I had more students like you. Not many will venture so far into enemy territory. I salute your courage.' WHERE entry=5408; /* Text0_1: I only wish I had more students like you. Not many will venture so far into enemy territory. I salute your courage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me?' WHERE entry=5409; /* Text0_1: We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $N. I have no time to teach basic skills. We\'re fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don\'t return to me until you are more prepared.' WHERE entry=5410; /* Text0_1: You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $N. I have no time to teach basic skills. We\'re fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don\'t return to me until you are more prepared. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I can tell that your wardrobe is in dire need of care.' WHERE entry=5413; /* Text0_0: I can tell that your wardrobe is in dire need of care. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m a simple man who knows a few things about tailoring, but you need more assistance than I can provide. I have heard of a Night Elf who is quite an accomplished tailor. He resides in Stormwind, in the Magic District.' WHERE entry=5414; /* Text0_0: I\'m a simple man who knows a few things about tailoring, but you need more assistance than I can provide. I have heard of a Night Elf who is quite an accomplished tailor. He resides in Stormwind, in the Magic District. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='So you would like to learn a few things? I would be happy to get you started!' WHERE entry=5415; /* Text0_0: So you would like to learn a few things? I would be happy to get you started! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Life is like a carefully woven tapestry.' WHERE entry=5416; /* Text0_0: Life is like a carefully woven tapestry. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hmm... the things you need to learn are a little above my head. Have a talk with Sellandus over at Larson\'s Clothiers just up the path to the right. He taught me everything I know!' WHERE entry=5417; /* Text0_0: Hmm... the things you need to learn are a little above my head. Have a talk with Sellandus over at Larson\'s Clothiers just up the path to the right. He taught me everything I know! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Very well, let your journey of tailoring begin.' WHERE entry=5418; /* Text0_0: Very well, let your journey of tailoring begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Needlework requires a steady hand. And patience... above all, patience.' WHERE entry=5419; /* Text0_0: Needlework requires a steady hand. And patience... above all, patience. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is time for you to journey to Darnassus and speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you from now on.' WHERE entry=5420; /* Text0_0: It is time for you to journey to Darnassus and speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you from now on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I would be happy to take you under my wing. Let us begin.' WHERE entry=5421; /* Text0_0: I would be happy to take you under my wing. Let us begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to me shop. What can I do for ye\'?' WHERE entry=5422; /* Text0_0: Welcome to me shop. What can I do for ye\'? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hold on there, I\'m just an assistant. If ye want to start learnin\' the fancy stuff, talk to old Stonebrew over there.' WHERE entry=5423; /* Text0_0: Hold on there, I\'m just an assistant. If ye want to start learnin\' the fancy stuff, talk to old Stonebrew over there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Excellent! I\'ve been hopin\' for a new student. Well, let\'s get started right away then!' WHERE entry=5424; /* Text0_0: Excellent! I\'ve been hopin\' for a new student. Well, let\'s get started right away then! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We use many animal pelts and skins in our creations. ' WHERE entry=5425; /* Text0_0: We use many animal pelts and skins in our creations. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I know a few things, but I\'m no expert. Lucky for you, Magar is. He\'s standing near the back of the shop. See if he can help you, but be careful not to rile him. He can be irritable.' WHERE entry=5426; /* Text0_0: I know a few things, but I\'m no expert. Lucky for you, Magar is. He\'s standing near the back of the shop. See if he can help you, but be careful not to rile him. He can be irritable. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I will teach you what I can.' WHERE entry=5427; /* Text0_0: I will teach you what I can. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='No part of the animals we hunt is wasted. ' WHERE entry=5428; /* Text0_0: No part of the animals we hunt is wasted. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You seek a higher knowledge. Tepa is blessed with such knowledge. She should be standing somewhere nearby...' WHERE entry=5429; /* Text0_0: You seek a higher knowledge. Tepa is blessed with such knowledge. She should be standing somewhere nearby... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='With the Earth Mother\'s blessing, we shall begin.' WHERE entry=5430; /* Text0_0: With the Earth Mother\'s blessing, we shall begin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Pleased to make you acquaintance. May I help you?' WHERE entry=5431; /* Text0_0: Pleased to make you acquaintance. May I help you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am knowledgable, but I am not an expert. You know who you should talk to? Rhiannon! She\'s not far. Ask around for her in Undercity' WHERE entry=5432; /* Text0_0: I am knowledgable, but I am not an expert. You know who you should talk to? Rhiannon! She\'s not far. Ask around for her in Undercity */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='So... you want to be a tailor? Very well, we\'ll see if you have what it takes.' WHERE entry=5433; /* Text0_0: So... you want to be a tailor? Very well, we\'ll see if you have what it takes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We don\'t get many visitors out here. May I interest you in something?' WHERE entry=5434; /* Text0_0: We don\'t get many visitors out here. May I interest you in something? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m just a student myself, really. Rhiannon\'s the expert. She\'s standing by the crates over there. You can learn a lot from her.' WHERE entry=5435; /* Text0_0: I\'m just a student myself, really. Rhiannon\'s the expert. She\'s standing by the crates over there. You can learn a lot from her. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yes, I think you have potential. Maybe I can show you a thing or two.' WHERE entry=5436; /* Text0_0: Yes, I think you have potential. Maybe I can show you a thing or two. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='There is no greater way to clear the mind than to weave.' WHERE entry=5437; /* Text0_1: There is no greater way to clear the mind than to weave. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='My education is ongoing, and your knowledge surpasses mine. If you wish to learn more you must speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you.' WHERE entry=5438; /* Text0_1: My education is ongoing, and your knowledge surpasses mine. If you wish to learn more you must speak to Me\'lynn. She will guide you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You will not be disappointed, traveler. Tailoring is a joyous endeavor.' WHERE entry=5439; /* Text0_1: You will not be disappointed, traveler. Tailoring is a joyous endeavor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hey mon, what can I be doin\' for you?' WHERE entry=5440; /* Text0_0: Hey mon, what can I be doin\' for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='At dis point you know as much as I do, mon. Maybe you go see Magar in Orgrimmar. He not be da happiest tailor around, but he help you anyway.' WHERE entry=5441; /* Text0_0: At dis point you know as much as I do, mon. Maybe you go see Magar in Orgrimmar. He not be da happiest tailor around, but he help you anyway. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Dat\'s da attitude! Grab a needle and thread and let\'s get jammin\'!' WHERE entry=5442; /* Text0_0: Dat\'s da attitude! Grab a needle and thread and let\'s get jammin\'! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am afraid that I am no longer gentle or humble. Age and countless battles have hardened my skin and soul. Perhaps that is why Cairne assigned me to Sun Rock Retreat... the gentle winds and warm sun does ease the pain.' WHERE entry=5443; /* Text0_0: I am afraid that I am no longer gentle or humble. Age and countless battles have hardened my skin and soul. Perhaps that is why Cairne assigned me to Sun Rock Retreat... the gentle winds and warm sun does ease the pain. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings.  Our bats are well trained and fed.  You\'ll not find faster.' WHERE entry=5453; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  Our bats are well trained and fed.  You\'ll not find faster. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='How may I be of service?' WHERE entry=5454; /* Text0_0: How may I be of service? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, and welcome.  I am not very good at smiling, but trust me; I am happy to serve you.' WHERE entry=5455; /* Text0_0: Greetings, and welcome.  I am not very good at smiling, but trust me; I am happy to serve you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The Hippogryph is a noble beast, proud and swift.  They are an honor to train, and can quickly take their rider a great distance.' WHERE entry=5473; /* Text0_1: The Hippogryph is a noble beast, proud and swift.  They are an honor to train, and can quickly take their rider a great distance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='To maintain our link to the mainland, we have hippogryphs constantly flying between Rut\'theran Village and Darkshore.' WHERE entry=5474; /* Text0_0: To maintain our link to the mainland, we have hippogryphs constantly flying between Rut\'theran Village and Darkshore. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The fish off the coast of Teldrassil are quite large and robust.  Rumors say it is the speedy growth of our new world tree that is the cause.' WHERE entry=5475; /* Text0_1: The fish off the coast of Teldrassil are quite large and robust.  Rumors say it is the speedy growth of our new world tree that is the cause. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Although the coast of Darkshore is more dangerous than that of Teldrassil, many fishers find profit here.' WHERE entry=5476; /* Text0_0: Although the coast of Darkshore is more dangerous than that of Teldrassil, many fishers find profit here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is my honor to provide for adventurers, for they are heroes in the making.' WHERE entry=5477; /* Text0_0: It is my honor to provide for adventurers, for they are heroes in the making. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Fastest gryphons this side of Aerie Peak. Want to take a ride?' WHERE entry=5479; /* Text0_0: Fastest gryphons this side of Aerie Peak. Want to take a ride? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='On the northern dock, you can board a ship that will carry you to Rut\'theran Village and Darnassus.  From the southern dock, you can find passage across the Great Sea to Stormwind Harbor.  The dock to the west, at the end of the pier, leads to Azuremyst Isle, near the Exodar. Safe journeys to you!' WHERE entry=5480; /* Text0_0: On the northern dock, you can board a ship that will carry you to Rut\'theran Village and Darnassus.  From the southern dock, you can find passage across the Great Sea to Stormwind Harbor.  The dock to the west, at the end of the pier, leads to Azuremyst Isle, near the Exodar. Safe journeys to you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This dock here?  Well you can catch the ship that goes to that Night Elf place.  What\'s it\'s name?  Uhh Auberdine I think.  I don\'t really know for sure, I just load and unload stuff.' WHERE entry=5481; /* Text0_0: This dock here?  Well you can catch the ship that goes to that Night Elf place.  What\'s it\'s name?  Uhh Auberdine I think.  I don\'t really know for sure, I just load and unload stuff. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Delivering these barrels to the excavation site is hard work, but there are so many depending on us to get the blast powder there.$B$BWe must do what we can against the Dark Irons!' WHERE entry=5494; /* Text0_0: Delivering these barrels to the excavation site is hard work, but there are so many depending on us to get the blast powder there.$B$BWe must do what we can against the Dark Irons! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='My wind riders are trained to fly quickly through the hot Barrens air.' WHERE entry=5495; /* Text0_0: My wind riders are trained to fly quickly through the hot Barrens air. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Barrens, with its hot sun and hostile denizens, is the perfect place to test your strength and fortitude.' WHERE entry=5496; /* Text0_0: The Barrens, with its hot sun and hostile denizens, is the perfect place to test your strength and fortitude. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings.  If you are here for leather goods, then you will find my wares well crafted.' WHERE entry=5497; /* Text0_0: Greetings.  If you are here for leather goods, then you will find my wares well crafted. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Are you here to help with the delivery? Miran\'s just about ready.' WHERE entry=5498; /* Text0_0: Are you here to help with the delivery? Miran\'s just about ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='When mounted on the back of a wind rider, one sees that its reputation for strength and speed is well earned.' WHERE entry=5500; /* Text0_0: When mounted on the back of a wind rider, one sees that its reputation for strength and speed is well earned. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This is a dangerous line of business!$B$BMiran just left with a delivery. He should be back in a few minutes.' WHERE entry=5501; /* Text0_0: This is a dangerous line of business!$B$BMiran just left with a delivery. He should be back in a few minutes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead who works in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.' WHERE entry=5513; /* Text0_0: You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead who works in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Have a look at my meats, friend.  You won\'t want to go out into the Barrens without a good stock of provisions.' WHERE entry=5515; /* Text0_0: Have a look at my meats, friend.  You won\'t want to go out into the Barrens without a good stock of provisions. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You haven\'t lived until you\'ve looked down on the world from the back of a wind rider.' WHERE entry=5516; /* Text0_0: You haven\'t lived until you\'ve looked down on the world from the back of a wind rider. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You can find passage to Theramore from this dock.  Heed my words, those lands are rarely safe to travel for people of the Alliance.  Watch your step and your back.' WHERE entry=5517; /* Text0_0: You can find passage to Theramore from this dock.  Heed my words, those lands are rarely safe to travel for people of the Alliance.  Watch your step and your back. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Good day to you.' WHERE entry=5519; /* Text0_0: Good day to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You are beyond my level of expertise. Georgio Bolero, the master of Duncan\'s Textiles around the corner could help you advance your skills.' WHERE entry=5520; /* Text0_0: You are beyond my level of expertise. Georgio Bolero, the master of Duncan\'s Textiles around the corner could help you advance your skills. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Speak with Lawrence Shneider at Duncan\'s Textiles around the corner to the left. He is adept at dealing with beginners.' WHERE entry=5522; /* Text0_0: Speak with Lawrence Shneider at Duncan\'s Textiles around the corner to the left. He is adept at dealing with beginners. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A fine display of worthiness. Your instruction may now continue.' WHERE entry=5523; /* Text0_0: A fine display of worthiness. Your instruction may now continue. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, this Darnassian fabric is the finest!' WHERE entry=5524; /* Text0_0: Ah, this Darnassian fabric is the finest! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well, aren\'t you the smarty-pants? Ye know more than I do, I can tell ye that! Don\'t go getting\' a big head, but if ye want to keep learnin\', have a chat with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. They say he knows his tailorin\'!' WHERE entry=5525; /* Text0_0: Well, aren\'t you the smarty-pants? Ye know more than I do, I can tell ye that! Don\'t go getting\' a big head, but if ye want to keep learnin\', have a chat with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. They say he knows his tailorin\'! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I don\'t have time to babysit! Go talk to me assistant, Uthrar!' WHERE entry=5527; /* Text0_0: I don\'t have time to babysit! Go talk to me assistant, Uthrar! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hmm... you show a little promise, I\'ll give you that. Okay then, where were we?' WHERE entry=5528; /* Text0_0: Hmm... you show a little promise, I\'ll give you that. Okay then, where were we? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Do you hear the call of the hunt, $c?  You must listen closely, but the call comes from deep within you.  It comes from deep within all of us.' WHERE entry=5529; /* Text0_1: Do you hear the call of the hunt, $c?  You must listen closely, but the call comes from deep within you.  It comes from deep within all of us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I made a lot of the things you see in the store. What do you think? Answer carefully, your life may depend on it.' WHERE entry=5530; /* Text0_0: I made a lot of the things you see in the store. What do you think? Answer carefully, your life may depend on it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You need to learn from someone who knows more than I do. Go talk to Josef Gregorian in Undercity. Well, what are you still doing here?' WHERE entry=5531; /* Text0_0: You need to learn from someone who knows more than I do. Go talk to Josef Gregorian in Undercity. Well, what are you still doing here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What? Why are you bothering me? Why, I bet you can\'t even create a high quality robe! Go talk to Snang and come back when you\'re worthy of my talents!' WHERE entry=5533; /* Text0_0: What? Why are you bothering me? Why, I bet you can\'t even create a high quality robe! Go talk to Snang and come back when you\'re worthy of my talents! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='About time you showed me some results! Now I\'ll show you results!' WHERE entry=5534; /* Text0_0: About time you showed me some results! Now I\'ll show you results! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='They say a stitch in time saves... what, eleven? Ah, I can\'t remember. Stupid saying anyway.' WHERE entry=5535; /* Text0_0: They say a stitch in time saves... what, eleven? Ah, I can\'t remember. Stupid saying anyway. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Not bad... for an amateur! Still, you know about as much as I do. If you wanna\' learn more you\'re gonna\' have to talk to Josef Gregorian in Undercity.' WHERE entry=5536; /* Text0_0: Not bad... for an amateur! Still, you know about as much as I do. If you wanna\' learn more you\'re gonna\' have to talk to Josef Gregorian in Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well well, not too bad. Maybe I CAN show you a few things...' WHERE entry=5539; /* Text0_0: Well well, not too bad. Maybe I CAN show you a few things... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='What a fine day! It inspires me to create a new design.' WHERE entry=5540; /* Text0_1: What a fine day! It inspires me to create a new design. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Your talents excel! You are truly inspired. To continue your pursuit of knowledge, speak with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. He is held in high regard, and will be able to further your instruction.' WHERE entry=5541; /* Text0_1: Your talents excel! You are truly inspired. To continue your pursuit of knowledge, speak with Georgio Bolero in Stormwind. He is held in high regard, and will be able to further your instruction. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='There are basics that must be learned. Trianna is standing nearby, speak with her and return to me later.' WHERE entry=5543; /* Text0_1: There are basics that must be learned. Trianna is standing nearby, speak with her and return to me later. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You have done well, traveler. I am proud to call you my student!' WHERE entry=5544; /* Text0_1: You have done well, traveler. I am proud to call you my student! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to our tent. May I assist you?' WHERE entry=5545; /* Text0_1: Welcome to our tent. May I assist you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Your knowledge is great, traveler. You must learn from one who is wiser than I. Many tales have been told of the wisdom of Josef Gregorian. You may find him in Undercity.' WHERE entry=5546; /* Text0_1: Your knowledge is great, traveler. You must learn from one who is wiser than I. Many tales have been told of the wisdom of Josef Gregorian. You may find him in Undercity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Expertly accomplished! Now, let us continue your education...' WHERE entry=5549; /* Text0_1: Expertly accomplished! Now, let us continue your education... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Aren\'t the patterns beautiful? Each one speaks with its own voice.' WHERE entry=5551; /* Text0_1: Aren\'t the patterns beautiful? Each one speaks with its own voice. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='My knowledge is limited, though I am still learning. It is time for you to move on, traveler. Find Josef Gregorian in Undercity and tell him you are ready.' WHERE entry=5552; /* Text0_1: My knowledge is limited, though I am still learning. It is time for you to move on, traveler. Find Josef Gregorian in Undercity and tell him you are ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='There are fundamental things you must learn before I can aid you. Speak to my apprentice, Vhan. He is kind and patient and will teach you what you need to know.' WHERE entry=5554; /* Text0_1: There are fundamental things you must learn before I can aid you. Speak to my apprentice, Vhan. He is kind and patient and will teach you what you need to know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You are truly a determined student. I will be happy to provide you with instruction!' WHERE entry=5555; /* Text0_1: You are truly a determined student. I will be happy to provide you with instruction! */
