UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The place is a bit drafty... but what do I care? I\'m dead.' WHERE entry=5575; /* Text0_0: The place is a bit drafty... but what do I care? I\'m dead. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re doing very well in the art of tailoring, I must admit. Now, let\'s see how good you REALLY are...' WHERE entry=5577; /* Text0_0: You\'re doing very well in the art of tailoring, I must admit. Now, let\'s see how good you REALLY are... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Who sent you here? You\'re not ready for my instruction yet! You\'ll be told when you\'re ready.' WHERE entry=5578; /* Text0_0: Who sent you here? You\'re not ready for my instruction yet! You\'ll be told when you\'re ready. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I do so enjoy sitting out here, listening to the sounds of the Great Sea.  Oh, what?  Yes, there is a ship that will take you to Menethil Harbor.  It docks here from time to time.' WHERE entry=5579; /* Text0_1: I do so enjoy sitting out here, listening to the sounds of the Great Sea.  Oh, what?  Yes, there is a ship that will take you to Menethil Harbor.  It docks here from time to time. */
