UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='They say an army travels on its stomach, and that\'s the truth.  For any offensive to succeed, your troops have to be well-fed and well supplied.' WHERE entry=6255; /* Text0_0: They say an army travels on its stomach, and that\'s the truth.  For any offensive to succeed, your troops have to be well-fed and well supplied. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Some say that strength and bravery are most needed for an army\'s success.  And it\'s true!  But an army also needs supplies to keep itself in good shape, and it\'s my job to make sure they have what they need.' WHERE entry=6257; /* Text0_0: Some say that strength and bravery are most needed for an army\'s success.  And it\'s true!  But an army also needs supplies to keep itself in good shape, and it\'s my job to make sure they have what they need. */
