UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Zug zug, my friend!  I am Kelm Hargunth, the main supplier for the Warsong Outriders.  As you improve your standing with the Outriders, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you can use inside Warsong Gulch.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services.' WHERE entry=7294; /* Text0_0: Zug zug, my friend!  I am Kelm Hargunth, the main supplier for the Warsong Outriders.  As you improve your standing with the Outriders, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you can use inside Warsong Gulch.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='May the blessings of the night be yours, friend!  I am Illiyana Moonblaze, and I am the main supplier for the Silverwing Sentinels here in Ashenvale.  As you improve your standing with the Sentinels, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you can use inside Warsong Gulch.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services.' WHERE entry=7295; /* Text0_1: May the blessings of the night be yours, friend!  I am Illiyana Moonblaze, and I am the main supplier for the Silverwing Sentinels here in Ashenvale.  As you improve your standing with the Sentinels, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you can use inside Warsong Gulch.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services. */
