UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The burgeoning hero returns! It is good to see you again, $N. You are always welcome at our village.' WHERE entry=7456; /* Text0_0: The burgeoning hero returns! It is good to see you again, $N. You are always welcome at our village. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Let me at \'em, $N! Just give the word and I\'ll mount up and attack their bridge!' WHERE entry=7476; /* Text0_1: Let me at \'em, $N! Just give the word and I\'ll mount up and attack their bridge! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ll patrol the pass leading up to Frostwolf Keep. Just give me the word and I\'ll take flight, Commander.' WHERE entry=7479; /* Text0_0: I\'ll patrol the pass leading up to Frostwolf Keep. Just give me the word and I\'ll take flight, Commander. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Greetings $c.  Do you wish to aid the Silverwing Sentinels in their fight at Warsong Gulch?' WHERE entry=7481; /* Text0_1: Greetings $c.  Do you wish to aid the Silverwing Sentinels in their fight at Warsong Gulch? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Elune be praised!  You seek out our Warsong Gulch Battlemaster?  Her name is Aethalas, and she stands ready to greet you near the warrior trainers.'Text1_1_loc9='It is no light endeavor upon which you embark $N.  To get to Warsong Gulch you will want to speak to Aethalas, the Battlemaster of the Silverwing Sentinels.  She will guide your way.  Blessings of the Goddess be with you!' WHERE entry=7482; /* Text0_1: Elune be praised!  You seek out our Warsong Gulch Battlemaster?  Her name is Aethalas, and she stands ready to greet you near the warrior trainers. */ /* Text1_1: It is no light endeavor upon which you embark $N.  To get to Warsong Gulch you will want to speak to Aethalas, the Battlemaster of the Silverwing Sentinels.  She will guide your way.  Blessings of the Goddess be with you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='So $g lad : lass;, you think you have what it takes to defend the Alliance against the Horde in Alterac Valley?  Very well then, you will want to speak with our very own Glordrum Steelbeard here in Ironforge.  You\'ll find him strategizing over the war table in the Hall of Arms.',Text0_1_loc9='So $g lad : lass;, you think you have what it takes to defend the Alliance against the Horde in Alterac Valley?  Very well then, you will want to speak with our very own Glordrum Steelbeard here in Ironforge.  You\'ll find him strategizing over the war table in the Hall of Arms.',Text1_0_loc9='Ah, Alterac Valley, I have fine memories I tell ya.  <sigh>  Well, I cannot join ya, but do me proud just the same!  To get there you\'ll be wanting to speak with Glordrum Steelbeard at the Hall of Arms here in Ironforge.',Text1_1_loc9='Ah, Alterac Valley, I have fine memories I tell ya.  <sigh>  Well, I cannot join ya, but do me proud just the same!  To get there you\'ll be wanting to speak with Glordrum Steelbeard at the Hall of Arms here in Ironforge.' WHERE entry=7483; /* Text0_0: So $g lad : lass;, you think you have what it takes to defend the Alliance against the Horde in Alterac Valley?  Very well then, you will want to speak with our very own Glordrum Steelbeard here in Ironforge.  You\'ll find him strategizing over the war table in the Hall of Arms. */ /* Text0_1: So $g lad : lass;, you think you have what it takes to defend the Alliance against the Horde in Alterac Valley?  Very well then, you will want to speak with our very own Glordrum Steelbeard here in Ironforge.  You\'ll find him strategizing over the war table in the Hall of Arms. */ /* Text1_0: Ah, Alterac Valley, I have fine memories I tell ya.  <sigh>  Well, I cannot join ya, but do me proud just the same!  To get there you\'ll be wanting to speak with Glordrum Steelbeard at the Hall of Arms here in Ironforge. */ /* Text1_1: Ah, Alterac Valley, I have fine memories I tell ya.  <sigh>  Well, I cannot join ya, but do me proud just the same!  To get there you\'ll be wanting to speak with Glordrum Steelbeard at the Hall of Arms here in Ironforge. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you are going to Alterac Valley then go speak to Kartra Bloodsnarl.  You will find her inside the Hall of the Brave in the Valley of Honor.',Text1_0_loc9='How I yearn to join you in glorious battle, but instead I am stuck here on duty.  Go to the Hall of the Brave in Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Honor and speak to Kartra Bloodsnarl.  She will help you get to Alterac Valley.  Make us proud $N!' WHERE entry=7484; /* Text0_0: If you are going to Alterac Valley then go speak to Kartra Bloodsnarl.  You will find her inside the Hall of the Brave in the Valley of Honor. */ /* Text1_0: How I yearn to join you in glorious battle, but instead I am stuck here on duty.  Go to the Hall of the Brave in Orgrimmar\'s Valley of Honor and speak to Kartra Bloodsnarl.  She will help you get to Alterac Valley.  Make us proud $N! */
