UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am Rutherford Twing, the main supplier for the Defilers posted here at Arathi Basin.  As you improve your standing with us, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you might find useful.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services.' WHERE entry=7723; /* Text0_0: I am Rutherford Twing, the main supplier for the Defilers posted here at Arathi Basin.  As you improve your standing with us, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you might find useful.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am Samuel Hawke, the main supplier for the League of Arathor posted here at Arathi Basin.  As you improve your standing with us, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you might find useful.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services.' WHERE entry=7724; /* Text0_0: I am Samuel Hawke, the main supplier for the League of Arathor posted here at Arathi Basin.  As you improve your standing with us, I will make available to you a fine selection of goods that you might find useful.  Should you find yourself in need of item repair, I also provide those services. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The battle for Warsong Gulch is a battle that we cannot lose.  We fight for our honor and we fight for our land, and no orc or misguided ally will take them from us!' WHERE entry=7725; /* Text0_1: The battle for Warsong Gulch is a battle that we cannot lose.  We fight for our honor and we fight for our land, and no orc or misguided ally will take them from us! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is no easy task to protect the Horde\'s lumber gathering efforts here in Ashenvale, but we have never shied from battle!  The night elves and their allies will fall!' WHERE entry=7726; /* Text0_0: It is no easy task to protect the Horde\'s lumber gathering efforts here in Ashenvale, but we have never shied from battle!  The night elves and their allies will fall! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:Ах, бедолага, с головы до ног в песке! Пожалуйста, не надо стесняться – отдохни и восстанови силы в этом прекрасном оазисе.',Text0_1_loc9='Greetings, traveler. As long as you remain within the walls of the Cenarion Hold, you will be safe from harm.$B$BBe wary when leaving the protection of the Hold as the silithid have been swarming as of late.' WHERE entry=7727; /* Text0_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text0:Ах, бедолага, с головы до ног в песке! Пожалуйста, не надо стесняться – отдохни и восстанови силы в этом прекрасном оазисе. */ /* Text0_1: Greetings, traveler. As long as you remain within the walls of the Cenarion Hold, you will be safe from harm.$B$BBe wary when leaving the protection of the Hold as the silithid have been swarming as of late. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I supply the Hold with various relics required for spellcasting as well as other alchemical reagents.' WHERE entry=7728; /* Text0_0: I supply the Hold with various relics required for spellcasting as well as other alchemical reagents. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A great evil stirs, $r. Can you feel it?$B$BBah! Of course you cannot. Hand me your armor and weapons and I shall renew their vigor.' WHERE entry=7729; /* Text0_0: A great evil stirs, $r. Can you feel it?$B$BBah! Of course you cannot. Hand me your armor and weapons and I shall renew their vigor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Oh dear, I am running dangerously low on supplies! What is taking that blasted goblin so long?' WHERE entry=7730; /* Text0_1: Oh dear, I am running dangerously low on supplies! What is taking that blasted goblin so long? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Look behind you, $r. The hive stirs as the land that surrounds us shudders and shakes.$B$BThe time has come for me to fulfill a promise I made a thousand years past. The sands shift once more as the Qiraji plan for war.' WHERE entry=7731; /* Text0_0: Look behind you, $r. The hive stirs as the land that surrounds us shudders and shakes.$B$BThe time has come for me to fulfill a promise I made a thousand years past. The sands shift once more as the Qiraji plan for war. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Why now, $r? I just do not understand it. So much work to be done...' WHERE entry=7732; /* Text0_0: Why now, $r? I just do not understand it. So much work to be done... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Commander has not been himself as of late. His mistress disappeared while on an archaeological dig in the southern desert - vanished without a trace! Very strange, indeed.$B$BI suppose you\'re looking for work? Do I need to bash you in the head with a clue?' WHERE entry=7733; /* Text0_0: The Commander has not been himself as of late. His mistress disappeared while on an archaeological dig in the southern desert - vanished without a trace! Very strange, indeed.$B$BI suppose you\'re looking for work? Do I need to bash you in the head with a clue? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Can ye hear it, stranger? The humming is gettin\' louder with each passing day. These crystals must be what\'s driving these bugs crazy.' WHERE entry=7734; /* Text0_1: Can ye hear it, stranger? The humming is gettin\' louder with each passing day. These crystals must be what\'s driving these bugs crazy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Look up to the heavens, $c. The Dragonflights have not been seen in this area for a thousand years! Those Qiraji are up to something, I just know it!' WHERE entry=7735; /* Text0_0: Look up to the heavens, $c. The Dragonflights have not been seen in this area for a thousand years! Those Qiraji are up to something, I just know it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Bronzebeard\'s gone missing again! That dwarf sure didn\'t get any of his brother\'s good senses.' WHERE entry=7736; /* Text0_0: Bronzebeard\'s gone missing again! That dwarf sure didn\'t get any of his brother\'s good senses. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Happy Hallow\'s End, $c!',Text1_0_loc9='You like candy?  I like candy.' WHERE entry=7739; /* Text0_0: Happy Hallow\'s End, $c! */ /* Text1_0: You like candy?  I like candy. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc9='Go Forsaken!  Yay us!' WHERE entry=7739; /* Text2_0: Go Forsaken!  Yay us! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to the Wickerman Festival, $c!$B$BOn the observance of Hallow\'s End, the Forsaken burn a wickerman in honor of this, the most revered of occasions.  It was on this day that the Banshee Queen herself delivered us from the clutches of the Lich King and the Scourge.  We have remained free ever since.  Those who would have seen us fall are repaid in full... with vengeance!$B$BThe burning of the Wickerman begins at 8:00 PM!' WHERE entry=7740; /* Text0_1: Welcome to the Wickerman Festival, $c!$B$BOn the observance of Hallow\'s End, the Forsaken burn a wickerman in honor of this, the most revered of occasions.  It was on this day that the Banshee Queen herself delivered us from the clutches of the Lich King and the Scourge.  We have remained free ever since.  Those who would have seen us fall are repaid in full... with vengeance!$B$BThe burning of the Wickerman begins at 8:00 PM! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You there!  You look able bodied... we need your aid in defending Southshore!$B$BThe blasted Forsaken are all riled up because it\'s Hallow\'s End.  Their "celebration" will no doubt be leading them right to our doorstep.  If you\'ve got the time, we really could use your help!' WHERE entry=7741; /* Text0_0: You there!  You look able bodied... we need your aid in defending Southshore!$B$BThe blasted Forsaken are all riled up because it\'s Hallow\'s End.  Their "celebration" will no doubt be leading them right to our doorstep.  If you\'ve got the time, we really could use your help! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is we who must make the first strike. We cannot be allowed to repeat the mistakes of the past...' WHERE entry=7742; /* Text0_0: It is we who must make the first strike. We cannot be allowed to repeat the mistakes of the past... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Be gone, infidel!  May the power of the Abyss smite you down!',Text0_1_loc9='Be gone, infidel!  May the power of the Abyss smite you down!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7744; /* Text0_0: Be gone, infidel!  May the power of the Abyss smite you down! */ /* Text0_1: Be gone, infidel!  May the power of the Abyss smite you down! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Greetings, $c.  Welcome to Cenarion Hold.  From here we will strike against the silithid where they\'re at their strongest.  I hope you\'ve come to lend a hand.' WHERE entry=7746; /* Text0_1: Greetings, $c.  Welcome to Cenarion Hold.  From here we will strike against the silithid where they\'re at their strongest.  I hope you\'ve come to lend a hand. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It\'s a pleasure to see you again, $N.  Your aid has provided us with a considerable boost in the security of our supply lines.  I hope you understand the importance of the logistics involved in large battle efforts such as this.' WHERE entry=7747; /* Text0_1: It\'s a pleasure to see you again, $N.  Your aid has provided us with a considerable boost in the security of our supply lines.  I hope you understand the importance of the logistics involved in large battle efforts such as this. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='How dare you commune with a Duke of the Council, worm!',Text0_1_loc9='How dare you commune with a Duke of the Council, worm!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7749; /* Text0_0: How dare you commune with a Duke of the Council, worm! */ /* Text0_1: How dare you commune with a Duke of the Council, worm! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re hunting Deathclasp, $N?  Color me impressed.  I lost two of my men to her this week alone.  Let\'s hope your luck is better than theirs.' WHERE entry=7751; /* Text0_0: You\'re hunting Deathclasp, $N?  Color me impressed.  I lost two of my men to her this week alone.  Let\'s hope your luck is better than theirs. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hey!  Thanks for saving my hide!  I think I\'ll be lying down for a while until I recover my strength.' WHERE entry=7752; /* Text0_0: Hey!  Thanks for saving my hide!  I think I\'ll be lying down for a while until I recover my strength. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Who are you?  Where am I?  I feel... so weak...' WHERE entry=7753; /* Text0_0: Who are you?  Where am I?  I feel... so weak... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What bug comes before the lords of the Council?  A bug, no doubt, wishing to be squashed!',Text0_1_loc9='What bug comes before the lords of the Council?  A bug, no doubt, wishing to be squashed!',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=7754; /* Text0_0: What bug comes before the lords of the Council?  A bug, no doubt, wishing to be squashed! */ /* Text0_1: What bug comes before the lords of the Council?  A bug, no doubt, wishing to be squashed! */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You best have a seat then, this is gonna be a long one.$B$BWhen we initially arrived in Silithus, Mistress Mar\'alith was the first of the night elves from Cenarion Hold to join the expedition. Our routine was nothing out of the ordinary: Form a party to venture into the various hives and search for lost artifacts.' WHERE entry=7755; /* Text0_0: You best have a seat then, this is gonna be a long one.$B$BWhen we initially arrived in Silithus, Mistress Mar\'alith was the first of the night elves from Cenarion Hold to join the expedition. Our routine was nothing out of the ordinary: Form a party to venture into the various hives and search for lost artifacts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It sure is! Those hives were abuzz with various silithid that were none to happy to see us.$B$BEverything was going fine until we came across a glyphed crystal in Hive\'Regal. She was drawn to it like a moth to a flame! She put her pretty little cheek up against the crystal and instantly entered a trance like state. Naturally, this worried my crew. We picked her up and carried her out of there with a quickness!' WHERE entry=7756; /* Text0_0: It sure is! Those hives were abuzz with various silithid that were none to happy to see us.$B$BEverything was going fine until we came across a glyphed crystal in Hive\'Regal. She was drawn to it like a moth to a flame! She put her pretty little cheek up against the crystal and instantly entered a trance like state. Naturally, this worried my crew. We picked her up and carried her out of there with a quickness! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We took her to the Commander with hopes that the druids of the Circle could fix her up. Sure enough, they were able to wake her up. We figured our business with the Circle was done and we could get back to work.$B$BA few weeks passed and everything was going fine. Brann was still around back then so we had a bit of order in our work structure. Then one day, out of the blue, she appeared back at our camp.$b' WHERE entry=7757; /* Text0_0: We took her to the Commander with hopes that the druids of the Circle could fix her up. Sure enough, they were able to wake her up. We figured our business with the Circle was done and we could get back to work.$B$BA few weeks passed and everything was going fine. Brann was still around back then so we had a bit of order in our work structure. Then one day, out of the blue, she appeared back at our camp.$b */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Are you daft? Who else would I be talking about? Yes, the girl - Mistress Mar\'alith. Anyhow, she was back and not in too good of a mood. That\'s when the demands started flowing.$b' WHERE entry=7758; /* Text0_0: Are you daft? Who else would I be talking about? Yes, the girl - Mistress Mar\'alith. Anyhow, she was back and not in too good of a mood. That\'s when the demands started flowing.$b */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='She demanded that we immediately head back to Hive\'Regal! Brann would have none of that sass. He told her that there\'s no way we would go back into those hives without an army backing us up. It had gotten far too dangerous. The number of those stinking insects seemed to have tripled from when we first ventured into \'em.$B$BThat\'s when Natalia lost it!' WHERE entry=7759; /* Text0_0: She demanded that we immediately head back to Hive\'Regal! Brann would have none of that sass. He told her that there\'s no way we would go back into those hives without an army backing us up. It had gotten far too dangerous. The number of those stinking insects seemed to have tripled from when we first ventured into \'em.$B$BThat\'s when Natalia lost it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What do you mean what do I mean? She went nutso! The girl went straight crazy on us. Now ordinarily I don\'t hit girls but after I recovered from the blackout, I was pretty damned angry. Brann, Rutgar, me and the monkey went positively orc on her! It\'s a miracle we were able to fend her off. She seemed almost possessed!' WHERE entry=7760; /* Text0_0: What do you mean what do I mean? She went nutso! The girl went straight crazy on us. Now ordinarily I don\'t hit girls but after I recovered from the blackout, I was pretty damned angry. Brann, Rutgar, me and the monkey went positively orc on her! It\'s a miracle we were able to fend her off. She seemed almost possessed! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Who knows? Anyhow, that was the last I saw of her. Maybe Frankal can give you better information.$B$BNot to steer off topic here as I\'m sure the work you\'re doing for the Commander is important, but we\'re onto something huge here. HUGE! Our requests to Ironforge for an army have so far fallen on deaf ears. Apparently we\'re stretched too thin in protecting the realm or some such nonsense. Once you take your report back to the Commander, come back down here with some friends. We need your help!' WHERE entry=7761; /* Text0_0: Who knows? Anyhow, that was the last I saw of her. Maybe Frankal can give you better information.$B$BNot to steer off topic here as I\'m sure the work you\'re doing for the Commander is important, but we\'re onto something huge here. HUGE! Our requests to Ironforge for an army have so far fallen on deaf ears. Apparently we\'re stretched too thin in protecting the realm or some such nonsense. Once you take your report back to the Commander, come back down here with some friends. We need your help! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Oh brother, not this again... Have a seat $g sonny:missy;.$B$BI\'m sure Rutgar has told you some of this story already so I\'ll spare you the boring details and get right down to the nitty gritty.' WHERE entry=7762; /* Text0_0: Oh brother, not this again... Have a seat $g sonny:missy;.$B$BI\'m sure Rutgar has told you some of this story already so I\'ll spare you the boring details and get right down to the nitty gritty. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Right then! So the Mistress had come back for a second go at the hives but Brann was having none of that nonsense! Before the melee began, she started talking to something or someone. Crazier still, she started chanting in a language none of us had ever heard.' WHERE entry=7763; /* Text0_0: Right then! So the Mistress had come back for a second go at the hives but Brann was having none of that nonsense! Before the melee began, she started talking to something or someone. Crazier still, she started chanting in a language none of us had ever heard. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re telling me! It\'s even stranger considering between Brann, Rutgar, me and the monkey, we know 38 different languages including a touch of Titan - both Vanir and Aesir.$B$BSo anyway, whatever she was click clacking about, it definitely wasn\'t with anyone present. She then nodded and went on the offensive! Attacked us outright!' WHERE entry=7764; /* Text0_0: You\'re telling me! It\'s even stranger considering between Brann, Rutgar, me and the monkey, we know 38 different languages including a touch of Titan - both Vanir and Aesir.$B$BSo anyway, whatever she was click clacking about, it definitely wasn\'t with anyone present. She then nodded and went on the offensive! Attacked us outright! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Listen $g sonny:missy;, I\'ll  have you know that whatever attacked us was no priestess of nothin\'! Her eyes were aglow with something evil and she was genuinely frothing at the mouth! She came in, did some kind of crazy scream that sent us all runnin\' in separate directions then started flayin\' our minds one by one. I\'d be hearin\' shadowy words in my head, watchin\' the other\'s periodically black out here and there. It was madness! We would have been done for if not for the damned monkey.' WHERE entry=7765; /* Text0_0: Listen $g sonny:missy;, I\'ll  have you know that whatever attacked us was no priestess of nothin\'! Her eyes were aglow with something evil and she was genuinely frothing at the mouth! She came in, did some kind of crazy scream that sent us all runnin\' in separate directions then started flayin\' our minds one by one. I\'d be hearin\' shadowy words in my head, watchin\' the other\'s periodically black out here and there. It was madness! We would have been done for if not for the damned monkey. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What\'s there to ask? He\'s a monkey you crazy fool. Anyhow, so yea, the monkey went into a frenzy after seein\' ol\' Brann flop into the sand face first. Nothin\' the night elf could do was stopping Glibb here from poundin\' on her noggin.' WHERE entry=7766; /* Text0_0: What\'s there to ask? He\'s a monkey you crazy fool. Anyhow, so yea, the monkey went into a frenzy after seein\' ol\' Brann flop into the sand face first. Nothin\' the night elf could do was stopping Glibb here from poundin\' on her noggin. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ll tell you \'then what.\' She went runnin\' straight for the hive. And you know what\'s crazier? Not a single damned bug got in her way or tried to stop her. She ran through them all as if she\'d been best friends with \'em for centuries.' WHERE entry=7767; /* Text0_0: I\'ll tell you \'then what.\' She went runnin\' straight for the hive. And you know what\'s crazier? Not a single damned bug got in her way or tried to stop her. She ran through them all as if she\'d been best friends with \'em for centuries. */
