UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='$N!  I hope you\'re ready to get to work, because there is much for you to do here on Sunstrider Isle.$B$BEver since the destruction of the Sunwell by Arthas and the Scourge, we have been a race adrift on a sea of uncertainty.  We teeter on the edge of oblivion.  This will change, $c, and you will learn and aid our recovery at the same time.$B$BThe Outland awaits us!' WHERE entry=7781; /* Text0_1: $N!  I hope you\'re ready to get to work, because there is much for you to do here on Sunstrider Isle.$B$BEver since the destruction of the Sunwell by Arthas and the Scourge, we have been a race adrift on a sea of uncertainty.  We teeter on the edge of oblivion.  This will change, $c, and you will learn and aid our recovery at the same time.$B$BThe Outland awaits us! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The Cenarion Circle is wise, and has delved into many of earth\'s secrets.  Craftsmen would do well to heed the words of these druids.' WHERE entry=7782; /* Text0_1: The Cenarion Circle is wise, and has delved into many of earth\'s secrets.  Craftsmen would do well to heed the words of these druids. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The ghostly figure looks at you with mistrust in her eyes and remains silent.' WHERE entry=7783; /* Text0_1: The ghostly figure looks at you with mistrust in her eyes and remains silent. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Sunspire held a beautiful vantage of the Sunwell... once.  Our lives have been turned upside down, $N, but we nonetheless carry on.  It is our way; we are survivors.$B$BIf you are to survive this upheaval... to carry on in your own right, then you MUST learn how to survive.  All blood elves must do this.  You must master your insatiable hungering for magic before it masters you.' WHERE entry=7784; /* Text0_0: The Sunspire held a beautiful vantage of the Sunwell... once.  Our lives have been turned upside down, $N, but we nonetheless carry on.  It is our way; we are survivors.$B$BIf you are to survive this upheaval... to carry on in your own right, then you MUST learn how to survive.  All blood elves must do this.  You must master your insatiable hungering for magic before it masters you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your continued service to the Blood Elves is paramount to our survival!  We must all pitch in and pull ourselves out of the mire we all find ourselves in.$B$BIf you\'re ready to work, then let\'s get started.' WHERE entry=7785; /* Text0_0: Your continued service to the Blood Elves is paramount to our survival!  We must all pitch in and pull ourselves out of the mire we all find ourselves in.$B$BIf you\'re ready to work, then let\'s get started. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Knowledge is power - TRUE power, my young friend.  You\'ll be wise to acquire as much of it as you can, and pay proper heed to those who have already done so.$B$BBefore the razing of the Sunwell, we fooled ourselves into thinking we had neared the apex of our civilization.  It took the Scourge to bring us to our knees... and in a way, back to reality.' WHERE entry=7786; /* Text0_0: Knowledge is power - TRUE power, my young friend.  You\'ll be wise to acquire as much of it as you can, and pay proper heed to those who have already done so.$B$BBefore the razing of the Sunwell, we fooled ourselves into thinking we had neared the apex of our civilization.  It took the Scourge to bring us to our knees... and in a way, back to reality. */
