' WHERE entry=7804; /* Text0_1: Ancient forces stir - forces that have not been seen or felt for thousands of years. The world weeps, $r. Perhaps a new sundering comes. A sickness born from within...$B$BThe foulness has begun to seep into our lands. From the Dream come nightmares. Nightmares to befoul us in our waking hours... */
