UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It takes a bit of practice to be this close to the silithid and go unnoticed.  I don\'t recommend trying it if you can avoid it.' WHERE entry=8063; /* Text0_0: It takes a bit of practice to be this close to the silithid and go unnoticed.  I don\'t recommend trying it if you can avoid it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t get me wrong, I\'d rather not be in a tunnel filled with silithid day in and day out, but if hiding here and watching these creatures\' movements is going to help us win the war then I\'ll do it for as long as it takes.' WHERE entry=8064; /* Text0_0: Don\'t get me wrong, I\'d rather not be in a tunnel filled with silithid day in and day out, but if hiding here and watching these creatures\' movements is going to help us win the war then I\'ll do it for as long as it takes. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Soon we shall rid Azeroth of the silithids\' abominable presence.  Their potential for destruction is much greater than what you\'ve seen firsthand, $N.  Greater, darker powers are behind their activities.' WHERE entry=8065; /* Text0_0: Soon we shall rid Azeroth of the silithids\' abominable presence.  Their potential for destruction is much greater than what you\'ve seen firsthand, $N.  Greater, darker powers are behind their activities. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='An Alliance Commendation Signet is awarded to a $g hero : heroine; who goes above and beyond the call of duty to the Alliance.  Various Commendation Officers for the factions of the Alliance are located in all of the major cities; speak with the one with whom you\'d like to raise your reputation, and give them the number of signets they ask for!$B$BBy the way, during the war effort here, if you\'d rather receive a material reward for your signets in lieu of reputation, seek out Field Marshal Snowfall.' WHERE entry=8070; /* Text0_1: An Alliance Commendation Signet is awarded to a $g hero : heroine; who goes above and beyond the call of duty to the Alliance.  Various Commendation Officers for the factions of the Alliance are located in all of the major cities; speak with the one with whom you\'d like to raise your reputation, and give them the number of signets they ask for!$B$BBy the way, during the war effort here, if you\'d rather receive a material reward for your signets in lieu of reputation, seek out Field Marshal Snowfall. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We are united in cause, $r. An ancient evil threatens to extinguish all life on Kalimdor and consume the world with its depravity... It\'s hatred of all things born of the great Shapers: The eternal Titans.$B$BWe are the first and the last lines of defense against the armies of C\'Thun. If we do not rise up and strike at our enemy, our enemy will surely destroy us.$B$BThe war effort needs you!' WHERE entry=8071; /* Text0_0: We are united in cause, $r. An ancient evil threatens to extinguish all life on Kalimdor and consume the world with its depravity... It\'s hatred of all things born of the great Shapers: The eternal Titans.$B$BWe are the first and the last lines of defense against the armies of C\'Thun. If we do not rise up and strike at our enemy, our enemy will surely destroy us.$B$BThe war effort needs you! */
