UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Try not to draw too much attention, I\'m waiting for the King to grant me audience.  Not that I mind waiting, I feel pretty safe around all these burly guards.' WHERE entry=8333; /* Text0_1: Try not to draw too much attention, I\'m waiting for the King to grant me audience.  Not that I mind waiting, I feel pretty safe around all these burly guards. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Losing my life was a danger I had come to terms with.  Losing Ysida is something I cannot endure, even after my own death.' WHERE entry=8334; /* Text0_0: Losing my life was a danger I had come to terms with.  Losing Ysida is something I cannot endure, even after my own death. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, friend!  Can I interest you in some ectoplasmic capacitors?  Or perhaps a nice omni-directional spectral assimilator? ' WHERE entry=8335; /* Text0_0: Greetings, friend!  Can I interest you in some ectoplasmic capacitors?  Or perhaps a nice omni-directional spectral assimilator? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What now?  Can\'t you see I\'m rather busy?' WHERE entry=8336; /* Text0_0: What now?  Can\'t you see I\'m rather busy? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I\'ll be fine for now, don\'t worry about me.  I\'ll find a way out of here once I\'ve performed some cleansing rituals in this room.  Foul magic taints this place, $N.' WHERE entry=8344; /* Text0_1: I\'ll be fine for now, don\'t worry about me.  I\'ll find a way out of here once I\'ve performed some cleansing rituals in this room.  Foul magic taints this place, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Our newest attraction, and at no cost to you I might add, these miniature tanks, or Tonks as we\'ve cleverly named them, can be controlled from any of the Tonk Control Consoles spread throughout the faire.$B$BAll that you have to do is activate an available control console. Each tonk will come equipped with a stock set of devices, and a random special power to unleash upon your enemy!$B$BHold epic battles with your friends, cruise around, or just cause wild mayhem... the choice is yours!' WHERE entry=8347; /* Text0_1: Our newest attraction, and at no cost to you I might add, these miniature tanks, or Tonks as we\'ve cleverly named them, can be controlled from any of the Tonk Control Consoles spread throughout the faire.$B$BAll that you have to do is activate an available control console. Each tonk will come equipped with a stock set of devices, and a random special power to unleash upon your enemy!$B$BHold epic battles with your friends, cruise around, or just cause wild mayhem... the choice is yours! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The Blastenheimer 5000 Ultra Cannon is a state-of-the-art single person projectile device. Delivering its payload at near the speed of a dragon, the cannon is the pride and joy of the Blastenheimer family, world renown for their aeronautical and combustible feats!$B$BIf you\'d like to be launched through the skies to fly free as a bird, seek out Maxima Blastenheimer on the south edge of Thunder Bluff\'s central rise. She\'ll aim you at the target far to south on Stonebull Lake!' WHERE entry=8349; /* Text0_1: The Blastenheimer 5000 Ultra Cannon is a state-of-the-art single person projectile device. Delivering its payload at near the speed of a dragon, the cannon is the pride and joy of the Blastenheimer family, world renown for their aeronautical and combustible feats!$B$BIf you\'d like to be launched through the skies to fly free as a bird, seek out Maxima Blastenheimer on the south edge of Thunder Bluff\'s central rise. She\'ll aim you at the target far to south on Stonebull Lake! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It is said that Kel\'Thuzad seeks the legendary Atiesh, greatstaff of the Guardian.$B$BYes, the very staff once held by Medivh.' WHERE entry=8350; /* Text0_1: It is said that Kel\'Thuzad seeks the legendary Atiesh, greatstaff of the Guardian.$B$BYes, the very staff once held by Medivh. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Watch your step, $r. We of the Brotherhood of the Light are not as lenient as our brethren when it comes to meting justice to those that would do this world wrong.$B$BWoe unto those that would anger Korfax.$B$BNow if you have no business with me or the other members of the Brotherhood, please leave so that we may continue our meeting. $B' WHERE entry=8351; /* Text0_0: Watch your step, $r. We of the Brotherhood of the Light are not as lenient as our brethren when it comes to meting justice to those that would do this world wrong.$B$BWoe unto those that would anger Korfax.$B$BNow if you have no business with me or the other members of the Brotherhood, please leave so that we may continue our meeting. $B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Lich King is attempting to make his presence known in our world. This must not be allowed to occur.$B' WHERE entry=8352; /* Text0_0: The Lich King is attempting to make his presence known in our world. This must not be allowed to occur.$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What is the Brotherhood of the Light? Well... We are all members of the Argent Dawn at the core - members of the Argent Dawn that aren\'t held in check by morals, guilt and useless human emotion. Consider us Scarlet Crusade minus the stupidity, lack of leadership, and blind zealotry.$B$BDon\'t let the Scarlet Commander tell you otherwise.$B$BAnd don\'t let Tyrosus know I said that... It would be a terrible shame if I had to brutally maim him should a brawl break out.$B' WHERE entry=8353; /* Text0_0: What is the Brotherhood of the Light? Well... We are all members of the Argent Dawn at the core - members of the Argent Dawn that aren\'t held in check by morals, guilt and useless human emotion. Consider us Scarlet Crusade minus the stupidity, lack of leadership, and blind zealotry.$B$BDon\'t let the Scarlet Commander tell you otherwise.$B$BAnd don\'t let Tyrosus know I said that... It would be a terrible shame if I had to brutally maim him should a brawl break out.$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The Argent Dawn might be impotent idealists but their delusional leader knows that they are outmatched. I have been sent here as an emissary of the Scarlet Crusade. An ambassador, if you will... It is doubtful that we could even dent the armies of Kel\'Thuzad - united or not - but we might be able to contain them long enough for some sort of miracle to happen.$B$BAs for me? I\'ll die in battle...$B$B<Marjhan shrugs.>$B' WHERE entry=8354; /* Text0_1: The Argent Dawn might be impotent idealists but their delusional leader knows that they are outmatched. I have been sent here as an emissary of the Scarlet Crusade. An ambassador, if you will... It is doubtful that we could even dent the armies of Kel\'Thuzad - united or not - but we might be able to contain them long enough for some sort of miracle to happen.$B$BAs for me? I\'ll die in battle...$B$B<Marjhan shrugs.>$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The title is misleading. I\'m really a very nice person once you get to know me.' WHERE entry=8355; /* Text0_0: The title is misleading. I\'m really a very nice person once you get to know me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='They almost sent my brother, Loksey, to this gathering. He cannot even take care of his hounds, let alone represent the Scarlet Crusade in a competent manner.' WHERE entry=8356; /* Text0_0: They almost sent my brother, Loksey, to this gathering. He cannot even take care of his hounds, let alone represent the Scarlet Crusade in a competent manner. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve been expec...$B$B<Rimblat coughs.>$B$BExcuse me, old habit. I am Rimblat of the Earthen Ring. ' WHERE entry=8357; /* Text0_0: I\'ve been expec...$B$B<Rimblat coughs.>$B$BExcuse me, old habit. I am Rimblat of the Earthen Ring. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Hello, $c. Please excuse me as I am having a conversation with Rimblat. He believes that even this land is not beyond saving.' WHERE entry=8358; /* Text0_1: Hello, $c. Please excuse me as I am having a conversation with Rimblat. He believes that even this land is not beyond saving. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What is it that you want, lemming? Get out of my sight before you find out why I am known as the Wrathcaster.' WHERE entry=8359; /* Text0_0: What is it that you want, lemming? Get out of my sight before you find out why I am known as the Wrathcaster. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The first suit of Dreadnaught armor was made exclusively for the Scarlet Highlord Mograine. Whilst donning the full suit, the Highlord looked himself to be a demon from the depths of the Nether.$B$BAye, \'twas quite a sight to behold as Mograine would wade into a hundred Scourge, Ashbringer held high, and come out on the other side in a cloud of dust and flames - enemies left in ashes beneath his feet."' WHERE entry=8363; /* Text0_0: The first suit of Dreadnaught armor was made exclusively for the Scarlet Highlord Mograine. Whilst donning the full suit, the Highlord looked himself to be a demon from the depths of the Nether.$B$BAye, \'twas quite a sight to behold as Mograine would wade into a hundred Scourge, Ashbringer held high, and come out on the other side in a cloud of dust and flames - enemies left in ashes beneath his feet." */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It was not until after his controversial death that the knights and warriors of Lordaeron would wear similarly fashioned suits in honor of their fallen hero. While the death of Mograine was a great victory for Kel\'Thuzad, the resulting martyrdom would be felt until the end of the war.$B$BWhere one did fall, many would rise...' WHERE entry=8364; /* Text0_0: It was not until after his controversial death that the knights and warriors of Lordaeron would wear similarly fashioned suits in honor of their fallen hero. While the death of Mograine was a great victory for Kel\'Thuzad, the resulting martyrdom would be felt until the end of the war.$B$BWhere one did fall, many would rise... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'m what you call a capitalist, $r.' WHERE entry=8366; /* Text0_0: I\'m what you call a capitalist, $r. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Oh, hello there.. um, what\'s your name?$B$BNo matter, what brings you to my home-away-from-home here out in the beautiful countryside?',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8374; /* Text0_0: Oh, hello there.. um, what\'s your name?$B$BNo matter, what brings you to my home-away-from-home here out in the beautiful countryside? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hello, $c. I trust that you are enjoying youself? What do you think of the party? I do so hope that we aren\'t running out of anything. Nothing kills a fete faster than running out of drinks and hors d\'oeuvres, wouldn\'t you say?$B$BYes, well, I must be about attending to my other guests. Do enjoy your stay.' WHERE entry=8375; /* Text0_0: Hello, $c. I trust that you are enjoying youself? What do you think of the party? I do so hope that we aren\'t running out of anything. Nothing kills a fete faster than running out of drinks and hors d\'oeuvres, wouldn\'t you say?$B$BYes, well, I must be about attending to my other guests. Do enjoy your stay. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Greetings, my $g lord : lady;. I trust that you are having a pleasant time?' WHERE entry=8378; /* Text0_1: Greetings, my $g lord : lady;. I trust that you are having a pleasant time? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Isn\'t this just so much fun? I\'m so glad that Lord Saltheril throws these parties every night, especially with all of that nastiness occurring to the south. Kind of just makes all of that go away, don\'t you think?' WHERE entry=8379; /* Text0_1: Isn\'t this just so much fun? I\'m so glad that Lord Saltheril throws these parties every night, especially with all of that nastiness occurring to the south. Kind of just makes all of that go away, don\'t you think? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Like Kel\'Thuzad, I too was once a mage of the Kirin Tor. And like Kel\'Thuzad, I seek the legendary Atiesh, greatstaff of the Guardian. Our fates are intertwined as such, $c.' WHERE entry=8388; /* Text0_1: Like Kel\'Thuzad, I too was once a mage of the Kirin Tor. And like Kel\'Thuzad, I seek the legendary Atiesh, greatstaff of the Guardian. Our fates are intertwined as such, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Progeny of Aegwynn, he that would be the last Guardian of Tirisfal... Medivh.' WHERE entry=8389; /* Text0_1: Progeny of Aegwynn, he that would be the last Guardian of Tirisfal... Medivh. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It is a story of legend and one that I do not have the time nor the inclination to retell. Just know that Medivh was the last of the Guardians. The greatstaff of Atiesh was a focal point of his power and a focal point of corruption.' WHERE entry=8390; /* Text0_1: It is a story of legend and one that I do not have the time nor the inclination to retell. Just know that Medivh was the last of the Guardians. The greatstaff of Atiesh was a focal point of his power and a focal point of corruption. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The corruption of a fallen titan. The corruption of the Destroyer. After all, the staff was forged from the seed of hate. That is, of course, what has brought me here...' WHERE entry=8391; /* Text0_1: The corruption of a fallen titan. The corruption of the Destroyer. After all, the staff was forged from the seed of hate. That is, of course, what has brought me here... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='After the fall of Karazhan, the Kirin Tor dispatched an assembly of mages to search the tower and seize all items of import... for the purposes of "research." It was then that the fabled staff was discovered and brought back to Dalaran.' WHERE entry=8392; /* Text0_1: After the fall of Karazhan, the Kirin Tor dispatched an assembly of mages to search the tower and seize all items of import... for the purposes of "research." It was then that the fabled staff was discovered and brought back to Dalaran. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='What followed were a series of tragic events, leading to the death of every Kirin Tor mage that came into contact with Atiesh.$B$BYou see, it was an artifact with sentience. A sentience granted to it by Sargeras...' WHERE entry=8393; /* Text0_1: What followed were a series of tragic events, leading to the death of every Kirin Tor mage that came into contact with Atiesh.$B$BYou see, it was an artifact with sentience. A sentience granted to it by Sargeras... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='<Angela nods.>$B$BAfter the deaths, the Six decided that the best course of action was to seal the staff behind impenetrable barriers of magic and appoint a watcher: A guardian of the staff... I would be that watcher.' WHERE entry=8394; /* Text0_1: <Angela nods.>$B$BAfter the deaths, the Six decided that the best course of action was to seal the staff behind impenetrable barriers of magic and appoint a watcher: A guardian of the staff... I would be that watcher. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='There is not much more to tell. Dalaran was nearly wholly destroyed by Archimonde, the staff lost, presumably shattered by the barrier\'s fail-safe mechanisms.$B$BThere are those that believe the staff to be the cause of Archimonde\'s reprisal.' WHERE entry=8395; /* Text0_1: There is not much more to tell. Dalaran was nearly wholly destroyed by Archimonde, the staff lost, presumably shattered by the barrier\'s fail-safe mechanisms.$B$BThere are those that believe the staff to be the cause of Archimonde\'s reprisal. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='After the fall of Dalaran, I took my leave from the Kirin Tor. I spent years watching over Atiesh, only to have my purpose amongst the Kirin Tor taken from me in one fell swoop. I would find the staff, though it might take a lifetime. That is how I came to join the Argent Dawn and why I am here now.' WHERE entry=8396; /* Text0_1: After the fall of Dalaran, I took my leave from the Kirin Tor. I spent years watching over Atiesh, only to have my purpose amongst the Kirin Tor taken from me in one fell swoop. I would find the staff, though it might take a lifetime. That is how I came to join the Argent Dawn and why I am here now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I have tracked the various fragments of the staff across this world and in doing so, discovered Kel\'Thuzad\'s plans to reform the staff. He has already collected several of the staff\'s fragments - which are being held by his most trusted lieutenants.$B$BI cannot emphasize enough the importance of keeping the greatstaff of the Guardian out of Kel\'Thuzad\'s grasp. Frankly, I do not know what the result would be, other than a catastrophe of epic proportion.' WHERE entry=8397; /* Text0_1: I have tracked the various fragments of the staff across this world and in doing so, discovered Kel\'Thuzad\'s plans to reform the staff. He has already collected several of the staff\'s fragments - which are being held by his most trusted lieutenants.$B$BI cannot emphasize enough the importance of keeping the greatstaff of the Guardian out of Kel\'Thuzad\'s grasp. Frankly, I do not know what the result would be, other than a catastrophe of epic proportion. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is power, imbecile.$B$B<Mataus\'s eyes darken.>$B$BThese fools send idiots like you into Naxxramas to retrieve desecrated armor so that they may purify it and restore the pieces to their former glory.$B$B<Mataus spits.>$B$BJust the thought of such utter stupidity brings the bile up to my throat.$B$BI too seek that armor, but in its most foul and desecrated form.' WHERE entry=8398; /* Text0_0: It is power, imbecile.$B$B<Mataus\'s eyes darken.>$B$BThese fools send idiots like you into Naxxramas to retrieve desecrated armor so that they may purify it and restore the pieces to their former glory.$B$B<Mataus spits.>$B$BJust the thought of such utter stupidity brings the bile up to my throat.$B$BI too seek that armor, but in its most foul and desecrated form. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I make no pretenses, maggot. The darkness such items hold could very well destroy the both of us. That is why the price is so high. If I\'m going to die, it\'s going to be as a rich man.$B$BAnd I don\'t give an ounce of gnoll spit how you die, only that you do as I ask. Bring me what I require and we will both benefit - or die, but I\'ve already explained this...' WHERE entry=8399; /* Text0_0: I make no pretenses, maggot. The darkness such items hold could very well destroy the both of us. That is why the price is so high. If I\'m going to die, it\'s going to be as a rich man.$B$BAnd I don\'t give an ounce of gnoll spit how you die, only that you do as I ask. Bring me what I require and we will both benefit - or die, but I\'ve already explained this... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, travelers. I have been instructed to treat any bearer of a key to Karazhan as an honored guest of the Master. Feel free to ask any questions you wish of me. How may I assist you?' WHERE entry=8401; /* Text0_0: Greetings, travelers. I have been instructed to treat any bearer of a key to Karazhan as an honored guest of the Master. Feel free to ask any questions you wish of me. How may I assist you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We\'re too merciful with the Wretched.  We ought to drive a sword through each of them.$B$BTheir boldness in Sunsail Anchorage is unpardonable.' WHERE entry=8402; /* Text0_0: We\'re too merciful with the Wretched.  We ought to drive a sword through each of them.$B$BTheir boldness in Sunsail Anchorage is unpardonable. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It\'s been a long day of cutting down the mindless Scourge that endlessly parade down the Dead Scar.  I hope you\'re here to lend a hand and not to waste my time with idle chatter.' WHERE entry=8403; /* Text0_1: It\'s been a long day of cutting down the mindless Scourge that endlessly parade down the Dead Scar.  I hope you\'re here to lend a hand and not to waste my time with idle chatter. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah, guests of the Master. I hope you\'ve been watching your step in here.' WHERE entry=8404; /* Text0_0: Ah, guests of the Master. I hope you\'ve been watching your step in here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Damn all these vermin! I don\'t suppose you could help me with this situation?' WHERE entry=8406; /* Text0_0: Damn all these vermin! I don\'t suppose you could help me with this situation? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I cannot be teachin\' a Tauren to ride a Raptor.',Text0_1_loc9='I cannot be teachin\' a Tauren to ride a Raptor.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8407; /* Text0_0: I cannot be teachin\' a Tauren to ride a Raptor. */ /* Text0_1: I cannot be teachin\' a Tauren to ride a Raptor. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Those filthy beasts are all over the place.$B$BIf you prefer hunting outdoors, you\'ll find most of them around Plaguewood and Terrordale, with a good concentration of them in the Terrorweb tunnel. They are also likely to appear at almost any Scourge encampment in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BIf you\'re a hearty dungeon crawler, you\'ll find a good lot of them in Stratholme and a few of the necrofiend variety in Scholomance.' WHERE entry=8408; /* Text0_0: Those filthy beasts are all over the place.$B$BIf you prefer hunting outdoors, you\'ll find most of them around Plaguewood and Terrordale, with a good concentration of them in the Terrorweb tunnel. They are also likely to appear at almost any Scourge encampment in the Eastern Plaguelands.$B$BIf you\'re a hearty dungeon crawler, you\'ll find a good lot of them in Stratholme and a few of the necrofiend variety in Scholomance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Are you daft? Did you miss the BONY SKELETAL CREATURES littering the landscape on your way over here?$B$B<Rohan sighs.>$B$BIf you\'re the outdoor type, you\'ll find skeletal creatures all over both the Western and Eastern Plaguelands. Trust me, you can\'t miss \'em - they certainly won\'t miss you if they get the chance.$B$BIf you\'re a dungeon type, Stratholme and Scholomance are definitely the place to be for bone fragments.' WHERE entry=8409; /* Text0_0: Are you daft? Did you miss the BONY SKELETAL CREATURES littering the landscape on your way over here?$B$B<Rohan sighs.>$B$BIf you\'re the outdoor type, you\'ll find skeletal creatures all over both the Western and Eastern Plaguelands. Trust me, you can\'t miss \'em - they certainly won\'t miss you if they get the chance.$B$BIf you\'re a dungeon type, Stratholme and Scholomance are definitely the place to be for bone fragments. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Another lovely, gloomy day here in Tranquillien, wouldn\'t you say, $c?$B$BWhat can I do for you?' WHERE entry=8410; /* Text0_1: Another lovely, gloomy day here in Tranquillien, wouldn\'t you say, $c?$B$BWhat can I do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='No greater freedom than to soar through the skies, $c. What can I do for you today?' WHERE entry=8411; /* Text0_0: No greater freedom than to soar through the skies, $c. What can I do for you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hello, friend. How may I be of service to you today?',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8412; /* Text0_0: Hello, friend. How may I be of service to you today? */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Heading down to Tranquillien today, $c, or is there something else that I can do for you?' WHERE entry=8413; /* Text0_1: Heading down to Tranquillien today, $c, or is there something else that I can do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ah, a good question.$B$BIf you prefer hunting in the great outdoors, there are elementals here in the Plaguelands, Azshara, Burning Steppes, Felwood, Silithus, Winterspring, and even Un\'Goro Crater.$B$BIf you are the type that laughs in the face of danger, then perhaps you should visit Dire Maul. I have heard that a great many elemental abberations exist within its walls. You would also do well in seeking out the elementals employed by the Dark Iron dwarves of Blackrock Depths.' WHERE entry=8414; /* Text0_1: Ah, a good question.$B$BIf you prefer hunting in the great outdoors, there are elementals here in the Plaguelands, Azshara, Burning Steppes, Felwood, Silithus, Winterspring, and even Un\'Goro Crater.$B$BIf you are the type that laughs in the face of danger, then perhaps you should visit Dire Maul. I have heard that a great many elemental abberations exist within its walls. You would also do well in seeking out the elementals employed by the Dark Iron dwarves of Blackrock Depths. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Is this a serious question? You really don\'t know?$B$BIf you are the cowardly sort, afraid to get their hands too dirty, you will find Dark Iron scraps on the creatures in the Burning Steppes and Searing Gorge.$B$BIf you\'re the bloodthirsty adventuring type, the dungeons of Blackrock Spire and Blackrock Depths hold quite a large supply of the scraps.' WHERE entry=8415; /* Text0_0: Is this a serious question? You really don\'t know?$B$BIf you are the cowardly sort, afraid to get their hands too dirty, you will find Dark Iron scraps on the creatures in the Burning Steppes and Searing Gorge.$B$BIf you\'re the bloodthirsty adventuring type, the dungeons of Blackrock Spire and Blackrock Depths hold quite a large supply of the scraps. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='If you are one that prefers to hunt in the outdoor world, both Felwood\'s treants and Un\'Goro\'s lashers are an excellent source of fronds.$B$BIf you are more of a risk-taker, the eastern and western wings of Dire Maul will provide you with a nearly limitless supply of savage fronds.' WHERE entry=8416; /* Text0_1: If you are one that prefers to hunt in the outdoor world, both Felwood\'s treants and Un\'Goro\'s lashers are an excellent source of fronds.$B$BIf you are more of a risk-taker, the eastern and western wings of Dire Maul will provide you with a nearly limitless supply of savage fronds. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='$C, look what they\'ve done to our beloved land. The Scourge must be destroyed!' WHERE entry=8417; /* Text0_0: $C, look what they\'ve done to our beloved land. The Scourge must be destroyed! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It\'s going to take a bit of work, but I think we can save this blood elf\'s life.' WHERE entry=8418; /* Text0_1: It\'s going to take a bit of work, but I think we can save this blood elf\'s life. */
