UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Such a delight to see you again, $c. No, really. You\'re the reason that I\'m making money here, hand over fist.$B$BNow, what can I sell to you today?' WHERE entry=8432; /* Text0_0: Such a delight to see you again, $c. No, really. You\'re the reason that I\'m making money here, hand over fist.$B$BNow, what can I sell to you today? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to Tranquillien, $c. I apologize for the state that you find it in. As you can see, we\'ve been having some trouble, but the Forsaken, and their Lady Sylvanas Windrunner, have been gracious enough to lend us a great deal of assistance in our time of need.$B$BIf you can lend a hand please do not hesitate to do so. We can use all of the help that we can get in our struggle against the myriad forces arrayed against us.' WHERE entry=8433; /* Text0_1: Welcome to Tranquillien, $c. I apologize for the state that you find it in. As you can see, we\'ve been having some trouble, but the Forsaken, and their Lady Sylvanas Windrunner, have been gracious enough to lend us a great deal of assistance in our time of need.$B$BIf you can lend a hand please do not hesitate to do so. We can use all of the help that we can get in our struggle against the myriad forces arrayed against us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The time has come for Horde and Alliance to look towards the north and the invasion of the Scourge. In recent days, territories across Kalimdor and the Eastern Kindgoms have come under attack. Will you take up arms to save your land from destruction at their hands?' WHERE entry=8434; /* Text0_0: The time has come for Horde and Alliance to look towards the north and the invasion of the Scourge. In recent days, territories across Kalimdor and the Eastern Kindgoms have come under attack. Will you take up arms to save your land from destruction at their hands? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t be afraid of the sword, nubling. It\'s the mutton that gets ya!' WHERE entry=8435; /* Text0_0: Don\'t be afraid of the sword, nubling. It\'s the mutton that gets ya! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Terrible thing, what happened to them mules... Metz is gonna have my hide for this failure.' WHERE entry=8438; /* Text0_0: Terrible thing, what happened to them mules... Metz is gonna have my hide for this failure. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It is very important that we find out what the the night elves are up to, $c! Please concentrate all of your efforts toward that end.' WHERE entry=8439; /* Text0_1: It is very important that we find out what the the night elves are up to, $c! Please concentrate all of your efforts toward that end. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We are most pleased with your actions against the night elves. When you uncovered their plot to use the ley-line nexi and their so-called moon crystals to spy upon us, you strengthened our position here by an order of magnitude.$B$BYou have our gratitude, $N.' WHERE entry=8440; /* Text0_1: We are most pleased with your actions against the night elves. When you uncovered their plot to use the ley-line nexi and their so-called moon crystals to spy upon us, you strengthened our position here by an order of magnitude.$B$BYou have our gratitude, $N. */
