UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well met, $r. I am here as a resource of advice for the High Executor to make use of as he will. I am confident that together we can forge the Horde into something that is even stronger than before and turn back the Scourge menace once and for all!' WHERE entry=8462; /* Text0_0: Well met, $r. I am here as a resource of advice for the High Executor to make use of as he will. I am confident that together we can forge the Horde into something that is even stronger than before and turn back the Scourge menace once and for all! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='<Varnis coughs violently as the restorative draught takes effect.>$B$BThank you for rescuing me.  I must go back to Tranquillien at once!' WHERE entry=8463; /* Text0_0: <Varnis coughs violently as the restorative draught takes effect.>$B$BThank you for rescuing me.  I must go back to Tranquillien at once! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The drafts of fresh air that blow from Eversong from time to time really upset my stomach, if you know what I mean.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8464; /* Text0_0: The drafts of fresh air that blow from Eversong from time to time really upset my stomach, if you know what I mean. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='If it is a matter of import that you wish to speak on, $c, it may be more appropriate to seek an audience with Dame Auriferous. I warn you though, she is very busy and you may be in for quite a wait.' WHERE entry=8466; /* Text0_1: If it is a matter of import that you wish to speak on, $c, it may be more appropriate to seek an audience with Dame Auriferous. I warn you though, she is very busy and you may be in for quite a wait. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Normally it would not be my place to speak with you directly; rather, you would seek an audience with milady. However, I did give you a task directly, so what is it that we need to discuss?' WHERE entry=8467; /* Text0_1: Normally it would not be my place to speak with you directly; rather, you would seek an audience with milady. However, I did give you a task directly, so what is it that we need to discuss? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='$C, Dame Auriferous has conveyed to me her great pleasure in the service that you have done us in the past. She wishes to extend to you her hope that you will continue to be a champion of sin\'dorei interests here in the Ghostlands.' WHERE entry=8468; /* Text0_1: $C, Dame Auriferous has conveyed to me her great pleasure in the service that you have done us in the past. She wishes to extend to you her hope that you will continue to be a champion of sin\'dorei interests here in the Ghostlands. */
