UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We\'ve important work to do, $N.  Let us attack our enemies while their guard is down.  Let us show them that sin\'dorei vengeance never forgets nor forgives.' WHERE entry=8470; /* Text0_1: We\'ve important work to do, $N.  Let us attack our enemies while their guard is down.  Let us show them that sin\'dorei vengeance never forgets nor forgives. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The tides of war have come again. From the cold north, the Lich King\'s necropolises have laid siege to our lands.  He and his cursed general, Kel\'Thuzad, send flying necropolises to invade across the world.' WHERE entry=8471; /* Text0_0: The tides of war have come again. From the cold north, the Lich King\'s necropolises have laid siege to our lands.  He and his cursed general, Kel\'Thuzad, send flying necropolises to invade across the world. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Well this is troublesome! How am I supposed to collect the ore samples for the magisters if the mines have been overrun with gnoll vermin?' WHERE entry=8472; /* Text0_1: Well this is troublesome! How am I supposed to collect the ore samples for the magisters if the mines have been overrun with gnoll vermin? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Where could she possibly be? I sent my apprentice, Shatharia, to the Underlight Mines to the west quite some time ago. We need those ore samples back, and fast or our experiment is going to fail!',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8474; /* Text0_0: Where could she possibly be? I sent my apprentice, Shatharia, to the Underlight Mines to the west quite some time ago. We need those ore samples back, and fast or our experiment is going to fail! */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Without delivery of the Underlight ore in such a timely fashion, our research would have failed.$B$BJust wait until Shatharia shows her head here again. I\'ve got some interesting tasks for her, you can be sure of it!' WHERE entry=8475; /* Text0_0: Without delivery of the Underlight ore in such a timely fashion, our research would have failed.$B$BJust wait until Shatharia shows her head here again. I\'ve got some interesting tasks for her, you can be sure of it! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Sin\'dorei have lost far too much in the past years.  Our land, our homes, even our identities...$B$BIt\'s about time we started taking it all back.' WHERE entry=8476; /* Text0_1: Sin\'dorei have lost far too much in the past years.  Our land, our homes, even our identities...$B$BIt\'s about time we started taking it all back. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Before we can overcome external obstacles like the Scourge and the Amani trolls, we must overcome obstacles from within.  The Wretched have been a nuisance for long enough; it is time we vanquished them.' WHERE entry=8477; /* Text0_0: Before we can overcome external obstacles like the Scourge and the Amani trolls, we must overcome obstacles from within.  The Wretched have been a nuisance for long enough; it is time we vanquished them. */
