UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Kel\'Thuzad has put forth considerable effort in attempting to reform the staff. The pieces were once scattered across this world, from Kalimdor to the South Seas. I myself held twenty of the pieces at one point in time - until they were stolen from me by Kel\'Thuzad\'s minions. It is why I am here.' WHERE entry=8530; /* Text0_0: Kel\'Thuzad has put forth considerable effort in attempting to reform the staff. The pieces were once scattered across this world, from Kalimdor to the South Seas. I myself held twenty of the pieces at one point in time - until they were stolen from me by Kel\'Thuzad\'s minions. It is why I am here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Haven\'t you been listening? No, I very much doubt we would be having this conversation had Kel\'Thuzad formed the staff. Kel\'Thuzad holds the head. His underlings hold forty splinters of Atiesh. The last piece - the base - was uncovered by Brann Bronzebeard. He was last seen in the Silithus desert; undoubtedly doing his best to stay as far away as possible from the relentless seekers Kel\'Thuzad has dispatched into the world.' WHERE entry=8531; /* Text0_0: Haven\'t you been listening? No, I very much doubt we would be having this conversation had Kel\'Thuzad formed the staff. Kel\'Thuzad holds the head. His underlings hold forty splinters of Atiesh. The last piece - the base - was uncovered by Brann Bronzebeard. He was last seen in the Silithus desert; undoubtedly doing his best to stay as far away as possible from the relentless seekers Kel\'Thuzad has dispatched into the world. */
