UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We must maintain a state of vigilance, $c! Between Dar\'Khan the Betrayer and his Scourge, and the Shadowpine trolls backed by the might of Zul\'Aman, we\'re barely keeping our heads above water here. We really shouldn\'t have to be dividing our attentions!$B$BI hope you\'re here to help.' WHERE entry=8569; /* Text0_1: We must maintain a state of vigilance, $c! Between Dar\'Khan the Betrayer and his Scourge, and the Shadowpine trolls backed by the might of Zul\'Aman, we\'re barely keeping our heads above water here. We really shouldn\'t have to be dividing our attentions!$B$BI hope you\'re here to help. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I\'m glad that you\'re here to help, $c. The faster we can deal with these trolls, the faster we\'ll get to send the scourge back to where they came from.' WHERE entry=8570; /* Text0_1: I\'m glad that you\'re here to help, $c. The faster we can deal with these trolls, the faster we\'ll get to send the scourge back to where they came from. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='One set of trolls dealt with, one yet to go. You have no idea how much I appreciate what you\'re doing, $N! Before you came along I didn\'t think we\'d ever get the Shadowpine problem under control.' WHERE entry=8571; /* Text0_1: One set of trolls dealt with, one yet to go. You have no idea how much I appreciate what you\'re doing, $N! Before you came along I didn\'t think we\'d ever get the Shadowpine problem under control. */
