UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Though we\'ve arrived at the promised land, $N, much work remains to be done.  Our people won\'t reach Kael\'thas if we lunge desperately across Outland.$B$BSafe routes must be found, resources must be secured and our enemies must be avoided or destroyed.' WHERE entry=8659; /* Text0_0: Though we\'ve arrived at the promised land, $N, much work remains to be done.  Our people won\'t reach Kael\'thas if we lunge desperately across Outland.$B$BSafe routes must be found, resources must be secured and our enemies must be avoided or destroyed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What I wouldn\'t give for a healing crystal right about now!' WHERE entry=8662; /* Text0_0: What I wouldn\'t give for a healing crystal right about now! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Thank you for delivering that list!  My leg is almost recovered enough that I\'ll be able to walk back to the crash site.' WHERE entry=8663; /* Text0_0: Thank you for delivering that list!  My leg is almost recovered enough that I\'ll be able to walk back to the crash site. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='How are we ever going to get out of here?' WHERE entry=8664; /* Text0_1: How are we ever going to get out of here? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Thank you for taking care of the lake, the lashers and the owlkin, $c.' WHERE entry=8665; /* Text0_1: Thank you for taking care of the lake, the lashers and the owlkin, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='None will question your actions, $c.  You did what had to be done.' WHERE entry=8666; /* Text0_1: None will question your actions, $c.  You did what had to be done. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It is good to see you alive and well, $N!' WHERE entry=8667; /* Text0_0: It is good to see you alive and well, $N! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Thank you again for replenishing our healing crystals. I hear that you\'re helping out all over the place. Keep up the good work!' WHERE entry=8669; /* Text0_0: Thank you again for replenishing our healing crystals. I hear that you\'re helping out all over the place. Keep up the good work! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Mirren and I are two of the very best hunters on either side of the Dark Portal.  Stick around, you might learn a thing or two.' WHERE entry=8672; /* Text0_0: Mirren and I are two of the very best hunters on either side of the Dark Portal.  Stick around, you might learn a thing or two. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I hope yer not here for our ale.  We\'re not sharing and that\'s final!$B$BIt\'s not our fault no one had the good sense to bring beer to Outland but us.' WHERE entry=8673; /* Text0_0: I hope yer not here for our ale.  We\'re not sharing and that\'s final!$B$BIt\'s not our fault no one had the good sense to bring beer to Outland but us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Here\'s to hoping not all of Outland is as barren as this region.  This is quite a change from the green grasslands and forests of Eversong.' WHERE entry=8674; /* Text0_1: Here\'s to hoping not all of Outland is as barren as this region.  This is quite a change from the green grasslands and forests of Eversong. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There exist in Outland demonic presences much more powerful than anything we\'d ever seen in the old world.$B$BGreat power shall come to those who do not shy away from it, but learn to harness and master its strength.' WHERE entry=8675; /* Text0_0: There exist in Outland demonic presences much more powerful than anything we\'d ever seen in the old world.$B$BGreat power shall come to those who do not shy away from it, but learn to harness and master its strength. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I was born here, $r. This is my world - all that I know... As a boy, my mother and father would regale me with tales of your world and the splendor it held. How I longed to leave this place.$B$BAlas, fate is a cruel mistress. My mother and father have long since passed, buried in this very graveyard. I remain to uphold their honor and the honor of my family - the Sons of Lothar.' WHERE entry=8676; /* Text0_0: I was born here, $r. This is my world - all that I know... As a boy, my mother and father would regale me with tales of your world and the splendor it held. How I longed to leave this place.$B$BAlas, fate is a cruel mistress. My mother and father have long since passed, buried in this very graveyard. I remain to uphold their honor and the honor of my family - the Sons of Lothar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='How may I serve?',Text0_1_loc9='How may I serve?',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=8678; /* Text0_0: How may I serve? */ /* Text0_1: How may I serve? */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Outland just oozes with magical energy, it\'s in the very air.  Can you feel it, $N?  I can\'t think of a place better suited to our race.  Soon the sin\'dorei shall have a new land to call our own!' WHERE entry=8680; /* Text0_0: Outland just oozes with magical energy, it\'s in the very air.  Can you feel it, $N?  I can\'t think of a place better suited to our race.  Soon the sin\'dorei shall have a new land to call our own! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='My husband\'s been missing for days.  We went on this pilgrimage together; we were supposed to finish it together.$B$BAll this worry has gotten me tapping into mana crystals more often than I really should.' WHERE entry=8681; /* Text0_1: My husband\'s been missing for days.  We went on this pilgrimage together; we were supposed to finish it together.$B$BAll this worry has gotten me tapping into mana crystals more often than I really should. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Dragonhawks, if raised properly, are really quite tame.  Don\'t you think that is fascinating?  To be so friendly and companionable if raised right and so vicious and deadly in the wild...I just love them so much.' WHERE entry=8682; /* Text0_1: Dragonhawks, if raised properly, are really quite tame.  Don\'t you think that is fascinating?  To be so friendly and companionable if raised right and so vicious and deadly in the wild...I just love them so much. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Don\'t... worry... about me...' WHERE entry=8683; /* Text0_0: Don\'t... worry... about me... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I really don\'t think our situation is so bad.  I am certain it will all be rectified soon and the Sunwell\'s power will be restored.  It just can\'t possibly be as bad as everyone is making it out to be.' WHERE entry=8684; /* Text0_1: I really don\'t think our situation is so bad.  I am certain it will all be rectified soon and the Sunwell\'s power will be restored.  It just can\'t possibly be as bad as everyone is making it out to be. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Befriending the Sunstriders has paid off; I get to conduct research with subjects I can only find in Outland and they get... my charming personality and rugged good looks.' WHERE entry=8685; /* Text0_0: Befriending the Sunstriders has paid off; I get to conduct research with subjects I can only find in Outland and they get... my charming personality and rugged good looks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I was only an infant when my father was deployed to this wasteland. All that I have ever known of him is what others have told me.$B$BDo your dreams change, $N? Mine do not. I have one dream: A crimson skyline envelops me as Legion, numbering beyond comprehension, battle in the distance. I kneel before the body of a man, presumably my father, and weep. As he is gasping for air, his body wholly crushed, he whispers something. Despite every effort, I am unable to hear what he is trying to tell me.' WHERE entry=8688; /* Text0_0: I was only an infant when my father was deployed to this wasteland. All that I have ever known of him is what others have told me.$B$BDo your dreams change, $N? Mine do not. I have one dream: A crimson skyline envelops me as Legion, numbering beyond comprehension, battle in the distance. I kneel before the body of a man, presumably my father, and weep. As he is gasping for air, his body wholly crushed, he whispers something. Despite every effort, I am unable to hear what he is trying to tell me. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You think I\'m being cruel to this worm?$B$BThey\'ve killed two of my men this month!  We\'re too kind to this Wretched scum.' WHERE entry=8698; /* Text0_0: You think I\'m being cruel to this worm?$B$BThey\'ve killed two of my men this month!  We\'re too kind to this Wretched scum. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to Fairbreeze Village.  Silvermoon\'s all but given up on us, but we refuse to leave.  This is our home.' WHERE entry=8699; /* Text0_1: Welcome to Fairbreeze Village.  Silvermoon\'s all but given up on us, but we refuse to leave.  This is our home. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='My job consists of one task and one task only: ensuring that the West Sanctum runs smoothly.$B$BYou\'ll have to excuse my temper but, as you can see, the situation here is a bit out of hand.'Text1_1_loc9='Could night elf saboteurs be behind this?  I doubt it.  With the load we\'ve been putting on the West Sanctum it was only a matter of time until something went wrong.' WHERE entry=8700; /* Text0_1: My job consists of one task and one task only: ensuring that the West Sanctum runs smoothly.$B$BYou\'ll have to excuse my temper but, as you can see, the situation here is a bit out of hand. */ /* Text1_1: Could night elf saboteurs be behind this?  I doubt it.  With the load we\'ve been putting on the West Sanctum it was only a matter of time until something went wrong. */
