UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='How embarrassing to be taken as a pet by a hunter!$B$BI owe you my life, but please, trouble yourself no longer with my welfare.  Now that you\'ve freed me from Musel\'ek, I\'ll be able to find my way out.  Maybe I\'ll pick up Rayge along the way.' WHERE entry=9125; /* Text0_0: How embarrassing to be taken as a pet by a hunter!$B$BI owe you my life, but please, trouble yourself no longer with my welfare.  Now that you\'ve freed me from Musel\'ek, I\'ll be able to find my way out.  Maybe I\'ll pick up Rayge along the way. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='May the Light bend to your will in all endeavors.' WHERE entry=9127; /* Text0_1: May the Light bend to your will in all endeavors. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='All things in nature exists in an interconnected web; an ecology.  If we\'re careful not to disturb it, and simply observe, we may be fortunate to piece together the complex relationship between the diverse organisms around us.$B$BOnce we have that understanding, we can take the appropriate actions to ensure the wellbeing of all creatures.  Interfere without that knowledge, and we\'ll surely cause destruction.$B$BI am here to observe the complex interactions between the sporelings and the bog lords.' WHERE entry=9128; /* Text0_1: All things in nature exists in an interconnected web; an ecology.  If we\'re careful not to disturb it, and simply observe, we may be fortunate to piece together the complex relationship between the diverse organisms around us.$B$BOnce we have that understanding, we can take the appropriate actions to ensure the wellbeing of all creatures.  Interfere without that knowledge, and we\'ll surely cause destruction.$B$BI am here to observe the complex interactions between the sporelings and the bog lords. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='<Vindicator Aesom salutes you.>$B$BHave you spoken with Admetius? I believe he was inquiring as to your whereabouts.' WHERE entry=9130; /* Text0_0: <Vindicator Aesom salutes you.>$B$BHave you spoken with Admetius? I believe he was inquiring as to your whereabouts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The druids protect me from the naga and evil Lost Ones.  In exchange, I teach them about the plants and animals of the marsh.' WHERE entry=9131; /* Text0_0: The druids protect me from the naga and evil Lost Ones.  In exchange, I teach them about the plants and animals of the marsh. */
