UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I humbly welcome you to our temple, spirit.' WHERE entry=9226; /* Text0_0: I humbly welcome you to our temple, spirit. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Treat with the draenei, the people who turned their backs on us while we suffered? I think not.$B$BA true spirit does not speak thus! Reveal yourself, impostor. Who sent you?' WHERE entry=9227; /* Text0_0: Treat with the draenei, the people who turned their backs on us while we suffered? I think not.$B$BA true spirit does not speak thus! Reveal yourself, impostor. Who sent you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='So we\'re to trust people who would insult us with this deception? Do the draenei think so little of us that they must resort to trickery to get our attention?$B$BWe\'re aware of their desire to \'redeem\' us, but my people want none of their redemption. We are capable of standing on our own and we will pursue our destiny as a proud and separate people. Carry this message to your allies.' WHERE entry=9229; /* Text0_0: So we\'re to trust people who would insult us with this deception? Do the draenei think so little of us that they must resort to trickery to get our attention?$B$BWe\'re aware of their desire to \'redeem\' us, but my people want none of their redemption. We are capable of standing on our own and we will pursue our destiny as a proud and separate people. Carry this message to your allies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Burning Legion presses us hard, but our defenses hold. Every moment we keep Archimonde away from the World Tree brings us closer to victory.' WHERE entry=9230; /* Text0_0: The Burning Legion presses us hard, but our defenses hold. Every moment we keep Archimonde away from the World Tree brings us closer to victory. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Good. Be sure they understand.$B$BNow, I would appreciate it if you would leave my temple in peace.' WHERE entry=9231; /* Text0_0: Good. Be sure they understand.$B$BNow, I would appreciate it if you would leave my temple in peace. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to the Orebor Harborage, friend. You have nothing to fear here. We are Broken, but we are not your enemies.$B$BI am Ikuti of the Kurenai, a group of Broken who desire to reestablish ties with our draenei brothers and their newfound allies.' WHERE entry=9235; /* Text0_0: Welcome to the Orebor Harborage, friend. You have nothing to fear here. We are Broken, but we are not your enemies.$B$BI am Ikuti of the Kurenai, a group of Broken who desire to reestablish ties with our draenei brothers and their newfound allies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Maktu doesn\'t recognize you, $r, but he is pleased to meet you. If ever you need to buy or repair armor, look no further than Maktu.' WHERE entry=9236; /* Text0_0: Maktu doesn\'t recognize you, $r, but he is pleased to meet you. If ever you need to buy or repair armor, look no further than Maktu. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Memories of this temple shroud my mind like a thick haze, yet I cannot assemble them into a coherent story. This place meant something to me once. Until I can restore that memory, I will feel as though a part of me is missing.$B$BPerhaps the draenei can help me recover what I\'ve lost.' WHERE entry=9237; /* Text0_0: Memories of this temple shroud my mind like a thick haze, yet I cannot assemble them into a coherent story. This place meant something to me once. Until I can restore that memory, I will feel as though a part of me is missing.$B$BPerhaps the draenei can help me recover what I\'ve lost. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There are some who call me \'Tim,\' but to my friends, I am \'the specialist.\'' WHERE entry=9238; /* Text0_0: There are some who call me \'Tim,\' but to my friends, I am \'the specialist.\' */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you have to ask, you don\'t know me anywhere near well enough to be using that appellation.' WHERE entry=9239; /* Text0_0: If you have to ask, you don\'t know me anywhere near well enough to be using that appellation. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings, $c.  You seek to push yourself to the limits of your hunting prowess?  Look no further.$B$BHemet Nesingwary has assembled the finest expedition the remnant of this world has ever known.  Join us on safari if you dare.' WHERE entry=9240; /* Text0_0: Greetings, $c.  You seek to push yourself to the limits of your hunting prowess?  Look no further.$B$BHemet Nesingwary has assembled the finest expedition the remnant of this world has ever known.  Join us on safari if you dare. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do not be fooled by the ruins surrounding us, $c.  Dalaran is as powerful as ever.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9241; /* Text0_0: Do not be fooled by the ruins surrounding us, $c.  Dalaran is as powerful as ever. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Karazhan is more than a mere building, $N.  If you traced the ley-lines traversing Azeroth you would find that they all converge right about there.$B$B<Alturus points at an invisible spot below the tower.>$B$BFascinating, isn\'t it?',Text1_0_loc9='Archmage Alvareux once wrote a treatise exploring a fascinating theory.  He proposed the existence of an exact copy of Karazhan in a world other than our own and that both somehow shared the same space.$B$BHe went mad soon after.  A real pity.' WHERE entry=9242; /* Text0_0: Karazhan is more than a mere building, $N.  If you traced the ley-lines traversing Azeroth you would find that they all converge right about there.$B$B<Alturus points at an invisible spot below the tower.>$B$BFascinating, isn\'t it? */ /* Text1_0: Archmage Alvareux once wrote a treatise exploring a fascinating theory.  He proposed the existence of an exact copy of Karazhan in a world other than our own and that both somehow shared the same space.$B$BHe went mad soon after.  A real pity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The naaru are wise beyond our understanding.  I\'ve learned more from A\'dal in the last five months than all the years I spent in the libraries of Dalaran.' WHERE entry=9243; /* Text0_0: The naaru are wise beyond our understanding.  I\'ve learned more from A\'dal in the last five months than all the years I spent in the libraries of Dalaran. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Bounties for notorious criminals and vicious animals are posted here. It would be much too dangerous for you to pursue the bounty posted here right now, but check the board again as you gain strength.' WHERE entry=9244; /* Text0_0: Bounties for notorious criminals and vicious animals are posted here. It would be much too dangerous for you to pursue the bounty posted here right now, but check the board again as you gain strength. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:Слова "РАЗЫСКИВАЕТСЯ: Коготь Смерти" перечеркнуты красными чернилами. Ниже красуется новая надпись: "Эту награду $gполучил:получила; $N, героически $gпобедивший:победившая; ужасное чудовище".',Text0_1_loc9='A thick red slash has been drawn across the words WANTED: Deathclaw.  "This bounty has been claimed by the heroic $N, who has overcome the fearsome beast," declares more writing in the same red ink.' WHERE entry=9245; /* Text0_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text0:Слова "РАЗЫСКИВАЕТСЯ: Коготь Смерти" перечеркнуты красными чернилами. Ниже красуется новая надпись: "Эту награду $gполучил:получила; $N, героически $gпобедивший:победившая; ужасное чудовище". */ /* Text0_1: A thick red slash has been drawn across the words WANTED: Deathclaw.  "This bounty has been claimed by the heroic $N, who has overcome the fearsome beast," declares more writing in the same red ink. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This sign contains various announcements and notices of rewards.' WHERE entry=9246; /* Text0_0: This sign contains various announcements and notices of rewards. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to Zabra\'jin, $c. I am Shadow Hunter Denjai, overseer of this outpost and commander of the Darkspear forces in Zangarmarsh.' WHERE entry=9248; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Zabra\'jin, $c. I am Shadow Hunter Denjai, overseer of this outpost and commander of the Darkspear forces in Zangarmarsh. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Now don\'t you be thinkin\' about tryin\' to make off with me baby murlocs! I got the eyes of a hawk and ears like... ears like... like somethin\' with mighty powerful ears!' WHERE entry=9249; /* Text0_0: Now don\'t you be thinkin\' about tryin\' to make off with me baby murlocs! I got the eyes of a hawk and ears like... ears like... like somethin\' with mighty powerful ears! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Tor\'gash believes he can see the future in the entrails of birds, or by tossing the knucklebones of his ancestors. Really, all you need to do is ask the spirits. But don\'t try telling him that, $N. He\'s very stubborn.' WHERE entry=9250; /* Text0_1: Tor\'gash believes he can see the future in the entrails of birds, or by tossing the knucklebones of his ancestors. Really, all you need to do is ask the spirits. But don\'t try telling him that, $N. He\'s very stubborn. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve proven yourself a very capable game hunter, $N.  But there\'s still one beastie that haunts your dreams... Tusker!' WHERE entry=9256; /* Text0_0: You\'ve proven yourself a very capable game hunter, $N.  But there\'s still one beastie that haunts your dreams... Tusker! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'ve bagged them all: Bach\'lor, Banthar, Gutripper, and even the mighty Tusker!  You\'re truly the finest big game hunter that I know!' WHERE entry=9257; /* Text0_0: You\'ve bagged them all: Bach\'lor, Banthar, Gutripper, and even the mighty Tusker!  You\'re truly the finest big game hunter that I know! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There I was tumbling in a patch of prickly undergrowth with a talbuk stag, hand-to-hand, only my sharp knife...<cough>... and keen hunter\'s intellect to save me.$B$BAll of a sudden I\'m jumped by a pair of fierce windroc hunters that came at me from the skies!  Their cowardly attack...<cough>... didn\'t help them any though.$B$BAnd while I have their beaks as trophies, I received an infected scratch out of the ordeal.  Kind of nasty, and I\'m in a lot of pain, but I\'m sure it\'ll heal up in a day or two.' WHERE entry=9258; /* Text0_0: There I was tumbling in a patch of prickly undergrowth with a talbuk stag, hand-to-hand, only my sharp knife...<cough>... and keen hunter\'s intellect to save me.$B$BAll of a sudden I\'m jumped by a pair of fierce windroc hunters that came at me from the skies!  Their cowardly attack...<cough>... didn\'t help them any though.$B$BAnd while I have their beaks as trophies, I received an infected scratch out of the ordeal.  Kind of nasty, and I\'m in a lot of pain, but I\'m sure it\'ll heal up in a day or two. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The first time I saw mushrooms taller than trees, I wasn\'t so sure I could call this place home. After a while you just stop noticing.' WHERE entry=9259; /* Text0_0: The first time I saw mushrooms taller than trees, I wasn\'t so sure I could call this place home. After a while you just stop noticing. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Don\'t forget to take some time out to fish while you\'re in Zangarmarsh. You never know when you\'ll see water again.' WHERE entry=9260; /* Text0_1: Don\'t forget to take some time out to fish while you\'re in Zangarmarsh. You never know when you\'ll see water again. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Telredor was once a secluded retreat for draenei priests and pilgrims. The resident priests seldom received visitors.$B$BWhen the orcs started to attack draenei settlements, refugees began to arrive in larger numbers. Anchorite Ahuurn and the others transformed Telredor from a shrine into a safe haven. Many draenei, myself included, owe our survival to his efforts.' WHERE entry=9261; /* Text0_0: Telredor was once a secluded retreat for draenei priests and pilgrims. The resident priests seldom received visitors.$B$BWhen the orcs started to attack draenei settlements, refugees began to arrive in larger numbers. Anchorite Ahuurn and the others transformed Telredor from a shrine into a safe haven. Many draenei, myself included, owe our survival to his efforts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The view from the top of Telredor is magnificent, isn\'t it?' WHERE entry=9262; /* Text0_1: The view from the top of Telredor is magnificent, isn\'t it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to Telredor, $c. If you need anything, don\'t hesitate to ask.' WHERE entry=9263; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Telredor, $c. If you need anything, don\'t hesitate to ask. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve never seen so many different kinds of mushrooms in one place. Given enough time, I\'m sure I could find a use for all of them.' WHERE entry=9264; /* Text0_0: I\'ve never seen so many different kinds of mushrooms in one place. Given enough time, I\'m sure I could find a use for all of them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Telredor has seen more change in the last 20 years than it did in prior centuries. I cannot complain, $N, for the world has changed far more in that time.$B$BThe Light has brought me friends and companions I could not have met as a cloistered priest. Learn what you can of the past in your time here. It will help you to understand where your journey is leading you.' WHERE entry=9265; /* Text0_0: Telredor has seen more change in the last 20 years than it did in prior centuries. I cannot complain, $N, for the world has changed far more in that time.$B$BThe Light has brought me friends and companions I could not have met as a cloistered priest. Learn what you can of the past in your time here. It will help you to understand where your journey is leading you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Shadow Hunter Denjai sent me here with a small contingent of builders and warriors to establish this outpost. We\'ve barely finished building it and he\'s already asking for reports!$B$BIf you need supplies, I can offer a few things, but we\'re still waiting for our first shipment.' WHERE entry=9267; /* Text0_0: Shadow Hunter Denjai sent me here with a small contingent of builders and warriors to establish this outpost. We\'ve barely finished building it and he\'s already asking for reports!$B$BIf you need supplies, I can offer a few things, but we\'re still waiting for our first shipment. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you ever meet Witch Doctor Tor\'gash, tell him his concoctions and charms don\'t work! I did exactly as he told me to and still Magasha has eyes only for Zurai.$B$BDon\'t believe a thing that sham witch doctor tells you!' WHERE entry=9268; /* Text0_0: If you ever meet Witch Doctor Tor\'gash, tell him his concoctions and charms don\'t work! I did exactly as he told me to and still Magasha has eyes only for Zurai.$B$BDon\'t believe a thing that sham witch doctor tells you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Reavij has all the subtlety of a kodo! What\'s funny is that he doesn\'t think he\'s being obvious. I see the way he stares at me when he thinks no one\'s looking.$B$BHe creeps me out. I really wish Shadow Hunter Denjai hadn\'t sent him with us. Setting up Swamprat Post was the perfect opportunity to get away from him.' WHERE entry=9269; /* Text0_1: Reavij has all the subtlety of a kodo! What\'s funny is that he doesn\'t think he\'s being obvious. I see the way he stares at me when he thinks no one\'s looking.$B$BHe creeps me out. I really wish Shadow Hunter Denjai hadn\'t sent him with us. Setting up Swamprat Post was the perfect opportunity to get away from him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hello, $c.  I am what is referred to as one of the Broken.  Like the Lost Ones, though not as badly as they, we were afflicted with fel energies that transformed us from our original draenei forms.' WHERE entry=9270; /* Text0_0: Hello, $c.  I am what is referred to as one of the Broken.  Like the Lost Ones, though not as badly as they, we were afflicted with fel energies that transformed us from our original draenei forms. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Garadar is in shambles, stranger. Since the Greatmother took ill, Garrosh has gone into a deep depression. He is most certainly not his father\'s boy.$B$B<Kurkush sighs.>$B' WHERE entry=9271; /* Text0_0: Garadar is in shambles, stranger. Since the Greatmother took ill, Garrosh has gone into a deep depression. He is most certainly not his father\'s boy.$B$B<Kurkush sighs.>$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Notices of reward for the naga leaders of the Darkcrest and Bloodscale tribes are listed here.' WHERE entry=9274; /* Text0_0: Notices of reward for the naga leaders of the Darkcrest and Bloodscale tribes are listed here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='They died. All of them...$B$BAs the Murkbloods cut through us, something took hold of me that I cannot understand. Tell me, have you ever felt a rage so great that the whole of your being burns? A heat that wilts the living? A heat that incinerates the blood in your veins? That is what I felt.$B$B<Saurfang\'s eyes glow red for a brief moment.>$B$BI was the last one left alive. 30 of them surrounded me... Murkbloods... I remember nothing beyond that vision. I blacked out and awoke some time later.' WHERE entry=9275; /* Text0_0: They died. All of them...$B$BAs the Murkbloods cut through us, something took hold of me that I cannot understand. Tell me, have you ever felt a rage so great that the whole of your being burns? A heat that wilts the living? A heat that incinerates the blood in your veins? That is what I felt.$B$B<Saurfang\'s eyes glow red for a brief moment.>$B$BI was the last one left alive. 30 of them surrounded me... Murkbloods... I remember nothing beyond that vision. I blacked out and awoke some time later. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Dark times loom ahead, stranger...' WHERE entry=9276; /* Text0_0: Dark times loom ahead, stranger... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The spirits are greatly agitated. We must find the cause of this disturbance.' WHERE entry=9277; /* Text0_0: The spirits are greatly agitated. We must find the cause of this disturbance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hemet is the greatest hunter that I know.  We chanced upon each other in the hills of Winterspring back on Azeroth many moons ago.  He and I were stalking the same quarry: the great cat known as Rak\'shiri.$B$BRather than fight each other over our prey, we made a wager out of it; whoever collected the frostsaber\'s skin would get to demand something of the other.  To my eternal shame, this is how I earned the nickname, Fitz.$B$BDo I look like a Fitz?' WHERE entry=9283; /* Text0_0: Hemet is the greatest hunter that I know.  We chanced upon each other in the hills of Winterspring back on Azeroth many moons ago.  He and I were stalking the same quarry: the great cat known as Rak\'shiri.$B$BRather than fight each other over our prey, we made a wager out of it; whoever collected the frostsaber\'s skin would get to demand something of the other.  To my eternal shame, this is how I earned the nickname, Fitz.$B$BDo I look like a Fitz? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The mighty hunter, $N returns.  Tell me the tale of stalking your latest prey.' WHERE entry=9284; /* Text0_0: The mighty hunter, $N returns.  Tell me the tale of stalking your latest prey. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yeah, yeah, I\'m feeling better, but I kind of like it down here.',Text0_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text0:',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=9286; /* Text0_0: Yeah, yeah, I\'m feeling better, but I kind of like it down here. */ /* Text0_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text0: */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Consortium has been planning this operation for months!  We were to dig Oshu\'gun, the largest known diamond in the universe.$B$BMinutes before we were to begin, Nexus-Prince Haramaad sends word that we\'re to hold off until a political matter is resolved in Netherstorm.  I\'ve transformed our operation into a clearing house for smuggled gems in the meantime, but this is slowly eating into our profits.' WHERE entry=9287; /* Text0_0: The Consortium has been planning this operation for months!  We were to dig Oshu\'gun, the largest known diamond in the universe.$B$BMinutes before we were to begin, Nexus-Prince Haramaad sends word that we\'re to hold off until a political matter is resolved in Netherstorm.  I\'ve transformed our operation into a clearing house for smuggled gems in the meantime, but this is slowly eating into our profits. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Gezhe is here to get a job done.  I\'m here to make sure no one bothers him while he does it.' WHERE entry=9288; /* Text0_0: Gezhe is here to get a job done.  I\'m here to make sure no one bothers him while he does it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do you know who we are, stranger? We are Mag\'har - brown orcs, as I have heard your kind call us. The Mag\'har are survivors: Survivors of a fallen dynasty; Survivors of the Red Pox; Survivors of a shattered world...$B$BI am Jorin, son of Kilrogg; last of the lineage of Deadeye: Warchief of the Bleeding Hollow Clan.' WHERE entry=9289; /* Text0_0: Do you know who we are, stranger? We are Mag\'har - brown orcs, as I have heard your kind call us. The Mag\'har are survivors: Survivors of a fallen dynasty; Survivors of the Red Pox; Survivors of a shattered world...$B$BI am Jorin, son of Kilrogg; last of the lineage of Deadeye: Warchief of the Bleeding Hollow Clan. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We wouldn\'t have crashed if Hemet could learn how to avoid shooting through the ailerons when he\'s trying to bag game on the ground!$B$BNo worries though, I\'ll have her fixed up quick enough.' WHERE entry=9290; /* Text0_1: We wouldn\'t have crashed if Hemet could learn how to avoid shooting through the ailerons when he\'s trying to bag game on the ground!$B$BNo worries though, I\'ll have her fixed up quick enough. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I am SO glad that evil Gankly Rottenfist got his just desserts!  I have lots of skins if you want some to give to Harold.' WHERE entry=9292; /* Text0_1: I am SO glad that evil Gankly Rottenfist got his just desserts!  I have lots of skins if you want some to give to Harold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Greetings $N.' WHERE entry=9296; /* Text0_0: Greetings $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='The Greatmother raised all of us. Any Mag\'hari that you see has had their life touched in some special way by the Greatmother. We will miss her greatly when she passes.'Text1_1_loc9='Greatmother tells me that I was named after a great orcish hero.' WHERE entry=9297; /* Text0_1: The Greatmother raised all of us. Any Mag\'hari that you see has had their life touched in some special way by the Greatmother. We will miss her greatly when she passes. */ /* Text1_1: Greatmother tells me that I was named after a great orcish hero. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You look like a reasonable $r.  Perhaps we could be of mutual assistance.' WHERE entry=9312; /* Text0_0: You look like a reasonable $r.  Perhaps we could be of mutual assistance. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Be strong. Kael\'thas has betrayed us and what we know is in flux, but do not lose heart. We will endure, as we always have. Arthas did not crush our spirit when he swept through our land, and neither will Kael\'thas. Let it serve as a lesson to us all as we move forward to our prosperous future.' WHERE entry=9315; /* Text0_0: Be strong. Kael\'thas has betrayed us and what we know is in flux, but do not lose heart. We will endure, as we always have. Arthas did not crush our spirit when he swept through our land, and neither will Kael\'thas. Let it serve as a lesson to us all as we move forward to our prosperous future. */
