UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='You\'ll be purchasing no hawkstrider here until you\'ve proven your worth and dedication to our people.$bDo not return until you are considered exalted among the blood elves. Away with you!' WHERE entry=10305; /* Text0_1: You\'ll be purchasing no hawkstrider here until you\'ve proven your worth and dedication to our people.$bDo not return until you are considered exalted among the blood elves. Away with you! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='These orcs must really be eager to stake their claim in Outland! If I told you how much they were paying for my allegiance, you\'d kill me out of jealousy!' WHERE entry=10306; /* Text0_0: These orcs must really be eager to stake their claim in Outland! If I told you how much they were paying for my allegiance, you\'d kill me out of jealousy! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If you\'ve the gold, I can teach you how to ride a hawkstrider.' WHERE entry=10308; /* Text0_0: If you\'ve the gold, I can teach you how to ride a hawkstrider. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You must be exalted with the blood elves before I will teach you a riding skill, $c.' WHERE entry=10310; /* Text0_0: You must be exalted with the blood elves before I will teach you a riding skill, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Are you ready to hear the story of the Cipher of Damnation, $N?' WHERE entry=10312; /* Text0_0: Are you ready to hear the story of the Cipher of Damnation, $N? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Very well. The words you seek have a name, $N. They are known as the Cipher of Damnation: The words uttered by Gul\'dan himself to shatter this land. The very spell that severed the last remaining tie the orcs had with the elements of Draenor.$B$B<Oronok nods.>$B$BAye, it is the cipher that you must reconstruct and ultimately the words of the cipher that you must call.' WHERE entry=10313; /* Text0_0: Very well. The words you seek have a name, $N. They are known as the Cipher of Damnation: The words uttered by Gul\'dan himself to shatter this land. The very spell that severed the last remaining tie the orcs had with the elements of Draenor.$B$B<Oronok nods.>$B$BAye, it is the cipher that you must reconstruct and ultimately the words of the cipher that you must call. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Cipher of Damnation was kept in Gul\'dan\'s private quarters inside Karabor for twenty years. Ah, that\'s right, you have no idea what Karabor is, do you?$B$BThe Black Temple...$B$BAye, now home to Illidan Stormrage.$B$BWhen Illidan took control of the Black Temple, he discovered the cipher. He recognized that the damage to this world had already been done but thought it wise to keep the cipher secure for later use.' WHERE entry=10314; /* Text0_0: The Cipher of Damnation was kept in Gul\'dan\'s private quarters inside Karabor for twenty years. Ah, that\'s right, you have no idea what Karabor is, do you?$B$BThe Black Temple...$B$BAye, now home to Illidan Stormrage.$B$BWhen Illidan took control of the Black Temple, he discovered the cipher. He recognized that the damage to this world had already been done but thought it wise to keep the cipher secure for later use. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='When you stand at the Altar of Damnation and see the spirits of the damned, kneeling in prayer, what you do not see is me, standing next to Gul\'dan.$B$B<Oronok nods.>$B$BI told you that I was a lot of things, did I not? One of those \'things\' was a lieutenant of Gul\'dan.$B$BI have done many terrible things in my life. I have slaughtered man, woman, and child alike. Danced in the blood of innocent draenei... yet...$B$B<Oronok chokes on his words.>' WHERE entry=10315; /* Text0_0: When you stand at the Altar of Damnation and see the spirits of the damned, kneeling in prayer, what you do not see is me, standing next to Gul\'dan.$B$B<Oronok nods.>$B$BI told you that I was a lot of things, did I not? One of those \'things\' was a lieutenant of Gul\'dan.$B$BI have done many terrible things in my life. I have slaughtered man, woman, and child alike. Danced in the blood of innocent draenei... yet...$B$B<Oronok chokes on his words.> */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I will never forget that day, $r. Never. Even though I had long since abandoned shamanism in favor of shadow magic, I felt the cut. A sense of loss so profound... I could not explain it to you with mere words.$B$BWhen the tie to the elements was severed, all orcs on Draenor changed. If there was ever any doubt in the power of the shadows, it was washed away with the cresting of the molten lava over the shattered earth.$B' WHERE entry=10316; /* Text0_0: I will never forget that day, $r. Never. Even though I had long since abandoned shamanism in favor of shadow magic, I felt the cut. A sense of loss so profound... I could not explain it to you with mere words.$B$BWhen the tie to the elements was severed, all orcs on Draenor changed. If there was ever any doubt in the power of the shadows, it was washed away with the cresting of the molten lava over the shattered earth.$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A wave of sickness rushed through me. After the ritual was over, I ran home to my children. I gathered what belongings I could carry in my arms and left with my boys. We ran to the hills and hid. There really was no other option...$B$BNot a day goes by that I don\'t think of the cut. It has taken 20 years to reconnect with the elements. It has taken 20 years for the elements to even begin to heal.' WHERE entry=10317; /* Text0_0: A wave of sickness rushed through me. After the ritual was over, I ran home to my children. I gathered what belongings I could carry in my arms and left with my boys. We ran to the hills and hid. There really was no other option...$B$BNot a day goes by that I don\'t think of the cut. It has taken 20 years to reconnect with the elements. It has taken 20 years for the elements to even begin to heal. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='As I said, the cipher was found by Illidan when he took over the Black Temple. He divided the tome into three parts and charged their care to his minions.$B$BMy boys... My boys are grown now. When I got word of what Illidan had done with the cipher, I sent my boys to recover the pieces.$B$BYou must find my boys, $N. You must find them and recover the Cipher of Damnation.' WHERE entry=10318; /* Text0_0: As I said, the cipher was found by Illidan when he took over the Black Temple. He divided the tome into three parts and charged their care to his minions.$B$BMy boys... My boys are grown now. When I got word of what Illidan had done with the cipher, I sent my boys to recover the pieces.$B$BYou must find my boys, $N. You must find them and recover the Cipher of Damnation. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome to Shattrath City, seat of the Sha\'tar in Outland. You seek guidance?',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to Shattrath City, seat of the Sha\'tar in Outland. You seek guidance?' WHERE entry=10321; /* Text0_0: Welcome to Shattrath City, seat of the Sha\'tar in Outland. You seek guidance? */ /* Text0_1: Welcome to Shattrath City, seat of the Sha\'tar in Outland. You seek guidance? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I came to this place because of my study into the backward culture that used to be the Thunderlord clan.$B$BThey were weak and succumbed to the lure of power that came with being transformed into fel orcs through Mannoroth\'s blood.$B$BI have read all of their texts.  I am particularly interested in the recovery of an artifact, a drum, an arrow and a tablet that were lost when we crushed the Bladespire ogres and pushed them back down into their hold.' WHERE entry=10322; /* Text0_1: I came to this place because of my study into the backward culture that used to be the Thunderlord clan.$B$BThey were weak and succumbed to the lure of power that came with being transformed into fel orcs through Mannoroth\'s blood.$B$BI have read all of their texts.  I am particularly interested in the recovery of an artifact, a drum, an arrow and a tablet that were lost when we crushed the Bladespire ogres and pushed them back down into their hold. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ar\'tor\'s lifeless body remains suspended in mid-air by demonic magic. They take from him, even in death...' WHERE entry=10323; /* Text0_0: Ar\'tor\'s lifeless body remains suspended in mid-air by demonic magic. They take from him, even in death... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I am pleased that you\'ve decided to take up our cause.  As a reward I will infuse a ring with the remnants of the Well of Eternity you brought me.$B$BI offer you four different paths in which to unlock their power.  Choose wisely, $N.  The sands of time flow easily in one direction and not the other.' WHERE entry=10324; /* Text0_1: I am pleased that you\'ve decided to take up our cause.  As a reward I will infuse a ring with the remnants of the Well of Eternity you brought me.$B$BI offer you four different paths in which to unlock their power.  Choose wisely, $N.  The sands of time flow easily in one direction and not the other. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I... died.$B$BWhy am I still here? Is there no great hunting ground that I ascend to?$B$BNo... I must first complete my task. Before I can leave this world, the second part of the Cipher of Damnation must be recovered.',Text0_1_loc9='I... died.$B$BWhy am I still here? Is there no great hunting ground that I ascend to?$B$BNo... I must first complete my task. Before I can leave this world, the second part of the Cipher of Damnation must be recovered.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=10327; /* Text0_0: I... died.$B$BWhy am I still here? Is there no great hunting ground that I ascend to?$B$BNo... I must first complete my task. Before I can leave this world, the second part of the Cipher of Damnation must be recovered. */ /* Text0_1: I... died.$B$BWhy am I still here? Is there no great hunting ground that I ascend to?$B$BNo... I must first complete my task. Before I can leave this world, the second part of the Cipher of Damnation must be recovered. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
