UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='When I first set up my rogue academy in Shattrath, it wasn\'t nearly this crowded. Then, the refugees started flooding in and the naaru needed every available building to house them.$B$BI\'ve closed the doors to my academy for now, but it\'s not permanent. I\'ll find a new place to set up.$B$BThen, a new generation of rogues will learn such staples as the gouge\'n grin, combat looting, and blaming someone else for breaking polymorph. And who can forget the central rule of roguery --- real rogues don\'t feint.'Text1_1_loc9='The trick to using evasion is realizing that the best fifteen seconds of your life are often the last.' WHERE entry=10686; /* Text0_1: When I first set up my rogue academy in Shattrath, it wasn\'t nearly this crowded. Then, the refugees started flooding in and the naaru needed every available building to house them.$B$BI\'ve closed the doors to my academy for now, but it\'s not permanent. I\'ll find a new place to set up.$B$BThen, a new generation of rogues will learn such staples as the gouge\'n grin, combat looting, and blaming someone else for breaking polymorph. And who can forget the central rule of roguery --- real rogues don\'t feint. */ /* Text1_1: The trick to using evasion is realizing that the best fifteen seconds of your life are often the last. */
