UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We shouldn\'t have left so many behind at Valgarde. Admiral Keller, that insufferable egomaniac!$B$BHow am I to fulfill my orders with so few? I need enough men to stay here at the keep and still properly garrison Fort Wildervar when it\'s ready!$B$BAt least we have a hope of dealing with our problems now that you\'re here.' WHERE entry=11494; /* Text0_0: We shouldn\'t have left so many behind at Valgarde. Admiral Keller, that insufferable egomaniac!$B$BHow am I to fulfill my orders with so few? I need enough men to stay here at the keep and still properly garrison Fort Wildervar when it\'s ready!$B$BAt least we have a hope of dealing with our problems now that you\'re here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I advise the captain on matters that he chooses to share with me, but I have a feeling that he\'d rather hear from you.' WHERE entry=11496; /* Text0_0: I advise the captain on matters that he chooses to share with me, but I have a feeling that he\'d rather hear from you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='All of these mouths to feed, and who has to do it? Me!$B$BAll the cooking, and the cleaning, and everything else!' WHERE entry=11498; /* Text0_1: All of these mouths to feed, and who has to do it? Me!$B$BAll the cooking, and the cleaning, and everything else! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='In all of my days I never thought to see such a magnificent new frontier.$B$BIf only it weren\'t tainted by evil and knowledge which is best left hidden.' WHERE entry=11502; /* Text0_0: In all of my days I never thought to see such a magnificent new frontier.$B$BIf only it weren\'t tainted by evil and knowledge which is best left hidden. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve seen a lot of things in my time, but the change that came over the Explorers\' League in the Whisper Gulch takes the cake.$B$BI\'m just glad that I got out of there with my skin intact!' WHERE entry=11504; /* Text0_0: I\'ve seen a lot of things in my time, but the change that came over the Explorers\' League in the Whisper Gulch takes the cake.$B$BI\'m just glad that I got out of there with my skin intact! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have reached the limits of my knowledge, but there is more yet to learn. Across the sea, in the Mage Quarter of Stormwind City, a great tailor dwells. His name is Georgio Bolero, and he will train you now, I think. Go and speak with him.' WHERE entry=11551; /* Text0_0: You have reached the limits of my knowledge, but there is more yet to learn. Across the sea, in the Mage Quarter of Stormwind City, a great tailor dwells. His name is Georgio Bolero, and he will train you now, I think. Go and speak with him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The ground... is frozen.  We\'re sitting ducks here; these meatwagons aren\'t going anywhere.' WHERE entry=11562; /* Text0_0: The ground... is frozen.  We\'re sitting ducks here; these meatwagons aren\'t going anywhere. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What does it look like?  The ground is frozen like a rock!$B$BThe wheels on these meatwagons were built to go over mud at best.  We\'re going to need an abomination and some chains to salvage them.' WHERE entry=11564; /* Text0_0: What does it look like?  The ground is frozen like a rock!$B$BThe wheels on these meatwagons were built to go over mud at best.  We\'re going to need an abomination and some chains to salvage them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I will never call Brackenwall Village my home. To do so is to give up hope of reclaiming our rightful lands.' WHERE entry=11567; /* Text0_0: I will never call Brackenwall Village my home. To do so is to give up hope of reclaiming our rightful lands. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Well then, I spose I be owin\' ya my thanks, $r.$b$bTruth is, I thought I\'d swallowed me last tankard \'til ye showed up.' WHERE entry=11578; /* Text0_0: Well then, I spose I be owin\' ya my thanks, $r.$b$bTruth is, I thought I\'d swallowed me last tankard \'til ye showed up. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A sad tale, that one - a wee bit embarrassin\' too.$b$bMy people be know fer havin\' a taste fer the ale, ya know. And I be no exception. Seems I been given more than me share of the thirst.$b$bSo I run inta ol\' Budd ya see, an\' he offers me all the grog I can swallow fer joinin\' his crew - a move I\'ve come to regret.$b$bOne night, after drinkin\' enough grog to drop a Kodo, I was lured into followin\' Budd\'s band o\' misfits into Zul\'Aman.$b$bThat be the last I recall before findin\' meself in that cage.' WHERE entry=11580; /* Text0_0: A sad tale, that one - a wee bit embarrassin\' too.$b$bMy people be know fer havin\' a taste fer the ale, ya know. And I be no exception. Seems I been given more than me share of the thirst.$b$bSo I run inta ol\' Budd ya see, an\' he offers me all the grog I can swallow fer joinin\' his crew - a move I\'ve come to regret.$b$bOne night, after drinkin\' enough grog to drop a Kodo, I was lured into followin\' Budd\'s band o\' misfits into Zul\'Aman.$b$bThat be the last I recall before findin\' meself in that cage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Ohh, thank you soo much for getting me out of that cage because I was in there for soo long and it smelled like minced mutton that had been sitting out in the sun for a week and I don\'t like mutton to begin with because when I was little, well littler, I was actually turned into a sheep for a minute and so I know what it feels like to be a sheep and I don\'t want someone eating me, especially an overgrown troll dressed up like a kitty....$b$b<Ashli takes a deep breath.>$b$bHow\'s my hair?$B' WHERE entry=11582; /* Text0_1: Ohh, thank you soo much for getting me out of that cage because I was in there for soo long and it smelled like minced mutton that had been sitting out in the sun for a week and I don\'t like mutton to begin with because when I was little, well littler, I was actually turned into a sheep for a minute and so I know what it feels like to be a sheep and I don\'t want someone eating me, especially an overgrown troll dressed up like a kitty....$b$b<Ashli takes a deep breath.>$b$bHow\'s my hair?$B */
