UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Our efforts have paid off.  We\'ve captured the Sun\'s Reach Sanctum, $N.  Go there and see if there\'s anyone you can assist.' WHERE entry=12259; /* Text0_0: Our efforts have paid off.  We\'ve captured the Sun\'s Reach Sanctum, $N.  Go there and see if there\'s anyone you can assist. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Arming the wards at the sanctum will help us secure it faster.  We don\'t want any Wretched getting in our way when we unleash a full scale attack on the Legion and Kael.$B$BWe are $3244w percent done with our goal.' WHERE entry=12260; /* Text0_0: Arming the wards at the sanctum will help us secure it faster.  We don\'t want any Wretched getting in our way when we unleash a full scale attack on the Legion and Kael.$B$BWe are $3244w percent done with our goal. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Bravery\'s crew will do its best to make your journey as swift and pleasant as possible.' WHERE entry=12262; /* Text0_0: The Bravery\'s crew will do its best to make your journey as swift and pleasant as possible. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Sorry, but we\'ll have to speak some other time. Farewell.' WHERE entry=12263; /* Text0_0: Sorry, but we\'ll have to speak some other time. Farewell. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Welcome to The Bravery, $gsir:madame;. Now if you\'ll excuse me...' WHERE entry=12264; /* Text0_1: Welcome to The Bravery, $gsir:madame;. Now if you\'ll excuse me... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Unlucky name fer a sailor, innit?' WHERE entry=12267; /* Text0_1: Unlucky name fer a sailor, innit? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This greyin\' seadog may be the oldest of the crew, but he\'s also the toughest of the lot! Eh? Eh? Arms like an ogre!' WHERE entry=12268; /* Text0_0: This greyin\' seadog may be the oldest of the crew, but he\'s also the toughest of the lot! Eh? Eh? Arms like an ogre! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We\'ve sworn to do our very best to protect the passengers of The Bravery. The sea lane between Auberdine to Stormwind Harbor must remain safe.' WHERE entry=12270; /* Text0_1: We\'ve sworn to do our very best to protect the passengers of The Bravery. The sea lane between Auberdine to Stormwind Harbor must remain safe. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hey, kid. You\'re aboard the Maiden\'s Fancy. The name\'s Captain Wrenchnozzle, and you\'ve got the privilege of sailing on the pride of the Blackwater Raiders. The Bloodsail don\'t come near us, not with my sharp crew and the large amount of gunpowder in the hold. Insurance, you know.$b$bIf you\'ve got questions, kid, I\'ll answer \'em.' WHERE entry=12271; /* Text0_0: Hey, kid. You\'re aboard the Maiden\'s Fancy. The name\'s Captain Wrenchnozzle, and you\'ve got the privilege of sailing on the pride of the Blackwater Raiders. The Bloodsail don\'t come near us, not with my sharp crew and the large amount of gunpowder in the hold. Insurance, you know.$b$bIf you\'ve got questions, kid, I\'ll answer \'em. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yeah, that\'s her you\'re standing on. A beaut, isn\'t she? The Baron set me up as the captain a while back. She\'s not mine originally, so I didn\'t name her; if you want my opinion, kid, I think the sailor who named her spent a little too much time at sea and not enough time in port, if you catch my meaning.' WHERE entry=12272; /* Text0_0: Yeah, that\'s her you\'re standing on. A beaut, isn\'t she? The Baron set me up as the captain a while back. She\'s not mine originally, so I didn\'t name her; if you want my opinion, kid, I think the sailor who named her spent a little too much time at sea and not enough time in port, if you catch my meaning. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='If your stomach\'s rumbling, talk to Galley Chief Steelbelly, but just between you and me? You might want to wait. He\'s got that name for a reason.' WHERE entry=12273; /* Text0_0: If your stomach\'s rumbling, talk to Galley Chief Steelbelly, but just between you and me? You might want to wait. He\'s got that name for a reason. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What\'s a Steamwheedle ship without an engineer, eh? Torquespindle can help you with anything you need. He\'s handy with repairing things quickly, too, if that\'s what you\'re after.' WHERE entry=12274; /* Text0_0: What\'s a Steamwheedle ship without an engineer, eh? Torquespindle can help you with anything you need. He\'s handy with repairing things quickly, too, if that\'s what you\'re after. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome aboard the Feathermoon Ferry.  We travel between Feathermoon Stronghold and the Forgotten Coast looking for those lost at sea.  The sea can be a dangerous place if you are not prepared.$b$bIf you need to get prepared, please speak to our provisioners.  They are more than happy to help you.' WHERE entry=12275; /* Text0_0: Welcome aboard the Feathermoon Ferry.  We travel between Feathermoon Stronghold and the Forgotten Coast looking for those lost at sea.  The sea can be a dangerous place if you are not prepared.$b$bIf you need to get prepared, please speak to our provisioners.  They are more than happy to help you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='On behalf of the crew of the Moonspray, I welcome you $c.  I hope you take advantage of our provisions before parting with us.' WHERE entry=12276; /* Text0_0: On behalf of the crew of the Moonspray, I welcome you $c.  I hope you take advantage of our provisions before parting with us. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Watch your step aboard Elune\'s Blessing, $r.  Though Elune\'s blessed us with the discovery of our new friends, we\'ve also had our share of hardships at sea.$b$bHowever, recovering souls lost at sea or lost in a new world is truly a blessing from Elune.' WHERE entry=12277; /* Text0_0: Watch your step aboard Elune\'s Blessing, $r.  Though Elune\'s blessed us with the discovery of our new friends, we\'ve also had our share of hardships at sea.$b$bHowever, recovering souls lost at sea or lost in a new world is truly a blessing from Elune. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Elune has blessed us many times over with all the discoveries we have made.  But we must remain vigilant, $c.',Text0_1_loc9='Elune has blessed us many times over with all the discoveries we have made.  But we must remain vigilant, $c.' WHERE entry=12278; /* Text0_0: Elune has blessed us many times over with all the discoveries we have made.  But we must remain vigilant, $c. */ /* Text0_1: Elune has blessed us many times over with all the discoveries we have made.  But we must remain vigilant, $c. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Forgive me, $r, I must focus on my job.' WHERE entry=12279; /* Text0_1: Forgive me, $r, I must focus on my job. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome aboard the Maiden\'s Fancy. It should be smooth sailing all the way to port.' WHERE entry=12281; /* Text0_0: Welcome aboard the Maiden\'s Fancy. It should be smooth sailing all the way to port. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It\'s amazing what you can learn from a gnome if you squeeze them hard enough: clever little tricks about getting out of a bind, making delicious cookies, and even how to make a flying machine.' WHERE entry=12282; /* Text0_0: It\'s amazing what you can learn from a gnome if you squeeze them hard enough: clever little tricks about getting out of a bind, making delicious cookies, and even how to make a flying machine. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='As often as I can.  It\'s great exercise and it keeps me informed on what they\'re up to--which, from my experience, is always no good.' WHERE entry=12283; /* Text0_0: As often as I can.  It\'s great exercise and it keeps me informed on what they\'re up to--which, from my experience, is always no good. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Urrrk... if that grubbing galley chief over there offers you his special, do yourself a favor and dump it in the ocean. It might kill a few makruras instead of your will to live.' WHERE entry=12284; /* Text0_0: Urrrk... if that grubbing galley chief over there offers you his special, do yourself a favor and dump it in the ocean. It might kill a few makruras instead of your will to live. */
