UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Twilight Cult seeks to undo everything we fight to preserve. It is our sworn duty to prevent this calamity from coming to pass, $r.',Text0_1_loc9='The Twilight Cult seeks to undo everything we fight to preserve. It is our sworn duty to prevent this calamity from coming to pass, $r.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=12390; /* Text0_0: The Twilight Cult seeks to undo everything we fight to preserve. It is our sworn duty to prevent this calamity from coming to pass, $r. */ /* Text0_1: The Twilight Cult seeks to undo everything we fight to preserve. It is our sworn duty to prevent this calamity from coming to pass, $r. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am dishonored. I should have died with the farseer at Magmoth.$B$BLeave me to my thoughts.' WHERE entry=12394; /* Text0_0: I am dishonored. I should have died with the farseer at Magmoth.$B$BLeave me to my thoughts. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The element of air here is restless. Beware... they will not let you pass unharmed.' WHERE entry=12395; /* Text0_0: The element of air here is restless. Beware... they will not let you pass unharmed. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It pains me to see my ancestors disturbed from their graves.$B$BWe must strike down the cursed spirit of your Force-Commander Steeljaw, the one who foolishly led his caravan through these sacred grounds.' WHERE entry=12403; /* Text0_0: It pains me to see my ancestors disturbed from their graves.$B$BWe must strike down the cursed spirit of your Force-Commander Steeljaw, the one who foolishly led his caravan through these sacred grounds. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Only you can save me from Kaganishu, $N.' WHERE entry=12413; /* Text0_0: Only you can save me from Kaganishu, $N. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We\'ve lost a good many of our wind riders on scouting missions to the west. The Scourge is ruthless in their assault against any would-be spies.$B$BFortunately, I\'ve come up with a solution that only risks the life of the rider. It\'s seen a 30% survival rate to those being ferried across the Plains of Nasam. That\'s a 30% improvement over when we were using wind riders!' WHERE entry=12417; /* Text0_0: We\'ve lost a good many of our wind riders on scouting missions to the west. The Scourge is ruthless in their assault against any would-be spies.$B$BFortunately, I\'ve come up with a solution that only risks the life of the rider. It\'s seen a 30% survival rate to those being ferried across the Plains of Nasam. That\'s a 30% improvement over when we were using wind riders! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am dishonored. I should have died with the farseer at Magmoth.' WHERE entry=12419; /* Text0_0: I am dishonored. I should have died with the farseer at Magmoth. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Both Garrosh\'s Landing and Pal\'ea were wiped out by the mist. We\'re the only ones crazy enough to stay here, buddy!' WHERE entry=12422; /* Text0_0: Both Garrosh\'s Landing and Pal\'ea were wiped out by the mist. We\'re the only ones crazy enough to stay here, buddy! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='How am I supposed to get anything done with Fizzcrank breathing down my neck and me without all of my stuff?!' WHERE entry=12423; /* Text0_1: How am I supposed to get anything done with Fizzcrank breathing down my neck and me without all of my stuff?! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What you see here on this coast is not a result of the Scourge. In fact, we believe that the Scourge also fear the mist - which might be why they do not come here.$B$BYou see, the mist is alive, friend. Inside those airy tendrils lies death...$B$BShould you step within its grasp, you will vanish. The mist will take you!$B$BWe have never seen anyone return alive from the mist.' WHERE entry=12424; /* Text0_0: What you see here on this coast is not a result of the Scourge. In fact, we believe that the Scourge also fear the mist - which might be why they do not come here.$B$BYou see, the mist is alive, friend. Inside those airy tendrils lies death...$B$BShould you step within its grasp, you will vanish. The mist will take you!$B$BWe have never seen anyone return alive from the mist. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Since landing here I have seen horrors that had previously only haunted my darkest nightmares, but nothing could have prepared me for what lies beyond the mist.$B$B<Mootoo nods.>$B$BThrough that fog, not more than a few yards from us, stand the bloodthirsty creatures known as Kvaldir. None have returned from the fog and few that were originally at the landing when the mist rolled in have escaped. The area has since been condemned by Hellscream. Enter at your own risk...' WHERE entry=12426; /* Text0_0: Since landing here I have seen horrors that had previously only haunted my darkest nightmares, but nothing could have prepared me for what lies beyond the mist.$B$B<Mootoo nods.>$B$BThrough that fog, not more than a few yards from us, stand the bloodthirsty creatures known as Kvaldir. None have returned from the fog and few that were originally at the landing when the mist rolled in have escaped. The area has since been condemned by Hellscream. Enter at your own risk... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I... Are you...$B$B<Mootoo shivers.>$B$BAre you here to save me?' WHERE entry=12427; /* Text0_1: I... Are you...$B$B<Mootoo shivers.>$B$BAre you here to save me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You\'re a sight for sore eyes! I\'m too weak to break the links on this rusty ball and chain.$B$BWell, don\'t just stand there! Get me loose!' WHERE entry=12433; /* Text0_0: You\'re a sight for sore eyes! I\'m too weak to break the links on this rusty ball and chain.$B$BWell, don\'t just stand there! Get me loose! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve got my hands full here at the moment, $c.$B$BWhat can I do for you?' WHERE entry=12435; /* Text0_0: I\'ve got my hands full here at the moment, $c.$B$BWhat can I do for you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Speak slowly, child, I am new to your strange tongue.' WHERE entry=12440; /* Text0_1: Speak slowly, child, I am new to your strange tongue. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Please, keep your voice down, $r. Hamat is old and needs her rest.' WHERE entry=12441; /* Text0_1: Please, keep your voice down, $r. Hamat is old and needs her rest. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Fine then, have a seat. This might take a while.$B$BWhen we first came to this frozen hell, General Arlos, down in Valiance Keep, gave my group of flying daredevils and I a special task: to establish a forward airbase for Alliance operations.$B$BThis airstrip is the result. Let me tell you, it wasn\'t easy, what with all the nasty beasts and the ground rock-hard from being frozen! But we managed, and we did it quickly too!' WHERE entry=12456; /* Text0_0: Fine then, have a seat. This might take a while.$B$BWhen we first came to this frozen hell, General Arlos, down in Valiance Keep, gave my group of flying daredevils and I a special task: to establish a forward airbase for Alliance operations.$B$BThis airstrip is the result. Let me tell you, it wasn\'t easy, what with all the nasty beasts and the ground rock-hard from being frozen! But we managed, and we did it quickly too! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Anyway, we needed to pump up lots of sand and oil for the machinery. The nearby pools proved to be perfect for that.$B$BSome of the sand even proved to have magical properties... can you say possibilities!? But that\'s a different tale.$B$BSo, we drained most of the water out and built the pumping station smack dab in the middle. Everything was going swimmingly until one day the main suction pipe got clogged.' WHERE entry=12457; /* Text0_0: Anyway, we needed to pump up lots of sand and oil for the machinery. The nearby pools proved to be perfect for that.$B$BSome of the sand even proved to have magical properties... can you say possibilities!? But that\'s a different tale.$B$BSo, we drained most of the water out and built the pumping station smack dab in the middle. Everything was going swimmingly until one day the main suction pipe got clogged. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Mind you, this part I learned later because I wasn\'t out there at the time.$B$BWhen they ratcheted up the suction on the pump, up came pieces of a robot that looked like a gnome! Of course the fools worked night and day to put it back together without telling us.$B$BThis is when we lost communication with the pumping station.' WHERE entry=12458; /* Text0_0: Mind you, this part I learned later because I wasn\'t out there at the time.$B$BWhen they ratcheted up the suction on the pump, up came pieces of a robot that looked like a gnome! Of course the fools worked night and day to put it back together without telling us.$B$BThis is when we lost communication with the pumping station. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='After a couple of days of silence, I sent a scouting party out to the platform. They never returned.$B$BI sent another group the next day with the same results, and lost a couple of flying machines out on aerial recon.$B$BAt that point I sent someone south to find help, and we hunkered down to prepare for the worst. We turned all of our attention to making armor, weapons and robots so that we could head out there in full force.$B$BWhen we did a few days ago, we couldn\'t believe our eyes!' WHERE entry=12459; /* Text0_0: After a couple of days of silence, I sent a scouting party out to the platform. They never returned.$B$BI sent another group the next day with the same results, and lost a couple of flying machines out on aerial recon.$B$BAt that point I sent someone south to find help, and we hunkered down to prepare for the worst. We turned all of our attention to making armor, weapons and robots so that we could head out there in full force.$B$BWhen we did a few days ago, we couldn\'t believe our eyes! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='As I was saying, what we saw out there defied explanation.$B$BMy people were nowhere to be found, but in their place was a veritable army of robots and androids going about their business!$B$BThe droids all looked like gnomes and they said that they\'d been expecting us. In fact, in their own strange way, they acted like they knew us. We were surrounded and quickly taken to the top of the pumping station.$B$BThat\'s where we saw their leader and what he was doing to the surviving gnomes!' WHERE entry=12460; /* Text0_0: As I was saying, what we saw out there defied explanation.$B$BMy people were nowhere to be found, but in their place was a veritable army of robots and androids going about their business!$B$BThe droids all looked like gnomes and they said that they\'d been expecting us. In fact, in their own strange way, they acted like they knew us. We were surrounded and quickly taken to the top of the pumping station.$B$BThat\'s where we saw their leader and what he was doing to the surviving gnomes! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='He called himself Gearmaster Mechazod. When we arrived he was busy transforming the survivors into mechanical beings!$B$BHe greeted us warmly and explained that he was one of the first gnomes ever to be created by something he called "The Grand Architect", a Titan keeper from within the halls of fabled Ulduar.$B$BApparently, he was the blockage that my team had accidentally sucked up from where he\'d malfunctioned thousands of years ago. It was just our luck that we\'d built the pumping station right above him.' WHERE entry=12461; /* Text0_0: He called himself Gearmaster Mechazod. When we arrived he was busy transforming the survivors into mechanical beings!$B$BHe greeted us warmly and explained that he was one of the first gnomes ever to be created by something he called "The Grand Architect", a Titan keeper from within the halls of fabled Ulduar.$B$BApparently, he was the blockage that my team had accidentally sucked up from where he\'d malfunctioned thousands of years ago. It was just our luck that we\'d built the pumping station right above him. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The station\'s mechanics had put him back together, bringing him back to "life".$B$BAnd now, by way of thanks, he was going to return the favor by curing all of us of what he called the "Curse of the Flesh".$B$BAccording to Mechazod, it\'s a condition that eventually befalls all of the creations of the Titans! In other words, we all supposedly start out as robots of some kind, and, over thousands of years, slowly turn into fleshy beings!$B$BPreposterous, I know.' WHERE entry=12462; /* Text0_0: The station\'s mechanics had put him back together, bringing him back to "life".$B$BAnd now, by way of thanks, he was going to return the favor by curing all of us of what he called the "Curse of the Flesh".$B$BAccording to Mechazod, it\'s a condition that eventually befalls all of the creations of the Titans! In other words, we all supposedly start out as robots of some kind, and, over thousands of years, slowly turn into fleshy beings!$B$BPreposterous, I know. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It didn\'t look like much of a "cure" to me, and I wasn\'t about to stand around listening to some crazy robot while he was butchering my people!$B$BWe did what any sane gnome would do... we ran! Well, actually, most of us parachuted off the side of the platform, but you get the picture.$B$BNot many of us managed to make it back here, and we\'re still spread thin from having to deal with everything else too, like the magnataur to the north and the Scourge to the east. To make things worse, the Horde just setup shop to the northwest!' WHERE entry=12463; /* Text0_0: It didn\'t look like much of a "cure" to me, and I wasn\'t about to stand around listening to some crazy robot while he was butchering my people!$B$BWe did what any sane gnome would do... we ran! Well, actually, most of us parachuted off the side of the platform, but you get the picture.$B$BNot many of us managed to make it back here, and we\'re still spread thin from having to deal with everything else too, like the magnataur to the north and the Scourge to the east. To make things worse, the Horde just setup shop to the northwest! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='And that\'s where we find ourselves now, $N.$B$BWe can\'t possibly deal with all of this by ourselves, and quite frankly, I feel a little out of my depth. Jinky knows what needs to be done. You should go see her now.$B$BI just hope you\'ll be able to get us out of this mess with our bodies intact.' WHERE entry=12464; /* Text0_0: And that\'s where we find ourselves now, $N.$B$BWe can\'t possibly deal with all of this by ourselves, and quite frankly, I feel a little out of my depth. Jinky knows what needs to be done. You should go see her now.$B$BI just hope you\'ll be able to get us out of this mess with our bodies intact. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The actions of these deserters shames us all. A shame so powerful that it must be witnessed to be understood. It is why Ug\'thor is here... The boy must learn.' WHERE entry=12472; /* Text0_0: The actions of these deserters shames us all. A shame so powerful that it must be witnessed to be understood. It is why Ug\'thor is here... The boy must learn. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Be careful around these parts, $r. The natives are ruthless.' WHERE entry=12475; /* Text0_1: Be careful around these parts, $r. The natives are ruthless. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am sworn by tuskarr law to avenge my kin... these murderers burned Pal\'ea to the ground.' WHERE entry=12477; /* Text0_0: I am sworn by tuskarr law to avenge my kin... these murderers burned Pal\'ea to the ground. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ve treated peasants, nobles, merchants\' sons and beggars.  Allow me to share one piece of wisdom with you - we\'re all the same when staring death in the face.' WHERE entry=12478; /* Text0_0: I\'ve treated peasants, nobles, merchants\' sons and beggars.  Allow me to share one piece of wisdom with you - we\'re all the same when staring death in the face. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Is your cause righteous and your heart true? If so, you are welcome here - among the druids for the ethical and humane treatment of animals. So long as you do not veer down the dark path of depravity and harm the animals that have allowed us to coexist within their world, D.E.H.T.A. will consider you an ally.$B' WHERE entry=12485; /* Text0_0: Is your cause righteous and your heart true? If so, you are welcome here - among the druids for the ethical and humane treatment of animals. So long as you do not veer down the dark path of depravity and harm the animals that have allowed us to coexist within their world, D.E.H.T.A. will consider you an ally.$B */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This recon pilot did not survive his squadron\'s crash.' WHERE entry=12489; /* Text0_0: This recon pilot did not survive his squadron\'s crash. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='So, $N, which item are you interested in?' WHERE entry=12494; /* Text0_0: So, $N, which item are you interested in? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ah - oddities and rarities. We specialize in Azeroth\'s more unique items for the discerning adventurer.$B$BSince you\'re speaking with me, you must already have an idea of what you\'re looking for.' WHERE entry=12495; /* Text0_0: Ah - oddities and rarities. We specialize in Azeroth\'s more unique items for the discerning adventurer.$B$BSince you\'re speaking with me, you must already have an idea of what you\'re looking for. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Did you know that alchemists can transmute certain gems?  Mar\'nah and I have been talking about this.$B$BI\'m convinced that given her prowess, once her lab is complete, she and I will be able to create gems that were thought to be lost in time.' WHERE entry=12496; /* Text0_1: Did you know that alchemists can transmute certain gems?  Mar\'nah and I have been talking about this.$B$BI\'m convinced that given her prowess, once her lab is complete, she and I will be able to create gems that were thought to be lost in time. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We\'ve done it, $N.  Mar\'nah has learned how to transmute very special gems.  And I\'ve learned how to work them.' WHERE entry=12497; /* Text0_1: We\'ve done it, $N.  Mar\'nah has learned how to transmute very special gems.  And I\'ve learned how to work them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Do not be frightened, $r. Our ends are the same.' WHERE entry=12498; /* Text0_0: Do not be frightened, $r. Our ends are the same. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I am Kalecgos, of the Blue Dragonflight.$b$bI have watched over the nascent powers of the Sunwell for some time, but now I see that its terrible power could usher in the end of our world!' WHERE entry=12500; /* Text0_0: I am Kalecgos, of the Blue Dragonflight.$b$bI have watched over the nascent powers of the Sunwell for some time, but now I see that its terrible power could usher in the end of our world! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Defeating Kael\'thas is a task worthy of your undivided attention. $b$bBeyond that, if you are capable of organizing an army, there are many wrongs in the Sunwell to be addressed.$b$bPerhaps we shall meet again there.' WHERE entry=12502; /* Text0_0: Defeating Kael\'thas is a task worthy of your undivided attention. $b$bBeyond that, if you are capable of organizing an army, there are many wrongs in the Sunwell to be addressed.$b$bPerhaps we shall meet again there. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with an Alliance settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Horde, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with an Alliance settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Horde, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them.' WHERE entry=12504; /* Text0_0: Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with an Alliance settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Horde, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with an Alliance settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Horde, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Behold, the Flames of Summer!',Text0_1_loc9='Behold, the Flames of Summer!',Text1_0_loc9='Careful, don\'t get burned!',Text1_1_loc9='Careful, don\'t get burned!' WHERE entry=12506; /* Text0_0: Behold, the Flames of Summer! */ /* Text0_1: Behold, the Flames of Summer! */ /* Text1_0: Careful, don\'t get burned! */ /* Text1_1: Careful, don\'t get burned! */
