UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The land is in great upheaval!$B$BThe Dark One rides forth again with his San\'layn, the dragons fight in their great Nexus War, and the vrykul are reawakened.$B$BYour people sail north on your wooden ships to fight them and one another, and we Kalu\'ak are caught in the middle.$B$BAnd now some great evil has been done so that the land explodes with the magical power of the world. We must find a safe haven where we will have a chance to survive.$B$BThese two ambassadors make my head hurt... perhaps you can help my people, $r?' WHERE entry=12575; /* Text0_0: The land is in great upheaval!$B$BThe Dark One rides forth again with his San\'layn, the dragons fight in their great Nexus War, and the vrykul are reawakened.$B$BYour people sail north on your wooden ships to fight them and one another, and we Kalu\'ak are caught in the middle.$B$BAnd now some great evil has been done so that the land explodes with the magical power of the world. We must find a safe haven where we will have a chance to survive.$B$BThese two ambassadors make my head hurt... perhaps you can help my people, $r? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='It is truly a pleasure to see you again, $n.'Text1_1_loc9='$n! I\'ve been wondering how you were. What\'s kept you?' WHERE entry=12576; /* Text0_1: It is truly a pleasure to see you again, $n. */ /* Text1_1: $n! I\'ve been wondering how you were. What\'s kept you? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_1_loc9='I trust you\'re taking every precaution....$b$bThis is a dangerous place and I couldn\'t forgive myself if something were to happen to you.'Text3_1_loc9='We must hurry, $n. Malygos\' ruinous plans will soon be irreversible.' WHERE entry=12576; /* Text2_1: I trust you\'re taking every precaution....$b$bThis is a dangerous place and I couldn\'t forgive myself if something were to happen to you. */ /* Text3_1: We must hurry, $n. Malygos\' ruinous plans will soon be irreversible. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text4_1_loc9='In times such as these, dear friends are invaluable.$b$bBe safe, $n. As safe as one can be in a place like this....'Text5_1_loc9='If you hadn\'t rescued me from that prison I surely would have succumbed by now.$b$bI have not forgotten....' WHERE entry=12576; /* Text4_1: In times such as these, dear friends are invaluable.$b$bBe safe, $n. As safe as one can be in a place like this.... */ /* Text5_1: If you hadn\'t rescued me from that prison I surely would have succumbed by now.$b$bI have not forgotten.... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text6_1_loc9='When our duty here is behind us, I shall find a way to repay you for my rescue.'Text7_1_loc9='My strength is returning, slowly....$b$bI hope to be able to show you the glory of my true form soon.' WHERE entry=12576; /* Text6_1: When our duty here is behind us, I shall find a way to repay you for my rescue. */ /* Text7_1: My strength is returning, slowly....$b$bI hope to be able to show you the glory of my true form soon. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Oh....$b$bWhere am I?' WHERE entry=12577; /* Text0_1: Oh....$b$bWhere am I? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Kvaldir are without mercy, $N.  But I cannot abandon sacred Kaskala.  If we don\'t abandon the spirits, the spirits will not abandon us either.' WHERE entry=12578; /* Text0_0: The Kvaldir are without mercy, $N.  But I cannot abandon sacred Kaskala.  If we don\'t abandon the spirits, the spirits will not abandon us either. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Kaskala\'s under attack!  We must hold them off until we can escape.' WHERE entry=12579; /* Text0_0: Kaskala\'s under attack!  We must hold them off until we can escape. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Cursed giant-men!  If they want a fight, a fight they\'ll get!' WHERE entry=12580; /* Text0_0: Cursed giant-men!  If they want a fight, a fight they\'ll get! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with a Horde settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Alliance, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them.',Text0_1_loc9='Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with a Horde settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Alliance, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them.',Text1_0_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:',Text1_1_loc9='MISSING ENGLISH Text1:' WHERE entry=12582; /* Text0_0: Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with a Horde settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Alliance, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them. */ /* Text0_1: Welcome, $c. Have you come to honor this flame?$b$bRemember: Our festival fires burn in every land with a Horde settlement. Make time to honor each of them, if you can.$b$bThe Alliance, too, burns fires of their own. You would do well to desecrate such unworthy efforts when you see them. */ /* Text1_0: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */ /* Text1_1: MISSING ENGLISH Text1: */
