UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We are what the cold wind carries. The icy chill of despair... The cold embrace of death...' WHERE entry=13174; /* Text0_0: We are what the cold wind carries. The icy chill of despair... The cold embrace of death... */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='It saddens all of us to see the Drakkari destroying themselves this way.$B$BThe power that they gain from killing the natural gods of the land is transitory.$B$BWhat is gained in the short run will be lost to them for all eternity.' WHERE entry=13176; /* Text0_0: It saddens all of us to see the Drakkari destroying themselves this way.$B$BThe power that they gain from killing the natural gods of the land is transitory.$B$BWhat is gained in the short run will be lost to them for all eternity. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Gather your senses quickly, we must press on.' WHERE entry=13177; /* Text0_0: Gather your senses quickly, we must press on. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This isn\'t getting any easier. Stratholme is burning. We must brave the Scourge and the flames to reach Mal\'Ganis. Prepare yourselves.' WHERE entry=13179; /* Text0_0: This isn\'t getting any easier. Stratholme is burning. We must brave the Scourge and the flames to reach Mal\'Ganis. Prepare yourselves. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Zim\'Torga is able to provide us with a certain level of protection, but she has been greatly weakened by the presence of the Scourge and the actions of the Drakkari.$B$BIt falls to me and Ahunae to see to the rest of our defenses.' WHERE entry=13180; /* Text0_1: Zim\'Torga is able to provide us with a certain level of protection, but she has been greatly weakened by the presence of the Scourge and the actions of the Drakkari.$B$BIt falls to me and Ahunae to see to the rest of our defenses. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ahunae\'s axe will be the end of the Drakkari.$B$BYou be takin\' care of any that get past my axe!' WHERE entry=13234; /* Text0_0: Ahunae\'s axe will be the end of the Drakkari.$B$BYou be takin\' care of any that get past my axe! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The trickster Mage-Lord Urom protects the third ring.  He will appear alone and defenseless, but do not be fooled by appearances!  Urom is a powerful conjurer who commands a menagerie of Phantasmal creatures.  Seek him out above.$B$BI can grant you the power to call upon a drake from the Red Fight.  Speak to Eternos or Verdisa if you prefer to draw on the power of the Bronze or the Green.' WHERE entry=13237; /* Text0_0: The trickster Mage-Lord Urom protects the third ring.  He will appear alone and defenseless, but do not be fooled by appearances!  Urom is a powerful conjurer who commands a menagerie of Phantasmal creatures.  Seek him out above.$B$BI can grant you the power to call upon a drake from the Red Fight.  Speak to Eternos or Verdisa if you prefer to draw on the power of the Bronze or the Green. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your greatest challenge lies ahead.  Ley-Guardian Eregos is a Blue dragon of immense power. You will find him flying above the uppermost ring. $B$BThe full power of your drakes has been unlocked.  Use their power to defeat Eregos!' WHERE entry=13238; /* Text0_0: Your greatest challenge lies ahead.  Ley-Guardian Eregos is a Blue dragon of immense power. You will find him flying above the uppermost ring. $B$BThe full power of your drakes has been unlocked.  Use their power to defeat Eregos! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You have wrested control of the Oculus from the forces of Malygos.  The Red Flight is in your debt.' WHERE entry=13239; /* Text0_0: You have wrested control of the Oculus from the forces of Malygos.  The Red Flight is in your debt. */
