UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='For a moment I thought you were my beloved Sif... that strand of hair... but no!  It can\'t be... Sif is dead....$B$BMy... my brother.... killed her!' WHERE entry=13801; /* Text0_0: For a moment I thought you were my beloved Sif... that strand of hair... but no!  It can\'t be... Sif is dead....$B$BMy... my brother.... killed her! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ulduar... I was sworn to protect Ulduar.$B$BSworn to protect the Terrace of the Makers.$B$BSworn to protect the pacts between the races of frost.$B$BBut I failed!  I let my brother trick me.  I let him turn me against my allies.  He tricked me into blaming Sif\'s death on a dear friend, Arngrim, the king of the frost giants.$B$BAfter I realized what I\'d done... I... gave in to despair.' WHERE entry=13802; /* Text0_0: Ulduar... I was sworn to protect Ulduar.$B$BSworn to protect the Terrace of the Makers.$B$BSworn to protect the pacts between the races of frost.$B$BBut I failed!  I let my brother trick me.  I let him turn me against my allies.  He tricked me into blaming Sif\'s death on a dear friend, Arngrim, the king of the frost giants.$B$BAfter I realized what I\'d done... I... gave in to despair. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Who are you, little one?  To come speak these words to the mighty Thorim...$B$BI should... crush you!$B$BYet, you\'ve delivered me from my stupor.  Your presence here is a sign!$B$BIt was no accident that I mistook you for Sif.  What would she think of me?  I must prepare for battle.$B$BI must avenge her death and liberate the titans\' sacred grounds from my brother\'s madness!' WHERE entry=13803; /* Text0_0: Who are you, little one?  To come speak these words to the mighty Thorim...$B$BI should... crush you!$B$BYet, you\'ve delivered me from my stupor.  Your presence here is a sign!$B$BIt was no accident that I mistook you for Sif.  What would she think of me?  I must prepare for battle.$B$BI must avenge her death and liberate the titans\' sacred grounds from my brother\'s madness! */
