UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Reinforcements, finally! The prison guards can\'t hold out against this invasion for much longer! You\'ll have to relieve my men and try to hold out for as long as you can. There\'s still some power in the defense system available. Use the activation crystals located around the prison to trigger a discharge if the situation worsens.' WHERE entry=13853; /* Text0_1: Reinforcements, finally! The prison guards can\'t hold out against this invasion for much longer! You\'ll have to relieve my men and try to hold out for as long as you can. There\'s still some power in the defense system available. Use the activation crystals located around the prison to trigger a discharge if the situation worsens. */
