UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Surprised to see an orc here? Don\'t be.$b$bThe forsaken need watching. If we\'d been paying closer attention from the start, maybe the Wrath Gate wouldn\'t have happened.',Text0_1_loc9='Surprised to see an orc here? Don\'t be.$b$bThe forsaken need watching. If we\'d been paying closer attention from the start, maybe the Wrath Gate wouldn\'t have happened.',Text1_0_loc9='Hope you\'re not looking for those abominations. The apothecaries can\'t be trusted, and that means none of their little constructs patrolling the halls. We\'re here to keep things safe.',Text1_1_loc9='Hope you\'re not looking for those abominations. The apothecaries can\'t be trusted, and that means none of their little constructs patrolling the halls. We\'re here to keep things safe.' WHERE entry=14931; /* Text0_0: Surprised to see an orc here? Don\'t be.$b$bThe forsaken need watching. If we\'d been paying closer attention from the start, maybe the Wrath Gate wouldn\'t have happened. */ /* Text0_1: Surprised to see an orc here? Don\'t be.$b$bThe forsaken need watching. If we\'d been paying closer attention from the start, maybe the Wrath Gate wouldn\'t have happened. */ /* Text1_0: Hope you\'re not looking for those abominations. The apothecaries can\'t be trusted, and that means none of their little constructs patrolling the halls. We\'re here to keep things safe. */ /* Text1_1: Hope you\'re not looking for those abominations. The apothecaries can\'t be trusted, and that means none of their little constructs patrolling the halls. We\'re here to keep things safe. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text2_0_loc9='Lok\'tar. Don\'t try anything suspicious around here. If these undead are going to be part of the Horde, they\'re going to mind themselves under our watch.',Text2_1_loc9='Lok\'tar. Don\'t try anything suspicious around here. If these undead are going to be part of the Horde, they\'re going to mind themselves under our watch.' WHERE entry=14931; /* Text2_0: Lok\'tar. Don\'t try anything suspicious around here. If these undead are going to be part of the Horde, they\'re going to mind themselves under our watch. */ /* Text2_1: Lok\'tar. Don\'t try anything suspicious around here. If these undead are going to be part of the Horde, they\'re going to mind themselves under our watch. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What\'s wrong, bonebag? Looking for someone else? I\'m all you\'ve got now, so if you want something, make it quick.',Text0_1_loc9='What\'s wrong, bonebag? Looking for someone else? I\'m all you\'ve got now, so if you want something, make it quick.',Text1_0_loc9='I bet you rotters thought you were pretty clever at the Wrath Gate, didn\'t you? Playtime\'s over. We\'re here to make sure you don\'t try anything.',Text1_1_loc9='I bet you rotters thought you were pretty clever at the Wrath Gate, didn\'t you? Playtime\'s over. We\'re here to make sure you don\'t try anything.' WHERE entry=14933; /* Text0_0: What\'s wrong, bonebag? Looking for someone else? I\'m all you\'ve got now, so if you want something, make it quick. */ /* Text0_1: What\'s wrong, bonebag? Looking for someone else? I\'m all you\'ve got now, so if you want something, make it quick. */ /* Text1_0: I bet you rotters thought you were pretty clever at the Wrath Gate, didn\'t you? Playtime\'s over. We\'re here to make sure you don\'t try anything. */ /* Text1_1: I bet you rotters thought you were pretty clever at the Wrath Gate, didn\'t you? Playtime\'s over. We\'re here to make sure you don\'t try anything. */
