UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A few weeks in this pathetic castle will give us time to work on some new products and let others forget about the unfortunate... misunderstanding in Dragonblight.' WHERE entry=15040; /* Text0_0: A few weeks in this pathetic castle will give us time to work on some new products and let others forget about the unfortunate... misunderstanding in Dragonblight. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Are you surprised to see me here? Everyone needs clean laundry, and what better way to do it than with your own water elemental?$B$BSimply bring your laundry, pay a nominal fee, and before you know it, everything will be fresh and clean!' WHERE entry=15066; /* Text0_0: Are you surprised to see me here? Everyone needs clean laundry, and what better way to do it than with your own water elemental?$B$BSimply bring your laundry, pay a nominal fee, and before you know it, everything will be fresh and clean! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='What is your business here, $c?' WHERE entry=15074; /* Text0_0: What is your business here, $c? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Never trust the Sunreavers. They are hard at work undermining us in the eyes of our Argent Crusade allies.' WHERE entry=15076; /* Text0_0: Never trust the Sunreavers. They are hard at work undermining us in the eyes of our Argent Crusade allies. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='There you are! I was beginning to think that the Sunreavers had intercepted you. Are you ready to deliver the tome to our representatives in Icecrown?' WHERE entry=15077; /* Text0_0: There you are! I was beginning to think that the Sunreavers had intercepted you. Are you ready to deliver the tome to our representatives in Icecrown? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I cannot hold him for long, we must leave at once!' WHERE entry=15081; /* Text0_1: I cannot hold him for long, we must leave at once! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The old wounds still linger, $g lad:lass;. I can feel \'em in me bones, even now. Aye, I got a score to settle with Arthas and ye can believe I\'m gonna give that boy the beatin\' I shoulda given \'im when he was a wee lad. Always knew there was something wrong with \'im.$B$BTell me when yer crew is ready and we\'ll lift off for the top o\' the citadel.$B$BArthas won\'t be expectin\' this!' WHERE entry=15101; /* Text0_0: The old wounds still linger, $g lad:lass;. I can feel \'em in me bones, even now. Aye, I got a score to settle with Arthas and ye can believe I\'m gonna give that boy the beatin\' I shoulda given \'im when he was a wee lad. Always knew there was something wrong with \'im.$B$BTell me when yer crew is ready and we\'ll lift off for the top o\' the citadel.$B$BArthas won\'t be expectin\' this! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='This is our final stand. What happens here will echo through the ages. Regardless of outcome, they will know that we fought with honor. That we fought for the freedom and safety of our people.$B$BRemember, hero, fear is your greatest enemy in these befouled halls. Steel your heart and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. They will fall as the light of righteousness envelops them!' WHERE entry=15103; /* Text0_0: This is our final stand. What happens here will echo through the ages. Regardless of outcome, they will know that we fought with honor. That we fought for the freedom and safety of our people.$B$BRemember, hero, fear is your greatest enemy in these befouled halls. Steel your heart and your soul will shine brighter than a thousand suns. The enemy will falter at the sight of you. They will fall as the light of righteousness envelops them! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your jormungar can only move if you\'ve submerged beneath the snow, but it cannot attack while submerged. Once your jormungar emerges, it can use its powerful acid attack to wear through the armor of the Iron Colossus. Be ready to submerge to escape from the Iron Colossus\'s most devastating attacks.' WHERE entry=15119; /* Text0_0: Your jormungar can only move if you\'ve submerged beneath the snow, but it cannot attack while submerged. Once your jormungar emerges, it can use its powerful acid attack to wear through the armor of the Iron Colossus. Be ready to submerge to escape from the Iron Colossus\'s most devastating attacks. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Lost your Rocket Pack? Have you checked your bags?' WHERE entry=15123; /* Text0_0: Lost your Rocket Pack? Have you checked your bags? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Why you\'re just the $c I was looking for! I\'m testing a new rocket-powered flying device, and I need your help!$B$BJust take one of these harnesses and put it on under your armor.  Hit the button on the side, and BOOM, off you go.$B$BDon\'t go trying to steal my work though. Each of these babies is fitted with a Transponster 8000 linked to the one in my hand. If you get too far from me the Transponster will shut down the main rocket and you\'ll be unable to lift off until you return.$B$BNow where did I put those liability forms?' WHERE entry=15134; /* Text0_0: Why you\'re just the $c I was looking for! I\'m testing a new rocket-powered flying device, and I need your help!$B$BJust take one of these harnesses and put it on under your armor.  Hit the button on the side, and BOOM, off you go.$B$BDon\'t go trying to steal my work though. Each of these babies is fitted with a Transponster 8000 linked to the one in my hand. If you get too far from me the Transponster will shut down the main rocket and you\'ll be unable to lift off until you return.$B$BNow where did I put those liability forms? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I will delay here until more reinforcements arrive, but you have to keep moving. We won\'t have much time until Arthas realizes we\'re here.' WHERE entry=15152; /* Text0_1: I will delay here until more reinforcements arrive, but you have to keep moving. We won\'t have much time until Arthas realizes we\'re here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='These appear to be the remains of Thalorien Dawnseeker, the last wielder of Quel\'Delar.' WHERE entry=15155; /* Text0_0: These appear to be the remains of Thalorien Dawnseeker, the last wielder of Quel\'Delar. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I cannot hold him for long, we must leave at once!' WHERE entry=15157; /* Text0_1: I cannot hold him for long, we must leave at once! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Ready yourself, $c.$b$bThe time has come for the Lich King\'s reign to come to an end.' WHERE entry=15158; /* Text0_0: Ready yourself, $c.$b$bThe time has come for the Lich King\'s reign to come to an end. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Ashen Verdict is a select group of the most talented craftsmen in the Ebon Blade and Argent Crusade. Its creation symbolizes the unity of our forces as we mount this final assault on the Lich King and his minions.$b$bIt is through the Ashen Verdict\'s efforts that we have discovered how to bend primordial saronite to our will.' WHERE entry=15159; /* Text0_0: The Ashen Verdict is a select group of the most talented craftsmen in the Ebon Blade and Argent Crusade. Its creation symbolizes the unity of our forces as we mount this final assault on the Lich King and his minions.$b$bIt is through the Ashen Verdict\'s efforts that we have discovered how to bend primordial saronite to our will. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Speak with Alchemist Finklestein, $c. He can set you on the path.$b$bDemonstrate your loyalty and their methods shall be made known to you.' WHERE entry=15160; /* Text0_0: Speak with Alchemist Finklestein, $c. He can set you on the path.$b$bDemonstrate your loyalty and their methods shall be made known to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The Lich King is near, $n. His voice taunts me...$b$bLet us silence him at last!' WHERE entry=15166; /* Text0_0: The Lich King is near, $n. His voice taunts me...$b$bLet us silence him at last! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Yo! I\'m here representing the Crown Chemical Company.$B$BYou looking for a gift? A job? Maybe a little something for yourself? Well, you\'ve come to the right place, friend.$B$BIf I don\'t have what you need, our mascot Kwee or the Lovely Merchant beside me will.' WHERE entry=15170; /* Text0_0: Yo! I\'m here representing the Crown Chemical Company.$B$BYou looking for a gift? A job? Maybe a little something for yourself? Well, you\'ve come to the right place, friend.$B$BIf I don\'t have what you need, our mascot Kwee or the Lovely Merchant beside me will. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We\'ll make use of these supplies to get everyone ready for a fight.$B$BContinue on. We\'ll meet you ahead.' WHERE entry=15171; /* Text0_0: We\'ll make use of these supplies to get everyone ready for a fight.$B$BContinue on. We\'ll meet you ahead. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I\'ll gather up the rest of slaves and get them ready to fight. We\'ll catch up with you before you engage Scourgelord Tyrannus.' WHERE entry=15172; /* Text0_0: I\'ll gather up the rest of slaves and get them ready to fight. We\'ll catch up with you before you engage Scourgelord Tyrannus. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='We will follow your lead, heroes. The Scourgelord will die this eve.' WHERE entry=15174; /* Text0_0: We will follow your lead, heroes. The Scourgelord will die this eve. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Hey, pal, I don\'t know who you are or why you\'ve been following me around, but I\'m about to board a ship and I want to be left alone, got it?' WHERE entry=15188; /* Text0_0: Hey, pal, I don\'t know who you are or why you\'ve been following me around, but I\'m about to board a ship and I want to be left alone, got it? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='Forgive me, heroes. I should have listened to Uther. I... I just had to see for myself. To look into his eyes one last time. I am sorry.' WHERE entry=15189; /* Text0_1: Forgive me, heroes. I should have listened to Uther. I... I just had to see for myself. To look into his eyes one last time. I am sorry. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We are safe... for now. His strength has increased tenfold since our last battle. It will take a mighty army to destroy the Lich King. An army greater than even the Horde can rouse.' WHERE entry=15190; /* Text0_1: We are safe... for now. His strength has increased tenfold since our last battle. It will take a mighty army to destroy the Lich King. An army greater than even the Horde can rouse. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='I will delay here until more reinforcements arrive, but you must keep moving. Arthas will soon realize that we\'re here.' WHERE entry=15191; /* Text0_1: I will delay here until more reinforcements arrive, but you must keep moving. Arthas will soon realize that we\'re here. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='\'Twas a fierce battle, $N! Take a moment to rest and gather yer forces. Who knows what lies beyond that door?$B$BLet me know when yer ready and we\'ll begin our ascent into the upper reaches of the citadel.' WHERE entry=15194; /* Text0_0: \'Twas a fierce battle, $N! Take a moment to rest and gather yer forces. Who knows what lies beyond that door?$B$BLet me know when yer ready and we\'ll begin our ascent into the upper reaches of the citadel. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Are ye sure, $g lad:lass;? Ye don\'t need another minute or two?' WHERE entry=15195; /* Text0_0: Are ye sure, $g lad:lass;? Ye don\'t need another minute or two? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_1_loc9='We have no time to waste, $c. Why do you delay here?' WHERE entry=15206; /* Text0_1: We have no time to waste, $c. Why do you delay here? */
