UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Truly an amazing sword, don\'t you think? That\'s no weapon of dwarven make, no, it\'s far more ancient than that.$B$BThese Sunreaver and Silver Covenant representatives seem intent on getting to the bottom of the mystery. I\'m already working on a report for Brann.' WHERE entry=15287; /* Text0_0: Truly an amazing sword, don\'t you think? That\'s no weapon of dwarven make, no, it\'s far more ancient than that.$B$BThese Sunreaver and Silver Covenant representatives seem intent on getting to the bottom of the mystery. I\'m already working on a report for Brann. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Long have I waited for this day, hero. Are you and your allies prepared to bring the Lich King to justice? We charge on your command!' WHERE entry=15290; /* Text0_0: Long have I waited for this day, hero. Are you and your allies prepared to bring the Lich King to justice? We charge on your command! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='A self-inflicted wound, friend.  I could not bear to look upon a world where I\'d committed so many horrors under the Lich King\'s grasp.$B$BIt was my first step towards redemption, and if my sins are unforgivable, then I will attempt to atone for them for the rest of my life.' WHERE entry=15297; /* Text0_0: A self-inflicted wound, friend.  I could not bear to look upon a world where I\'d committed so many horrors under the Lich King\'s grasp.$B$BIt was my first step towards redemption, and if my sins are unforgivable, then I will attempt to atone for them for the rest of my life. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='I was once a paladin, $N.  Now the Light shuns me, for my sins are too great.$B$BI will aid my allies as best I can, but never again will I wield the powers of darkness.' WHERE entry=15298; /* Text0_0: I was once a paladin, $N.  Now the Light shuns me, for my sins are too great.$B$BI will aid my allies as best I can, but never again will I wield the powers of darkness. */
