UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='At last it is time for the exiled gnomes to return.$B$BOnce again Gnomeregan will be our home!' WHERE entry=15578; /* Text0_0: At last it is time for the exiled gnomes to return.$B$BOnce again Gnomeregan will be our home! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The dwarves have kept us safe in their home for some time now, and for that we thank them.  However, the traitorous Thermaplugg\'s occupation of our home must at last come to an end.$B$BGnomeregan has festered beneath the atomic weight of our ill-conceived plan for too long. The detonation of the radiation bombs drove us from our city, but we now possess the technology to take it back!$B$BWe will regain what is ours... and bring Thermaplugg to justice!' WHERE entry=15580; /* Text0_0: The dwarves have kept us safe in their home for some time now, and for that we thank them.  However, the traitorous Thermaplugg\'s occupation of our home must at last come to an end.$B$BGnomeregan has festered beneath the atomic weight of our ill-conceived plan for too long. The detonation of the radiation bombs drove us from our city, but we now possess the technology to take it back!$B$BWe will regain what is ours... and bring Thermaplugg to justice! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Operation: Gnomeregan is divided into a number of phases:$B$BFirst, we must retake the air tower.  This will allow our planes give us air support as we move towards Gnomeregan\'s main entrance.$B$BIn addition, a cache of mechanized Battle Suits was discovered in one of the nearby buildings.  Once we have those suits, our assault on the entrance should be unstoppable.$B$BThen, we go straight for Thermaplugg in the heart of Gnomeregan!' WHERE entry=15581; /* Text0_0: Operation: Gnomeregan is divided into a number of phases:$B$BFirst, we must retake the air tower.  This will allow our planes give us air support as we move towards Gnomeregan\'s main entrance.$B$BIn addition, a cache of mechanized Battle Suits was discovered in one of the nearby buildings.  Once we have those suits, our assault on the entrance should be unstoppable.$B$BThen, we go straight for Thermaplugg in the heart of Gnomeregan! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='The continued sacrifice of the Ashen Verdict and heroes such as yourself bring us all closer to final victory. Now I have come to Icecrown Citadel to lend aid to those who fight against the Scourge. Together we will end the tyranny of the Lich King!' WHERE entry=15602; /* Text0_0: The continued sacrifice of the Ashen Verdict and heroes such as yourself bring us all closer to final victory. Now I have come to Icecrown Citadel to lend aid to those who fight against the Scourge. Together we will end the tyranny of the Lich King! */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You can do this alone, you say? Is this simple foolishness or misplaced confidence I see before me?$B$BNo, I can see it in your eyes. You have to know. You have to prove to yourself that you can do this alone. Very well. I will retreat from the battlefield if you so wish it.' WHERE entry=15603; /* Text0_0: You can do this alone, you say? Is this simple foolishness or misplaced confidence I see before me?$B$BNo, I can see it in your eyes. You have to know. You have to prove to yourself that you can do this alone. Very well. I will retreat from the battlefield if you so wish it. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='You will need more than bravery to defeat the Lich King. Good luck.' WHERE entry=15604; /* Text0_0: You will need more than bravery to defeat the Lich King. Good luck. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='Your choice has been made. Whether you live or die by that choice is now up to you.' WHERE entry=15605; /* Text0_0: Your choice has been made. Whether you live or die by that choice is now up to you. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET Text0_0_loc9='With the Warsong Offensive here in Icecrown Citadel, victory is within our grasp! The death of the Lich King will bring glory to the Horde!' WHERE entry=15606; /* Text0_0: With the Warsong Offensive here in Icecrown Citadel, victory is within our grasp! The death of the Lich King will bring glory to the Horde! */
